Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.87,0:00:39.86,CHT,2,0,0,0,,…大家注意，暴風仍在向西移動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.87,0:00:39.86,ENG,2,0,0,0,,... and I'll tell you what, the storm system's still moving west.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:42.96,CHT,3,0,0,0,,在看什麼呢，卡洛琳？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:42.96,ENG,3,0,0,0,,What are you looking at, Caroline?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:45.56,CHT,4,0,0,0,,看風，媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:45.56,ENG,4,0,0,0,,The wind, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.68,0:00:51.08,CHT,5,0,0,0,,他們說颶風要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.68,0:00:51.08,ENG,5,0,0,0,,They say the hurricane is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:55.91,CHT,6,0,0,0,,我感覺像在一艘船上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:55.91,ENG,6,0,0,0,,I'm on a boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.02,0:00:58.28,CHT,7,0,0,0,,漂浮著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.02,0:00:58.28,ENG,7,0,0,0,,I'm drifting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:02.92,CHT,8,0,0,0,,我可以做什麼嗎，媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:02.92,ENG,8,0,0,0,,Can I do anything for you, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:06.16,CHT,9,0,0,0,,讓你舒服點？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:06.16,ENG,9,0,0,0,,Make anything easier?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:08.53,CHT,10,0,0,0,,哦，寶貝…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:08.53,ENG,10,0,0,0,,Oh, sugar...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.06,0:01:11.33,CHT,11,0,0,0,,沒什麼可做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.06,0:01:11.33,ENG,11,0,0,0,,There's nothing left to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,0:01:13.42,CHT,12,0,0,0,,就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,0:01:13.42,ENG,12,0,0,0,,Is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:17.90,CHT,13,0,0,0,,我越來越睜不開眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:17.90,ENG,13,0,0,0,,Finding it harder to keep my eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:23.00,CHT,14,0,0,0,,嘴裡像是塞滿了棉花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:23.00,ENG,14,0,0,0,,My mouth's full of cotton.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.54,0:01:25.67,CHT,15,0,0,0,,好了，好了，黛西女士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.54,0:01:25.67,ENG,15,0,0,0,,There, there, Miss Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.78,0:01:28.51,CHT,16,0,0,0,,你快把自己抓傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.78,0:01:28.51,ENG,16,0,0,0,,You gonna scratch yourself to ribbons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.42,0:01:36.22,CHT,17,0,0,0,,藥還要嗎，媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.42,0:01:36.22,ENG,17,0,0,0,,Do you want any more medication, Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.12,0:01:40.32,CHT,18,0,0,0,,醫生說用多點沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.12,0:01:40.32,ENG,18,0,0,0,,Doctor said you could have as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:42.69,CHT,19,0,0,0,,這樣大家都不會遭罪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:42.69,ENG,19,0,0,0,,No need for anybody to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:02:00.58,CHT,20,0,0,0,,有個朋友說過，她甚至都沒有機會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:02:00.58,ENG,20,0,0,0,,A friend told me that she never had the chance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:02.98,CHT,21,0,0,0,,跟她母親道別
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:02.98,ENG,21,0,0,0,,to say goodbye to her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:08.45,CHT,22,0,0,0,,- 我想… - 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:08.45,ENG,22,0,0,0,,- I wanted to... - It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:12.08,CHT,23,0,0,0,,我想告訴你，我會非常想念你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:12.08,ENG,23,0,0,0,,I wanted to tell you how much I'm gonna miss you so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:13.65,CHT,24,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:13.65,ENG,24,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:17.43,CHT,25,0,0,0,,哦，卡洛琳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:17.43,ENG,25,0,0,0,,Oh, Caroline.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:24.73,CHT,26,0,0,0,,你怕嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:24.73,ENG,26,0,0,0,,Are you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:26.53,CHT,27,0,0,0,,我很好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:26.53,ENG,27,0,0,0,,I'm curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:29.94,CHT,28,0,0,0,,接下來會怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:29.94,ENG,28,0,0,0,,What comes next?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:40.25,CHT,29,0,0,0,,火車站建於1918年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:40.25,ENG,29,0,0,0,,They built the train station in 1918.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:44.02,CHT,30,0,0,0,,開站那天我父親也去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:44.02,ENG,30,0,0,0,,My father was there the day it opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:48.39,CHT,31,0,0,0,,他說那天還請了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:48.39,ENG,31,0,0,0,,He said they had
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:51.63,CHT,32,0,0,0,,銅管樂隊表演
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:51.63,ENG,32,0,0,0,,a tuba band playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:03:00.46,CHT,33,0,0,0,,還請來了整個南方最好的鐘錶匠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:03:00.46,ENG,33,0,0,0,,They had the finest clockmaker in all of the South
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:03.87,CHT,34,0,0,0,,建了那座雄偉的大鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:03.87,ENG,34,0,0,0,,to build that glorious clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:07.30,CHT,35,0,0,0,,那人叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:07.30,ENG,35,0,0,0,,His name was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:11.01,CHT,36,0,0,0,,蓋圖先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:11.01,ENG,36,0,0,0,,Mr. Gateau.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:16.55,CHT,37,0,0,0,,蛋糕先生 （蓋圖/Gateau在法語中是蛋糕之意）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:16.55,ENG,37,0,0,0,,Mr. Cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:23.29,CHT,38,0,0,0,,他娶了伊文格琳縣一個克裡奧爾人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:23.29,ENG,38,0,0,0,,He was married to a Creole of Evangeline Parish
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:25.63,CHT,39,0,0,0,,後來他們生了個兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:25.63,ENG,39,0,0,0,,and they had a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:32.67,CHT,40,0,0,0,,蓋圖先生先天失明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:32.67,ENG,40,0,0,0,,Mr. Gateau was, from birth, absolutely blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:39.17,CHT,41,0,0,0,,他們的兒子長大後就參了軍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:39.17,ENG,41,0,0,0,,When their son was old enough, he joined the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:44.48,CHT,42,0,0,0,,他們向上帝祈禱，保佑他平安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:44.48,ENG,42,0,0,0,,And they prayed God would keep him out of harm's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:52.15,CHT,43,0,0,0,,好幾個月，他除了建那鐘，什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:52.15,ENG,43,0,0,0,,For months, he did nothing but work on that clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:57.66,CHT,44,0,0,0,,然後有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:57.66,ENG,44,0,0,0,,One day,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:00.93,CHT,45,0,0,0,,他們收到一封信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:00.93,ENG,45,0,0,0,,a letter came.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:09.90,CHT,46,0,0,0,,那天晚上工作完後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:09.90,ENG,46,0,0,0,,And Mr. Gateau, done for the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:13.10,CHT,47,0,0,0,,蓋圖先生就獨自去睡覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:13.10,ENG,47,0,0,0,,went up, alone, to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:18.58,CHT,48,0,0,0,,然後他們的兒子回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:18.58,ENG,48,0,0,0,,And their son came home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:26.56,CHT,49,0,0,0,,他們把他埋在家族墓地裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:26.56,ENG,49,0,0,0,,They buried him in the family plot,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:30.56,CHT,50,0,0,0,,等他們死後，一家就能團聚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:30.56,ENG,50,0,0,0,,where he would be with them when their time came.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:35.66,CHT,51,0,0,0,,蛋糕先生繼續建造那座鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:35.66,ENG,51,0,0,0,,Mr. Cake worked on his clock,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:42.13,CHT,52,0,0,0,,耗盡心血，終於完工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:42.13,ENG,52,0,0,0,,laboring to finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:47.38,CHT,53,0,0,0,,那是一個值得紀念的早上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:47.38,ENG,53,0,0,0,,It was a morning to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:51.81,CHT,54,0,0,0,,爸爸說，那天人山人海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:51.81,ENG,54,0,0,0,,Papa said there were people everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:55.81,CHT,55,0,0,0,,連泰迪·羅斯福都來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:55.81,ENG,55,0,0,0,,Even Teddy Roosevelt came.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.57,0:05:15.44,CHT,56,0,0,0,,鐘倒走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.57,0:05:15.44,ENG,56,0,0,0,,It's running backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:18.81,CHT,57,0,0,0,,我故意這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:18.81,ENG,57,0,0,0,,I made it that way
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:22.28,CHT,58,0,0,0,,這樣那些在戰爭中死去的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:22.28,ENG,58,0,0,0,,so that perhaps the boys that we lost in the war
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:23.75,CHT,59,0,0,0,,也許就會死而復生，回家來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:23.75,ENG,59,0,0,0,,might stand and come home again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:30.09,CHT,60,0,0,0,,回家耕種
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:30.09,ENG,60,0,0,0,,Home to farm,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:32.39,CHT,61,0,0,0,,工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:32.39,ENG,61,0,0,0,,work,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:35.66,CHT,62,0,0,0,,生兒育女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:35.66,ENG,62,0,0,0,,have children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:41.43,CHT,63,0,0,0,,過完他們漫長而充實的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:41.43,ENG,63,0,0,0,,To live long, full lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:47.30,CHT,64,0,0,0,,也許我自己的兒子也能回家來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:47.30,ENG,64,0,0,0,,Perhaps my own son might come home again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:58.51,CHT,65,0,0,0,,如有得罪，請各位原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:58.51,ENG,65,0,0,0,,I'm sorry if I've offended anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:02.35,CHT,66,0,0,0,,希望你們喜歡我的鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:02.35,ENG,66,0,0,0,,I hope you enjoy my clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:07.13,CHT,67,0,0,0,,蛋糕先生自此再沒出現過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:07.13,ENG,67,0,0,0,,Mr. Cake was never seen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:15.90,CHT,68,0,0,0,,有人說他心碎而死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:15.90,ENG,68,0,0,0,,Some say he died of a broken heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:19.94,CHT,69,0,0,0,,有人說他出海了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:19.94,ENG,69,0,0,0,,Some say he went to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:26.24,CHT,70,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:26.24,ENG,70,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:28.91,CHT,71,0,0,0,,我可以打個電話嗎？我孩子請人照看著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:28.91,ENG,71,0,0,0,,Do you mind if I make a call? Somebody's watching my little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:30.24,CHT,72,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:30.24,ENG,72,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:42.72,CHT,73,0,0,0,,希望我沒讓你失望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:42.72,ENG,73,0,0,0,,I hope I haven't disappointed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:45.92,CHT,74,0,0,0,,你不會讓我失望的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:45.92,ENG,74,0,0,0,,You couldn't disappoint me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:52.27,CHT,75,0,0,0,,我知道自己沒什麼才能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:52.27,ENG,75,0,0,0,,Well, I know I don't have much to show for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:57.28,CHT,76,0,0,0,,把我的黑色手提箱找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:57.28,ENG,76,0,0,0,,Find my dark suitcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:04.55,CHT,77,0,0,0,,裡面有本日記
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:04.55,ENG,77,0,0,0,,There's a diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:07.78,CHT,78,0,0,0,,這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:07.78,ENG,78,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.52,0:07:13.43,CHT,79,0,0,0,,能念給我聽聽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.52,0:07:13.43,ENG,79,0,0,0,,Could you read it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:16.23,CHT,80,0,0,0,,你就想這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:16.23,ENG,80,0,0,0,,Is this what you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:20.23,CHT,81,0,0,0,,我讀過無數次了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:20.23,ENG,81,0,0,0,,I tried to read it a hundred different times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:23.19,CHT,82,0,0,0,,媽媽，這並不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:23.19,ENG,82,0,0,0,,Mom, it's not exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:26.70,CHT,83,0,0,0,,只是想聽聽你的聲音，親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:26.70,ENG,83,0,0,0,,It's just the sound of your voice, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.54,CHT,84,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.54,ENG,84,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:34.65,CHT,85,0,0,0,,時間是1985年4月4日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:34.65,ENG,85,0,0,0,,It's dated April 4th, 1985.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:38.11,CHT,86,0,0,0,,上面寫著新奧爾良
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:38.11,ENG,86,0,0,0,,And it says New Orleans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:40.95,CHT,87,0,0,0,,“這是我最後的遺言，也是遺囑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:40.95,ENG,87,0,0,0,,"This is my last will and testament.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:45.25,CHT,88,0,0,0,,“我沒留下什麼，沒財產，沒錢，真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:45.25,ENG,88,0,0,0,,"I don't have much to leave, few possessions, no money, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:50.89,CHT,89,0,0,0,,“我孤獨地來，孤獨地去 生不帶來，死不帶去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:50.89,ENG,89,0,0,0,,"I will go out of this world the same way I came in, alone and with nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:53.40,CHT,90,0,0,0,,“我僅有的就是我的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:53.40,ENG,90,0,0,0,,"All I have is my story,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:56.93,CHT,91,0,0,0,,“我現在就寫著，趁我還記得的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:56.93,ENG,91,0,0,0,,"and I'm writing it now while I still remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:00.90,CHT,92,0,0,0,,“我的名字叫本傑明，本傑明·巴頓”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:00.90,ENG,92,0,0,0,,"My name is Benjamin. Benjamin Button."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:04.37,CHT,93,0,0,0,,我的出生很不尋常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:04.37,ENG,93,0,0,0,,And I was born under unusual circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.35,0:08:07.58,CHT,94,0,0,0,,那時一戰剛結束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.35,0:08:07.58,ENG,94,0,0,0,,The First World War had ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:12.15,CHT,95,0,0,0,,後來我聽說，我出生的那個夜晚特別好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:12.15,ENG,95,0,0,0,,and I've been told it was an especially good night to be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:15.95,CHT,96,0,0,0,,謝天謝地終於結束了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:15.95,ENG,96,0,0,0,,Thank God it's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:17.85,CHT,97,0,0,0,,我們贏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:17.85,ENG,97,0,0,0,,We won the war!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:34.57,CHT,98,0,0,0,,世界大戰結束了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:34.57,ENG,98,0,0,0,,The Great War is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:47.88,CHT,99,0,0,0,,你來這幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:47.88,ENG,99,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.99,0:08:49.29,CHT,100,0,0,0,,湯瑪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.99,0:08:49.29,ENG,100,0,0,0,,Thomas,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:51.96,CHT,101,0,0,0,,恐怕她快撐不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:51.96,ENG,101,0,0,0,,I'm afraid she's going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:53.22,CHT,102,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:53.22,ENG,102,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:58.02,CHT,103,0,0,0,,夠了，你們都離她遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:58.02,ENG,103,0,0,0,,That's enough. All of you, get away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:04.33,CHT,104,0,0,0,,我已經儘快趕回來了，街上盡是人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:04.33,ENG,104,0,0,0,,I came as quickly as I could. The streets are filled with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:05.70,CHT,105,0,0,0,,湯瑪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:05.70,ENG,105,0,0,0,,Thomas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:08.80,CHT,106,0,0,0,,答應我，給他個容身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:08.80,ENG,106,0,0,0,,Promise me he has a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.34,CHT,107,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.34,ENG,107,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:15.70,CHT,108,0,0,0,,她把生命給了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:15.70,ENG,108,0,0,0,,She gave her life for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:19.72,CHT,109,0,0,0,,對此我畢生感激
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:19.72,ENG,109,0,0,0,,And for that, I am forever grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:30.73,CHT,110,0,0,0,,巴頓先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:30.73,ENG,110,0,0,0,,Mr. Button.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:47.27,CHT,111,0,0,0,,湯瑪斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:47.27,ENG,111,0,0,0,,Thomas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:48.61,CHT,112,0,0,0,,湯瑪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:48.61,ENG,112,0,0,0,,Thomas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:52.78,CHT,113,0,0,0,,湯瑪斯？你去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:52.78,ENG,113,0,0,0,,Thomas? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:23.75,CHT,114,0,0,0,,嘿！你在這幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:23.75,ENG,114,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:27.01,CHT,115,0,0,0,,懷裡的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:27.01,ENG,115,0,0,0,,What do you have there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:27.01,CHT,116,0,0,0,,- 快點，奎尼 - 快，韋瑟斯先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:27.01,ENG,116,0,0,0,,- Come on, Queenie. - Now, Mr. Weathers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.11,0:11:30.48,CHT,117,0,0,0,,得了，除了工作 我在這還有很多事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.11,0:11:30.48,ENG,117,0,0,0,,Come on, now, you know I ain't got nothing but work to do around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:32.85,CHT,118,0,0,0,,- 別，就一會 - 別犯傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:32.85,ENG,118,0,0,0,,- Come on. Just take some time. - Stop all this foolishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:37.82,CHT,119,0,0,0,,空氣真清新
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:37.82,ENG,119,0,0,0,,The air is sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:45.32,CHT,120,0,0,0,,你今晚真迷人，奎尼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:45.32,ENG,120,0,0,0,,You look very handsome tonight, Miss Queenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.79,CHT,121,0,0,0,,一如既往的美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.79,ENG,121,0,0,0,,Handsome as I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:52.47,CHT,122,0,0,0,,棕色真配你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:52.47,ENG,122,0,0,0,,The brown matches your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:53.90,CHT,CHT,0,0,0,,哦，討厭！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:53.90,ENG,CHT,0,0,0,,Oh, hush!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:59.51,CHT,124,0,0,0,,讓我瞧瞧，你也不賴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:59.51,ENG,124,0,0,0,,Let's see here. You ain't no slouch yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.09,0:12:09.89,CHT,125,0,0,0,,漢伯特回鎮上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.09,0:12:09.89,ENG,125,0,0,0,,Hambert's back in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:13.76,CHT,126,0,0,0,,他的兩條腿沒了，不過總算回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:13.76,ENG,126,0,0,0,,He came home legless, but he's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:17.39,CHT,127,0,0,0,,我知道你一度很迷戀他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:17.39,ENG,127,0,0,0,,I know you were sweet on him one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:19.80,CHT,128,0,0,0,,喜歡得都過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:19.80,ENG,128,0,0,0,,Sweeter than I should've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:21.80,CHT,129,0,0,0,,西蒙妮小姐又尿褲子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:21.80,ENG,129,0,0,0,,Miss Simone messed herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:23.13,CHT,130,0,0,0,,哦，我的小祖宗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:23.13,ENG,130,0,0,0,,Oh, sweet Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:25.76,CHT,131,0,0,0,,她可別這樣了，否則我要給她穿尿布了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:25.76,ENG,131,0,0,0,,She got to stop doing that or it's diapers for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:27.90,CHT,132,0,0,0,,- 我一會就去，詹姆森小姐！ - 快，奎尼，快來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:27.90,ENG,132,0,0,0,,- I'll be right there, Miss Jameson! - Now, Queenie, now come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:30.57,CHT,133,0,0,0,,好吧，奎尼馬上過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:30.57,ENG,133,0,0,0,,Okay, Queenie'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:31.94,CHT,134,0,0,0,,外面太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:31.94,ENG,134,0,0,0,,It's awful nice out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:35.24,CHT,135,0,0,0,,出來透透氣，別想那些事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:35.24,ENG,135,0,0,0,,Come on out back for a moment. Take your mind off things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:36.37,CHT,136,0,0,0,,你好壞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:36.37,ENG,136,0,0,0,,You're so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:38.95,CHT,137,0,0,0,,- 上帝啊？ - 這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:38.95,ENG,137,0,0,0,,- What in God's name? - What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:51.56,CHT,138,0,0,0,,哦，上帝保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:51.56,ENG,138,0,0,0,,Oh, the Lord done something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:55.16,CHT,139,0,0,0,,希望我沒踩傷他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:55.16,ENG,139,0,0,0,,Hope I didn't hurt it none stepping on it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:56.79,CHT,140,0,0,0,,我們最好交給員警處理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:56.79,ENG,140,0,0,0,,We best leave that for the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:58.39,CHT,141,0,0,0,,可憐的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:58.39,ENG,141,0,0,0,,Poor baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:00.57,CHT,142,0,0,0,,我去找員警
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:00.57,ENG,142,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:04.90,CHT,143,0,0,0,,肯定沒人願意收留他，來，寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:04.90,ENG,143,0,0,0,,It's for sure nobody wanted to keep it. Come on, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:10.01,CHT,144,0,0,0,,奎尼？你在哪，奎尼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:10.01,ENG,144,0,0,0,,Queenie? Where are you, Queenie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:12.05,CHT,145,0,0,0,,憋著！你去看下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:12.05,ENG,145,0,0,0,,Hold your water! You go deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:14.25,CHT,146,0,0,0,,好吧，不，你去，我馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:14.25,ENG,146,0,0,0,,Okay. No, go, I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:18.39,CHT,147,0,0,0,,奎尼，蘋果她憋不住又尿了一身！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:18.39,ENG,147,0,0,0,,Queenie, Apple, she went and messed herself all over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:20.36,CHT,148,0,0,0,,簡·查爾裡斯，給她洗洗！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:20.36,ENG,148,0,0,0,,Jane Childress, start her a bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:22.52,CHT,149,0,0,0,,管好你自己的事，杜普雷太太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:22.52,ENG,149,0,0,0,,And mind your own business, Mrs. Duprey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:24.43,CHT,150,0,0,0,,再沒多久你也一團糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:24.43,ENG,150,0,0,0,,You'll be messing yourself soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:26.09,CHT,151,0,0,0,,有人偷了我的項鍊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:26.09,ENG,151,0,0,0,,Somebody stole my necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:29.13,CHT,152,0,0,0,,好的，知道了，霍利斯特太太 我一會就來，好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:29.13,ENG,152,0,0,0,,Okay. All right, Mrs. Hollister, I'll be right with you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:31.43,CHT,153,0,0,0,,回樓上去，聽見了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:31.43,ENG,153,0,0,0,,Go on back upstairs, hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:40.27,CHT,154,0,0,0,,你醜的像只舊罐子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:40.27,ENG,154,0,0,0,,You are as ugly as an old pot
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.04,CHT,155,0,0,0,,可你仍是上帝的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.04,ENG,155,0,0,0,,but you're still a child of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:44.51,CHT,156,0,0,0,,奎尼，你不在蘋果她不肯洗澡！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:44.51,ENG,156,0,0,0,,Queenie, Apple, she won't take a bath without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:46.08,CHT,157,0,0,0,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:46.08,ENG,157,0,0,0,,Mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:48.15,CHT,158,0,0,0,,我馬上就來！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:48.15,ENG,158,0,0,0,,I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:54.13,CHT,159,0,0,0,,好了，你就在這等我，好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:54.13,ENG,159,0,0,0,,Okay. You just wait right here for me now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:14:02.09,CHT,160,0,0,0,,我姐姐給了我那條珍珠項鍊 我怎麼也找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:14:02.09,ENG,160,0,0,0,,My sister gave me those pearls. I can't find them anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:06.04,CHT,161,0,0,0,,- 有人偷了我的珠寶 - 這這呢，霍利斯特夫人，看見了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:06.04,ENG,161,0,0,0,,- Somebody's been stealing my jewelry. - They're right here, Mrs. Hollister. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:09.44,CHT,162,0,0,0,,就掛在你那雪白漂亮的脖子上 好了，都別吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:09.44,ENG,162,0,0,0,,Right around your pretty white neck. Now, come on. Hush all that noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:12.14,CHT,163,0,0,0,,- 羅斯醫生還在這嗎？ - 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:12.14,ENG,163,0,0,0,,- Is Dr. Rose still here? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.25,CHT,164,0,0,0,,你的心臟很健康
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.25,ENG,164,0,0,0,,Your heart is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:19.32,CHT,165,0,0,0,,只要避免過度刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:19.32,ENG,165,0,0,0,,You just want to avoid any undue stimulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:23.01,CHT,166,0,0,0,,我相信各位女士會照看好他的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:23.01,ENG,166,0,0,0,,I trust you ladies will help me out with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:26.25,CHT,167,0,0,0,,我有事找您，您能下樓來一趟嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:26.25,ENG,167,0,0,0,,I have something. Could you come downstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:33.66,CHT,168,0,0,0,,從沒見過，白內障導致幾乎失明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:33.66,ENG,168,0,0,0,,Never seen anything like it. Nearly blind from cataracts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:37.83,CHT,169,0,0,0,,我不確定他能不能聽見 從骨骼看他有嚴重的關節炎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:37.83,ENG,169,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if he can hear. His bones indicate severe arthritis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:43.04,CHT,170,0,0,0,,他的皮膚完全沒有彈性，手腳都硬化了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:43.04,ENG,170,0,0,0,,His skin has lost all elasticity, and his hands and feet are ossified.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:47.74,CHT,171,0,0,0,,他的身體正在衰退，衰弱 一點都不像新生兒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:47.74,ENG,171,0,0,0,,He shows all the deterioration, the infirmities, not of a newborn,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:50.48,CHT,172,0,0,0,,更像是個80多歲行將踏進墳墓的老人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:50.48,ENG,172,0,0,0,,but of a man well in his 80s on his way to the grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:51.57,CHT,173,0,0,0,,他會死嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:51.57,ENG,173,0,0,0,,He's dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:54.92,CHT,174,0,0,0,,生活還沒開始，他的身體就不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:54.92,ENG,174,0,0,0,,His body is failing him before his life's begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.72,CHT,175,0,0,0,,他從哪來？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.72,ENG,175,0,0,0,,Where'd he come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:03.19,CHT,176,0,0,0,,我姐姐的孩子，從拉斐特來（美國城市） 她遭遇了不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:03.19,ENG,176,0,0,0,,My sister's child. From Lafayette. She had an unfortunate adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:07.20,CHT,177,0,0,0,,可憐的孩子，真是太不幸了，還是個白人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:07.20,ENG,177,0,0,0,,The poor child, he got the worst of it. Come out white.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:14.83,CHT,178,0,0,0,,有些地方專門收留這樣的棄兒，奎尼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:14.83,ENG,178,0,0,0,,There are places for unwanted babies like these, Queenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:18.14,CHT,179,0,0,0,,這兒沒地方再養一張嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:18.14,ENG,179,0,0,0,,No room for another mouth to feed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:20.77,CHT,180,0,0,0,,儘管諾蘭基金會出於好意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:20.77,ENG,180,0,0,0,,The Nolan Foundation, despite their good intentions,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:23.64,CHT,181,0,0,0,,可他們還是覺得這地方是個大麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:23.64,ENG,181,0,0,0,,thinks this place is a large nuisance as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:23.85,CHT,182,0,0,0,,- 一個孩子… - 你剛說他活不長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:23.85,ENG,182,0,0,0,,- A baby... - You said he don't have long. - A baby... - You said he don't have long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:25.91,CHT,183,0,0,0,,- 一個孩子… - 你剛說他活不長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:30.58,CHT,184,0,0,0,,奎尼，有些生物註定無法存活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:30.58,ENG,184,0,0,0,,Queenie, some creatures aren't meant to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:37.72,CHT,185,0,0,0,,不，這個孩子，他是個奇跡 這是肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:37.72,ENG,185,0,0,0,,No, this baby, he is a miracle. That's for certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:40.82,CHT,186,0,0,0,,可惜不是那種大家期盼的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:40.82,ENG,186,0,0,0,,Just not the kind of miracle one hopes to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:46.36,CHT,187,0,0,0,,大家聽著，都聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:46.36,ENG,187,0,0,0,,Y'all listen. Y'all listen up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:48.16,CHT,188,0,0,0,,我們有一位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:48.16,ENG,188,0,0,0,,We're gonna have us a visitor
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:51.37,CHT,189,0,0,0,,要和我們住一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:51.37,ENG,189,0,0,0,,that's gonna be staying with us for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:55.17,CHT,190,0,0,0,,我姐姐生了個孩子，她無法撫養，所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:55.17,ENG,190,0,0,0,,My sister had a child and she couldn't see right by it, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:59.18,CHT,191,0,0,0,,他的名字叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:59.18,ENG,191,0,0,0,,He's known as...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:03.75,CHT,192,0,0,0,,本傑明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:03.75,ENG,192,0,0,0,,Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:05.72,CHT,193,0,0,0,,本傑明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:05.72,ENG,193,0,0,0,,Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:09.56,CHT,194,0,0,0,,他的身體不好，我們得好好照顧他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:09.56,ENG,194,0,0,0,,He's not a well child, so we're gonna have to take good care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:10.72,CHT,195,0,0,0,,我有過10個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:10.72,ENG,195,0,0,0,,I had 10 children.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:14.16,CHT,196,0,0,0,,每個我都照顧得很好，讓我看看他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:14.16,ENG,196,0,0,0,,There's not a baby I can't care for. Let me see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:20.00,CHT,197,0,0,0,,天啊，他跟我前夫真像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:20.00,ENG,197,0,0,0,,God in Heaven. He looks just like my ex-husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:23.47,CHT,198,0,0,0,,看，他先天早衰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:23.47,ENG,198,0,0,0,,Look, he's prematurely old.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:27.50,CHT,199,0,0,0,,羅斯醫生說他活不久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:27.50,ENG,199,0,0,0,,Dr. Rose said he ain't got much more time on this earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:28.97,CHT,200,0,0,0,,歡迎加入俱樂部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:28.97,ENG,200,0,0,0,,Join the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:35.55,CHT,201,0,0,0,,他在笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:35.55,ENG,201,0,0,0,,He's smiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.99,CHT,202,0,0,0,,漢伯特讓我轉達他的問候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.99,ENG,202,0,0,0,,Hambert sends his remembrances to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:57.14,CHT,203,0,0,0,,你瘋了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:57.14,ENG,203,0,0,0,,Are you right out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.44,0:17:01.81,CHT,204,0,0,0,,我知道你沒法有自己的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.44,0:17:01.81,ENG,204,0,0,0,,I know you ain't got all the parts it takes to make one of your own,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:03.14,CHT,205,0,0,0,,可你也不能撫養這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:03.14,ENG,205,0,0,0,,but this ain't yours to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:05.51,CHT,206,0,0,0,,他一點都不像人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:05.51,ENG,206,0,0,0,,It may not even be humankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:17.06,CHT,207,0,0,0,,韋瑟斯先生，回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:17.06,ENG,207,0,0,0,,Mr. Weathers, come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:20.63,CHT,208,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:20.63,ENG,208,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:39.54,CHT,209,0,0,0,,你永遠也不清楚接下來會發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:39.54,ENG,209,0,0,0,,You never know what's coming for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:51.93,CHT,210,0,0,0,,看來我找到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:51.93,ENG,210,0,0,0,,It seemed I had found a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:56.16,CHT,211,0,0,0,,這都是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:56.16,ENG,211,0,0,0,,Is any of this true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.27,0:17:59.64,CHT,212,0,0,0,,你的聲音真好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.27,0:17:59.64,ENG,212,0,0,0,,You have such a lovely voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.21,0:18:04.87,CHT,213,0,0,0,,媽媽，這有張舊電車票
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.21,0:18:04.87,ENG,213,0,0,0,,Mom, it's an ancient streetcar token.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:09.71,CHT,214,0,0,0,,那座鐘一直走著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:09.71,ENG,214,0,0,0,,That clock just kept going,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:14.92,CHT,215,0,0,0,,年復一年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:14.92,ENG,215,0,0,0,,year after year after year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.23,0:18:21.13,CHT,216,0,0,0,,可我不知道自己是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.23,0:18:21.13,ENG,216,0,0,0,,But I didn't know I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:23.70,CHT,217,0,0,0,,每天都是這些垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:23.70,ENG,217,0,0,0,,Same old crap every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:27.36,CHT,218,0,0,0,,我以為自己和這裡的人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:27.36,ENG,218,0,0,0,,I thought I was like everyone else there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:30.53,CHT,219,0,0,0,,一個遲暮的老人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:30.53,ENG,219,0,0,0,,An old man in the twilight of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:32.97,CHT,220,0,0,0,,你可以讓他停下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:32.97,ENG,220,0,0,0,,Could you make him stop that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:37.03,CHT,221,0,0,0,,別敲叉子了，那是用來吃飯的 不是拿來玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:37.03,ENG,221,0,0,0,,Stop banging that fork. It's used for eating, not for playing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:39.98,CHT,222,0,0,0,,還有戴上餐巾，本傑明先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:39.98,ENG,222,0,0,0,,And use your napkin, please, Mr. Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:43.61,CHT,223,0,0,0,,奎尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:43.61,ENG,223,0,0,0,,Queenie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:56.99,CHT,224,0,0,0,,嘿，小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:56.99,ENG,224,0,0,0,,Hey, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:06.67,CHT,225,0,0,0,,一直很好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:06.67,ENG,225,0,0,0,,Always had a healthy curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:11.30,CHT,226,0,0,0,,街上是什麼樣子的？下個街角又是怎樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:11.30,ENG,226,0,0,0,,What was up the street? Or around the next corner?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:14.48,CHT,227,0,0,0,,去抓住他！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:14.48,ENG,227,0,0,0,,Go get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:18.28,CHT,228,0,0,0,,本傑明！那太危險了，快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:18.28,ENG,228,0,0,0,,Benjamin! That is dangerous. Come back over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:20.75,CHT,229,0,0,0,,別動，小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:20.75,ENG,229,0,0,0,,Stay put, child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:25.06,CHT,230,0,0,0,,我非常愛她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:25.06,ENG,230,0,0,0,,I loved her very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:27.49,CHT,231,0,0,0,,她是我的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:27.49,ENG,231,0,0,0,,She was my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:28.75,CHT,232,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:28.75,ENG,232,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:30.59,CHT,233,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:30.59,ENG,233,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:35.16,CHT,234,0,0,0,,有時我覺得自己一天天地在改變
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:35.16,ENG,234,0,0,0,,Some days I feel different than the day before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.60,0:19:40.63,CHT,235,0,0,0,,每個人對於自己的感受都不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.60,0:19:40.63,ENG,235,0,0,0,,Everybody feels different about themselves, one way or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:43.91,CHT,236,0,0,0,,但是我們的終點是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:43.91,ENG,236,0,0,0,,But we're all going the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:48.94,CHT,237,0,0,0,,只是走的路不同罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:48.94,ENG,237,0,0,0,,Just taking different roads to get there, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:51.52,CHT,238,0,0,0,,你有你自己的道路，本傑明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:51.52,ENG,238,0,0,0,,You're on your own road, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:56.95,CHT,239,0,0,0,,媽媽？我還能活多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:56.95,ENG,239,0,0,0,,Mama? How much longer I got?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:20:00.76,CHT,240,0,0,0,,只要感謝上蒼賜予你的就行了，明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:20:00.76,ENG,240,0,0,0,,Just be thankful for what you're given, hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:03.92,CHT,241,0,0,0,,你已經多活了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:03.92,ENG,241,0,0,0,,You're already here longer than you're supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.83,0:20:09.73,CHT,242,0,0,0,,有些晚上，我得一個人睡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.83,0:20:09.73,ENG,242,0,0,0,,Some nights, I'd have to sleep alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:20.11,CHT,243,0,0,0,,我並不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:20.11,ENG,243,0,0,0,,I didn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.01,0:20:23.74,CHT,244,0,0,0,,我在聆聽這個房子的呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.01,0:20:23.74,ENG,244,0,0,0,,I would listen to the house breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:27.01,CHT,245,0,0,0,,聽著大家沉睡的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:27.01,ENG,245,0,0,0,,All those people sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.68,CHT,246,0,0,0,,我感到安心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.68,ENG,246,0,0,0,,I felt safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:54.14,CHT,247,0,0,0,,這裡的生活很有規律
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:54.14,ENG,247,0,0,0,,It was a place of great routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:57.15,CHT,248,0,0,0,,每天早上5:30，不管天氣如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:57.15,ENG,248,0,0,0,,Every morning at 5:30, no matter the weather,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.25,0:21:01.31,CHT,249,0,0,0,,美國退伍軍人溫斯洛將軍都會升旗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.25,0:21:01.31,ENG,249,0,0,0,,General Winslow, U.S. Army, Retired, would raise the flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:08.15,CHT,250,0,0,0,,曾經小有名氣的歌劇演員 西比爾·瓦格納夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:08.15,ENG,250,0,0,0,,Mrs. Sybil Wagner, once an opera singer of some note,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:10.89,CHT,251,0,0,0,,都會唱著瓦格納的歌劇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:10.89,ENG,251,0,0,0,,well, she sang Wagner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:24.14,CHT,252,0,0,0,,好了，孩子，過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:24.14,ENG,252,0,0,0,,All right, baby, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:28.08,CHT,253,0,0,0,,我們來給你這雙老腿增加點活力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:28.08,ENG,253,0,0,0,,We got to put some life into these old sticks for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:32.48,CHT,254,0,0,0,,讓你能走路，這樣就可以幫我忙 來，明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:32.48,ENG,254,0,0,0,,Get you walking so you can help me out around here. Come on now, hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:37.42,CHT,255,0,0,0,,一年四季，晚餐總是在5:30準時開始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:37.42,ENG,255,0,0,0,,No matter the season, supper was served promptly at 5:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:39.68,CHT,256,0,0,0,,（意思是糖漿，讀單詞中…）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:39.68,ENG,256,0,0,0,,Mo-lasses Molasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.79,0:21:41.02,ENG,257,0,0,0,,Molasses Molasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.26,0:21:43.82,ENG,258,0,0,0,,Molasses Molasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:47.32,CHT,259,0,0,0,,我五歲開始學著讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:47.32,ENG,259,0,0,0,,I learned to read when I was five.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:51.84,CHT,260,0,0,0,,我祖父曾是一個著名演員的化妝師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:51.84,ENG,260,0,0,0,,My grandfather was a dresser for a famous actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:54.63,CHT,261,0,0,0,,他會把每本劇本都帶回來給我看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:54.63,ENG,261,0,0,0,,He brung home every play for me to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:22:00.61,CHT,262,0,0,0,,“看守我這衰弱的老頭子的好人們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:22:00.61,ENG,262,0,0,0,,"Kind keepers of my weak decaying age,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:05.14,CHT,263,0,0,0,,“讓垂死的摩提默在這兒歇一歇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:05.14,ENG,263,0,0,0,,"Let dying Mortimer here rest himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:08.65,CHT,264,0,0,0,,“我由於長期監禁，肢體痛楚不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:08.65,ENG,264,0,0,0,,"Even like a man new haled from the rack,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.75,0:22:11.45,CHT,265,0,0,0,,“好像剛從刑架上拖下來的人一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.75,0:22:11.45,ENG,265,0,0,0,,"So fare my limbs with long imprisonment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.19,0:22:15.82,CHT,266,0,0,0,,“我這滿頭白髮 是在苦難的歲月中折磨出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.19,0:22:15.82,ENG,266,0,0,0,,"And these gray locks, the pursuivants of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:19.43,CHT,267,0,0,0,,“它預示著摩提默的死期不遠了”
