Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:38.88,CHT,272,0,0,0,,世事難料
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:38.88,ENG,272,0,0,0,,You never know what's coming for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.59,0:22:43.18,CHT,273,0,0,0,,週六晚上，媽媽會帶我去教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.59,0:22:43.18,ENG,273,0,0,0,,On Saturday nights, Mama would make me go to church.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:48.36,CHT,274,0,0,0,,本傑明！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:48.36,ENG,274,0,0,0,,Benjamin!
