Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.88,0:23:05.21,CHT,276,0,0,0,,有什麼需要幫忙的嗎，女士？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.88,0:23:05.21,ENG,276,0,0,0,,What can I do for you, sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.05,0:23:20.52,CHT,277,0,0,0,,她的內部器官有問題，無法生育
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.05,0:23:20.52,ENG,277,0,0,0,,Her parts are all twisted up inside and she can't have little children.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.33,0:23:28.36,CHT,278,0,0,0,,主啊，如果您能寬恕這個女人的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.33,0:23:28.36,ENG,278,0,0,0,,Lord, if you could see clear to forgive this woman her sins
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.47,0:23:30.56,CHT,279,0,0,0,,就讓她孕育胎兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.47,0:23:30.56,ENG,279,0,0,0,,so she can bear the fruit of the womb.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.67,0:23:33.07,CHT,280,0,0,0,,出來吧，該死的苦難！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.67,0:23:33.07,ENG,280,0,0,0,,Out, damnable affliction!
