Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.17,0:23:35.33,ENG,281,0,0,0,,- Praise God! - Praise God!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.44,0:23:36.60,CHT,282,0,0,0,,哈利路亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.44,0:23:36.60,ENG,282,0,0,0,,Hallelujah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.71,0:23:38.18,CHT,283,0,0,0,,- 哈利路亞！ - 哈利路亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.71,0:23:38.18,ENG,283,0,0,0,,- Hallelujah! - Hallelujah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.25,0:23:42.98,CHT,284,0,0,0,,這位老人又有什麼苦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.25,0:23:42.98,ENG,284,0,0,0,,And what's this old man's irrediction?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.68,0:23:46.12,CHT,285,0,0,0,,魔鬼纏上了他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.68,0:23:46.12,ENG,285,0,0,0,,He's got the Devil on his back,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.22,0:23:49.48,CHT,286,0,0,0,,想要提早把他趕進墳墓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.22,0:23:49.48,ENG,286,0,0,0,,trying to ride him into the grave before his time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.79,0:23:54.23,CHT,287,0,0,0,,- 出來吧，魔鬼！ - 是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.79,0:23:54.23,ENG,287,0,0,0,,- Out, Zebuchar! - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.33,0:23:56.16,CHT,288,0,0,0,,- 出來吧，魔鬼！ - 是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.33,0:23:56.16,ENG,288,0,0,0,,- Out, Beelzebub! - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.06,0:23:59.79,CHT,289,0,0,0,,你多大了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.06,0:23:59.79,ENG,289,0,0,0,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.90,0:24:02.39,CHT,290,0,0,0,,七歲，可我看起來要老得多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.90,0:24:02.39,ENG,290,0,0,0,,Seven. But I look a lot older.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.47,0:24:04.96,CHT,291,0,0,0,,上帝保佑你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.47,0:24:04.96,ENG,291,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.57,0:24:07.04,CHT,292,0,0,0,,他只有七歲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.57,0:24:07.04,ENG,292,0,0,0,,He's seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.84,0:24:13.78,CHT,293,0,0,0,,這是一個樂觀向上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.84,0:24:13.78,ENG,293,0,0,0,,Now, this is a man with optimism in his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.88,0:24:15.57,CHT,294,0,0,0,,- 是的 - 靈魂有所信仰！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.88,0:24:15.57,ENG,294,0,0,0,,- All right. - Belief in his soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.68,0:24:16.67,CHT,295,0,0,0,,- 是的！ - 是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.68,0:24:16.67,ENG,295,0,0,0,,- Yes! - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.78,0:24:18.58,CHT,296,0,0,0,,上帝的眼中我們都是孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.78,0:24:18.58,ENG,296,0,0,0,,We are all children in the eyes of God!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.68,0:24:19.98,CHT,297,0,0,0,,- 是的！ - 哈利路亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.68,0:24:19.98,ENG,297,0,0,0,,- Yes! - Hallelujah!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.09,0:24:22.95,CHT,298,0,0,0,,我們得幫你擺脫那個輪椅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.09,0:24:22.95,ENG,298,0,0,0,,We are gonna get you out of that chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.06,0:24:25.08,CHT,299,0,0,0,,- 讓你能走路 - 阿門
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.06,0:24:25.08,ENG,299,0,0,0,,- And we're gonna have you walk. - Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.96,0:24:27.52,CHT,300,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.96,0:24:27.52,ENG,300,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.46,0:24:30.66,CHT,301,0,0,0,,以上帝的名義…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.46,0:24:30.66,ENG,301,0,0,0,,In the name of God's glory...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.53,0:24:32.96,CHT,302,0,0,0,,站起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.53,0:24:32.96,ENG,302,0,0,0,,Rise up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.47,0:24:35.83,CHT,303,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.47,0:24:35.83,ENG,303,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.67,0:24:39.43,CHT,304,0,0,0,,加油，走起來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.67,0:24:39.43,ENG,304,0,0,0,,Come on. Walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.54,0:24:40.97,CHT,305,0,0,0,,加油，孩子，加油
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.54,0:24:40.97,ENG,305,0,0,0,,Come on, son. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.07,0:24:43.80,CHT,306,0,0,0,,- 用力，孩子，加把勁 - 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.07,0:24:43.80,ENG,306,0,0,0,,- Come on with it, son. Come on. - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.91,0:24:47.28,CHT,307,0,0,0,,上帝會一路看著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.91,0:24:47.28,ENG,307,0,0,0,,Now God is gonna see you the rest of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.38,0:24:52.18,CHT,308,0,0,0,,上帝會看著這個小老人 不靠拐杖輪椅，一路走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.38,0:24:52.18,ENG,308,0,0,0,,He's gonna see this little old man walk without the use of a crutch or a cane.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.28,0:24:54.08,CHT,309,0,0,0,,上帝會看著你…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.28,0:24:54.08,ENG,309,0,0,0,,He's gonna see that you walk from faith...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.19,0:24:57.16,CHT,310,0,0,0,,- 哈利路亞！ - 靠著信仰和保佑一個人走下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.19,0:24:57.16,ENG,310,0,0,0,,- Hallelujah! ...and divine inspiration alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.26,0:24:58.42,CHT,311,0,0,0,,- 是的 - 嗨，本！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.26,0:24:58.42,ENG,311,0,0,0,,- Yes. - Hey, Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.52,0:24:59.82,CHT,312,0,0,0,,- 去吧，孩子！ - 走走看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.52,0:24:59.82,ENG,312,0,0,0,,- Go, son! - Now walk.
