Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.93,0:25:01.15,ENG,313,0,0,0,,- Yes. - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.30,0:25:04.92,CHT,314,0,0,0,,別碰他
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.30,0:25:04.92,ENG,314,0,0,0,,Don't touch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.30,0:25:09.03,CHT,315,0,0,0,,站起來，老傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.30,0:25:09.03,ENG,315,0,0,0,,Rise up, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.10,0:25:12.66,CHT,316,0,0,0,,像拉撒路那樣站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.10,0:25:12.66,ENG,316,0,0,0,,Rise up like Lazarus.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.77,0:25:14.90,CHT,317,0,0,0,,給我站起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.77,0:25:14.90,ENG,317,0,0,0,,I said, rise up!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.57,0:25:16.94,CHT,318,0,0,0,,哈利路亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.57,0:25:16.94,ENG,318,0,0,0,,Hallelujah!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.11,0:25:20.31,CHT,319,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.11,0:25:20.31,ENG,319,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.78,0:25:21.97,CHT,320,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.78,0:25:21.97,ENG,320,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.08,0:25:23.07,CHT,321,0,0,0,,說哈利路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.08,0:25:23.07,ENG,321,0,0,0,,Say hallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.18,0:25:24.55,CHT,322,0,0,0,,- 哈利路亞！ - 哈利路亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.18,0:25:24.55,ENG,322,0,0,0,,- Hallelujah! - Hallelujah!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.29,0:25:27.48,CHT,323,0,0,0,,走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.29,0:25:27.48,ENG,323,0,0,0,,Walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.29,0:25:30.35,CHT,324,0,0,0,,繼續走，對
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.29,0:25:30.35,ENG,324,0,0,0,,Walk on. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.23,0:25:35.25,CHT,325,0,0,0,,就是這樣，本傑明
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.23,0:25:35.25,ENG,325,0,0,0,,That's right, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.36,0:25:38.59,CHT,326,0,0,0,,每當我回想起這些，還是覺得是個奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.36,0:25:38.59,ENG,326,0,0,0,,Now when I look back on it, it was miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.70,0:25:42.72,CHT,327,0,0,0,,有句話這麼說的，有得必有失
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.70,0:25:42.72,ENG,327,0,0,0,,But you know the saying, the Lord giveth and the Lord taketh away.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.00,0:25:44.87,CHT,328,0,0,0,,讚美主啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.00,0:25:44.87,ENG,328,0,0,0,,Glory in the highest!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.97,0:25:50.13,CHT,329,0,0,0,,上帝啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.97,0:25:50.13,ENG,329,0,0,0,,Sweet Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.28,0:25:51.37,CHT,330,0,0,0,,- 不！ - 不！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.28,0:25:51.37,ENG,330,0,0,0,,- No! - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.85,0:25:55.18,CHT,331,0,0,0,,這有很多人過生日
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.85,0:25:55.18,ENG,331,0,0,0,,There were so many birthdays.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.28,0:25:58.81,CHT,332,0,0,0,,他真是個快樂的好人 他真是個快樂的好人…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.28,0:25:58.81,ENG,332,0,0,0,,For he's a jolly good fellow For he's a jolly good fellow...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.92,0:26:01.51,CHT,333,0,0,0,,我們一般不出門，我們會省著用蠟燭
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.92,0:26:01.51,ENG,333,0,0,0,,So we wouldn't run out, we would spare the candles.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.62,0:26:05.65,CHT,334,0,0,0,,奎尼，你知道我不喜歡生日 也不喜歡蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.62,0:26:05.65,ENG,334,0,0,0,,Queenie, you know I don't like birthdays and I don't like cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.36,0:26:10.29,CHT,335,0,0,0,,死亡也是這裡的常客 人們來到這裡，又安靜離去
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.36,0:26:10.29,ENG,335,0,0,0,,And death was a common visitor. People came and went.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.13,0:26:14.53,CHT,336,0,0,0,,你可以感覺到有人離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.13,0:26:14.53,ENG,336,0,0,0,,You always knew when someone left us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.63,0:26:17.12,CHT,337,0,0,0,,那時房子裡總是寂靜無聲
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.63,0:26:17.12,ENG,337,0,0,0,,There was a silence in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.22,0:26:33.48,CHT,338,0,0,0,,這是個值得成長的美好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.22,0:26:33.48,ENG,338,0,0,0,,It was a wonderful place to grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.59,0:26:38.05,CHT,339,0,0,0,,在這個地方 人們拋開了過往生活中的矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.59,0:26:38.05,ENG,339,0,0,0,,I was with people who had shed all the inconsequences of earlier life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.76,0:26:42.85,CHT,340,0,0,0,,每天只關心天氣，洗澡水溫度
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.76,0:26:42.85,ENG,340,0,0,0,,Left wondering about the weather, the temperature of a bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.10,0:26:46.29,CHT,341,0,0,0,,一天行將結束時的陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.10,0:26:46.29,ENG,341,0,0,0,,the light at the end of a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.70,0:26:54.66,CHT,342,0,0,0,,總會有人來重新填補死者的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.70,0:26:54.66,ENG,342,0,0,0,,For everyone that died, someone would come to take their place.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.74,0:26:58.01,CHT,343,0,0,0,,我結過5次婚
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.74,0:26:58.01,ENG,343,0,0,0,,I've been married five times.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.54,0:27:02.24,CHT,344,0,0,0,,我和我的第五任妻子 被臨近的食人部落抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.54,0:27:02.24,ENG,344,0,0,0,,My fifth wife and I are captured by a neighbor tribe of cannibals.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.35,0:27:03.41,CHT,345,0,0,0,,哦，天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.35,0:27:03.41,ENG,345,0,0,0,,Oh, goodness gracious.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.52,0:27:04.98,CHT,346,0,0,0,,我們從河裡逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.52,0:27:04.98,ENG,346,0,0,0,,We escaped across the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.08,0:27:08.45,CHT,347,0,0,0,,我的妻子不會游泳，所以很不幸被吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.08,0:27:08.45,ENG,347,0,0,0,,My wife, she can't swim, so, sadly, she eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.55,0:27:09.75,CHT,348,0,0,0,,哦，天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.55,0:27:09.75,ENG,348,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.86,0:27:12.69,CHT,349,0,0,0,,我的第二任妻子踩到了眼鏡蛇，就這麼死了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.86,0:27:12.69,ENG,349,0,0,0,,My second wife steps on cobra and dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.26,0:27:16.02,CHT,350,0,0,0,,嫁給我真是很不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.26,0:27:16.02,ENG,350,0,0,0,,It was very bad luck to be married to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.13,0:27:19.15,CHT,351,0,0,0,,那是歐緹先生，他是我一個熟人的熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.13,0:27:19.15,ENG,351,0,0,0,,That's Mr. Oti. He's an acquaintance of an acquaintance of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.27,0:27:21.36,CHT,352,0,0,0,,- 第二年夏天我被… - 他是個矮人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.27,0:27:21.36,ENG,352,0,0,0,,- The next summer I'm captured... - He's a Pygmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.47,0:27:23.33,CHT,353,0,0,0,,…巴希勒部落的人抓了，還有其他三個人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.47,0:27:23.33,ENG,353,0,0,0,,...with three others by the Baschiele tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.44,0:27:28.30,CHT,354,0,0,0,,他們用我們跟一個奇怪的美國人 換了豬，鞋子和啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.44,0:27:28.30,ENG,354,0,0,0,,They trade us for pigs, shoes, and beer to a very strange American man.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.43,0:27:49.92,CHT,355,0,0,0,,聽說你並不像看起來那麼老
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.43,0:27:49.92,ENG,355,0,0,0,,I hear you're not so old as you're looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.03,0:27:52.26,CHT,356,0,0,0,,大家都被你耍了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.03,0:27:52.26,ENG,356,0,0,0,,You just fooling everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.83,0:27:55.86,CHT,357,0,0,0,,怎麼了？你有馬甲本嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.83,0:27:55.86,ENG,357,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Did you get Madjembe?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.97,0:27:57.33,CHT,358,0,0,0,,什麼是馬甲本？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.97,0:27:57.33,ENG,358,0,0,0,,What's Madjembe?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.44,0:27:58.73,CHT,359,0,0,0,,蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.44,0:27:58.73,ENG,359,0,0,0,,Worms.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.14,0:28:01.40,CHT,360,0,0,0,,我身上沒蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.14,0:28:01.40,ENG,360,0,0,0,,I don't think I have worms.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.07,0:28:03.60,CHT,361,0,0,0,,我就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.07,0:28:03.60,ENG,361,0,0,0,,This is just how I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.71,0:28:06.58,CHT,362,0,0,0,,- 今天吃藥了嗎？ - 沒有，夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.71,0:28:06.58,ENG,362,0,0,0,,- Did you take your pills today? - No, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.68,0:28:09.01,CHT,363,0,0,0,,來，喝點冰汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.68,0:28:09.01,ENG,363,0,0,0,,Come. Let's get a cold root beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.11,0:28:11.24,CHT,364,0,0,0,,我在枕頭下找到了藥片
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.11,0:28:11.24,ENG,364,0,0,0,,I found the medication under your pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.35,0:28:14.51,CHT,365,0,0,0,,我不該去，太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.35,0:28:14.51,ENG,365,0,0,0,,I'm not supposed to. It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.62,0:28:17.35,CHT,366,0,0,0,,誰說的？來，小傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.62,0:28:17.35,ENG,366,0,0,0,,Who said that? Come on, little man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.66,0:28:20.32,CHT,367,0,0,0,,孩子們好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.66,0:28:20.32,ENG,367,0,0,0,,Hello, children.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.57,0:28:33.06,CHT,368,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.57,0:28:33.06,ENG,368,0,0,0,,Hold, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.74,0:28:40.04,CHT,369,0,0,0,,我和費城動物園的猴子關在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.74,0:28:40.04,ENG,369,0,0,0,,Then I'm in the monkey house at Philadelphia Zoological Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.95,0:28:44.44,CHT,370,0,0,0,,第一天就有3000人來
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.95,0:28:44.44,ENG,370,0,0,0,,Three thousand people show up my first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.78,0:28:46.77,CHT,371,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.78,0:28:46.77,ENG,371,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.59,0:28:50.49,CHT,372,0,0,0,,住籠子裡是什麼感覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.59,0:28:50.49,ENG,372,0,0,0,,What's it like living in a cage?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.59,0:28:52.06,CHT,373,0,0,0,,臭死了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.59,0:28:52.06,ENG,373,0,0,0,,It stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.69,0:28:54.96,CHT,374,0,0,0,,可是有猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.69,0:28:54.96,ENG,374,0,0,0,,But the monkeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.76,0:28:57.79,CHT,375,0,0,0,,他們會表演戲法
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.76,0:28:57.79,ENG,375,0,0,0,,They do some tricks there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.03,0:29:00.73,CHT,376,0,0,0,,我扔矛，和科瓦利打架
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.03,0:29:00.73,ENG,376,0,0,0,,I throw a spear, wrestle with Kowali.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.57,0:29:03.30,CHT,377,0,0,0,,她是只母猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.57,0:29:03.30,ENG,377,0,0,0,,She is orangutan.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.74,0:29:07.26,CHT,378,0,0,0,,不和猴子玩的時候，他們就把我趕回籠子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.74,0:29:07.26,ENG,378,0,0,0,,When I'm not playing with the monkeys, they want me to run to the bars
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.37,0:29:09.47,CHT,379,0,0,0,,讓我咬來咬去
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.37,0:29:09.47,ENG,379,0,0,0,,in my cage, with my teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.42,0:29:21.48,CHT,380,0,0,0,,之後呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.42,0:29:21.48,ENG,380,0,0,0,,So then what'd you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.59,0:29:27.42,CHT,381,0,0,0,,後來我離開了動物園，這兒走走 那兒走走，四處遊蕩
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.59,0:29:27.42,ENG,381,0,0,0,,Then I leave zoo, go here, go there. Wandered most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.89,0:29:28.92,CHT,382,0,0,0,,獨自一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.89,0:29:28.92,ENG,382,0,0,0,,You were all alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.03,0:29:31.33,CHT,383,0,0,0,,大多數時候都是一個人的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.03,0:29:31.33,ENG,383,0,0,0,,Plenty of time you'll be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.43,0:29:34.87,CHT,384,0,0,0,,像我們這樣的異類，就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.43,0:29:34.87,ENG,384,0,0,0,,When you're different like us, it's gonna be that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.90,0:29:39.73,CHT,385,0,0,0,,告訴你個小秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.90,0:29:39.73,ENG,385,0,0,0,,But I'll tell you a little secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.84,0:29:43.14,CHT,386,0,0,0,,無論什麼膚色，什麼體型
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.84,0:29:43.14,ENG,386,0,0,0,,Fat people, skinny people, tall people,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.24,0:29:46.23,CHT,387,0,0,0,,人都是孤獨的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.24,0:29:46.23,ENG,387,0,0,0,,white people, they're just as alone as we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.78,0:29:48.97,CHT,388,0,0,0,,但可怕的不是孤獨，而是懼怕孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.78,0:29:48.97,ENG,388,0,0,0,,But they're scared shitless.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.19,0:29:57.82,CHT,389,0,0,0,,我想起了伴我長大的那條河
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.19,0:29:57.82,ENG,389,0,0,0,,I think about the river I grew up on.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.29,0:30:01.19,CHT,390,0,0,0,,再次坐在河邊感覺一定很妙
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.29,0:30:01.19,ENG,390,0,0,0,,It would be nice to sit by my river again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.46,0:30:05.83,CHT,391,0,0,0,,走吧，我約了人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.46,0:30:05.83,ENG,391,0,0,0,,Come, I have an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.23,0:30:10.79,CHT,392,0,0,0,,我的小傢伙來了，準備好了嗎，寶貝？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.23,0:30:10.79,ENG,392,0,0,0,,There's my little man. You ready, sugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.90,0:30:13.24,CHT,393,0,0,0,,時刻準備著，時刻準備著
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.90,0:30:13.24,ENG,393,0,0,0,,Always ready. Always ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.04,0:30:17.13,CHT,394,0,0,0,,菲拉門娜，本傑明先生
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.04,0:30:17.13,ENG,394,0,0,0,,Filamena, Mr. Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.18,0:30:21.24,CHT,395,0,0,0,,- 很高興見到你，先生 - 我的榮幸，夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.18,0:30:21.24,ENG,395,0,0,0,,- It's a pleasure to meet you, sir. - My pleasure, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.35,0:30:23.31,CHT,396,0,0,0,,你認得路回家，對嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.35,0:30:23.31,ENG,396,0,0,0,,You can find your own way home, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.42,0:30:26.15,CHT,397,0,0,0,,乘聖查理斯線到拿破崙路
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.42,0:30:26.15,ENG,397,0,0,0,,Take the St. Charles line to Napoleon.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.16,0:30:33.75,CHT,398,0,0,0,,嘿！嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.16,0:30:33.75,ENG,398,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.08,0:30:57.57,CHT,399,0,0,0,,你到底去哪了？進來
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.08,0:30:57.57,ENG,399,0,0,0,,Where in God's name have you been? Get in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.08,0:31:02.35,CHT,400,0,0,0,,我急死了，知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.08,0:31:02.35,ENG,400,0,0,0,,I mean, you take my breath away, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.76,0:31:05.35,CHT,401,0,0,0,,哦，天啊，我擔心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.76,0:31:05.35,ENG,401,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord, I was so worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.06,0:31:11.62,CHT,402,0,0,0,,這是我過得最開心的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.06,0:31:11.62,ENG,402,0,0,0,,It had been the best day of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.56,0:31:15.26,CHT,403,0,0,0,,- 她的呼吸情況如何？ - 很微弱
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.56,0:31:15.26,ENG,403,0,0,0,,- How's her breathing? - It's shallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.37,0:31:16.89,CHT,404,0,0,0,,他們幾小時後會到
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.37,0:31:16.89,ENG,404,0,0,0,,They say it'll reach us in a few hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.00,0:31:19.90,CHT,405,0,0,0,,所以我得把我孩子帶到姐姐那去
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.00,0:31:19.90,ENG,405,0,0,0,,so I gotta get my baby and take him to my sister's.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.01,0:31:22.47,CHT,406,0,0,0,,他們說醫院裡沒什麼好擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.01,0:31:22.47,ENG,406,0,0,0,,They say there's nothing to worry about here in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.57,0:31:25.07,CHT,407,0,0,0,,若需要，護士會馬上過來，你還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.57,0:31:25.07,ENG,407,0,0,0,,Nurses'll be right here if you need them. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.18,0:31:28.91,CHT,408,0,0,0,,- 沒事，我可以讀書 - 一小時內我就會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.18,0:31:28.91,ENG,408,0,0,0,,- Yeah, I'm okay reading. - I shouldn't be more than an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.32,0:31:32.94,CHT,409,0,0,0,,有人來陪了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.32,0:31:32.94,ENG,409,0,0,0,,Was there just company?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.52,0:31:35.92,CHT,410,0,0,0,,是桃樂茜要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.52,0:31:35.92,ENG,410,0,0,0,,It was just Dorothy leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.09,0:31:39.52,CHT,411,0,0,0,,繼續，卡洛琳
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.09,0:31:39.52,ENG,411,0,0,0,,Go on, Caroline.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.63,0:31:42.72,CHT,412,0,0,0,,“星期天，所有的家人都會來”
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.63,0:31:42.72,ENG,412,0,0,0,,"On Sundays, the families would come and visit."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.13,0:31:46.06,CHT,413,0,0,0,,那是1930年的感恩節
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.13,0:31:46.06,ENG,413,0,0,0,,It was Thanksgiving, 1930.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.17,0:31:49.13,CHT,414,0,0,0,,我遇見了那個改變我一生的人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.17,0:31:49.13,ENG,414,0,0,0,,I met the person who changed my life forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.21,0:32:03.27,CHT,415,0,0,0,,本傑明
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.21,0:32:03.27,ENG,415,0,0,0,,Well, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.72,0:32:07.01,CHT,416,0,0,0,,你看上去真是出奇地年輕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.72,0:32:07.01,ENG,416,0,0,0,,Might I say you are looking strikingly youthful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.49,0:32:09.04,CHT,417,0,0,0,,你好，富勒太太
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.49,0:32:09.04,ENG,417,0,0,0,,Good day, Mrs. Fuller.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.15,0:32:12.42,CHT,418,0,0,0,,一根拐杖，背也直了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.15,0:32:12.42,ENG,418,0,0,0,,A single cane, back straight as an arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.52,0:32:14.89,CHT,419,0,0,0,,你吃了什麼靈丹妙藥？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.52,0:32:14.89,ENG,419,0,0,0,,What elixir have you been drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.99,0:32:18.36,CHT,420,0,0,0,,- 謝謝，夫人 - 奶奶！看看我！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.99,0:32:18.36,ENG,420,0,0,0,,- Thank you, ma'am. - Grandma! Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.80,0:32:23.13,CHT,421,0,0,0,,真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.80,0:32:23.13,ENG,421,0,0,0,,That was really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.24,0:32:25.10,CHT,422,0,0,0,,快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.24,0:32:25.10,ENG,422,0,0,0,,Come on over here, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.24,0:32:28.04,CHT,423,0,0,0,,這是我孫女，黛西
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.24,0:32:28.04,ENG,423,0,0,0,,Now, this is my granddaughter, Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.97,0:32:30.81,CHT,424,0,0,0,,這位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.97,0:32:30.81,ENG,424,0,0,0,,This is Mr...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.94,0:32:34.61,CHT,425,0,0,0,,不好意思，本傑明，我還不知道你姓什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.94,0:32:34.61,ENG,425,0,0,0,,I'm afraid, Benjamin, I don't rightly know your last name.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.71,0:32:36.34,CHT,426,0,0,0,,叫我本傑明就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.71,0:32:36.34,ENG,426,0,0,0,,Benjamin's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.98,0:32:39.31,CHT,427,0,0,0,,我永遠忘不了她那雙藍眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.98,0:32:39.31,ENG,427,0,0,0,,I never forgot her blue eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.75,0:32:42.41,CHT,428,0,0,0,,各位，晚餐準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.75,0:32:42.41,ENG,428,0,0,0,,Good people, supper is served.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.52,0:32:48.62,CHT,429,0,0,0,,為了健康和食物，為了愛和友誼 為了上帝賜予的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.52,0:32:48.62,ENG,429,0,0,0,,Health and food, for love and friends. For everything thy goodness sends.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.06,0:32:50.22,CHT,430,0,0,0,,阿門
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.06,0:32:50.22,ENG,430,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.33,0:32:51.56,CHT,431,0,0,0,,- 阿門！ - 阿門！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.33,0:32:51.56,ENG,431,0,0,0,,- Amen! - Amen!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.27,0:32:57.83,CHT,432,0,0,0,,你們知道火雞並不是鳥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.27,0:32:57.83,ENG,432,0,0,0,,Did you know turkeys aren't really birds?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.94,0:32:58.96,CHT,433,0,0,0,,怎麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.94,0:32:58.96,ENG,433,0,0,0,,Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.07,0:33:02.20,CHT,434,0,0,0,,他們屬於雉科，基本不會飛
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.07,0:33:02.20,ENG,434,0,0,0,,They're in the pheasant family, can't hardly fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.31,0:33:04.83,CHT,435,0,0,0,,不覺得這很可憐嗎？不會飛的鳥？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.31,0:33:04.83,ENG,435,0,0,0,,It's sad, don't you think? Birds that can't fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.94,0:33:07.10,CHT,436,0,0,0,,我喜歡不會飛的鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.94,0:33:07.10,ENG,436,0,0,0,,I love birds that can't fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.21,0:33:09.20,CHT,437,0,0,0,,非常美味
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.21,0:33:09.20,ENG,437,0,0,0,,They are so delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.38,0:33:12.85,CHT,438,0,0,0,,- 你太壞了 - 在我們向主感謝恩賜之時
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.38,0:33:12.85,ENG,438,0,0,0,,- That's terrible. - I have something to tell y'all
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.95,0:33:16.11,CHT,439,0,0,0,,我有件事要宣佈
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.95,0:33:16.11,ENG,439,0,0,0,,while we're giving thanks for God's blessings.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.22,0:33:18.16,CHT,440,0,0,0,,奇跡在我身上發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.22,0:33:18.16,ENG,440,0,0,0,,I had a miracle happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.66,0:33:21.29,CHT,441,0,0,0,,主回應了我的祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.66,0:33:21.29,ENG,441,0,0,0,,The Lord saw fit to answer my prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.00,0:33:27.30,CHT,442,0,0,0,,什麼叫回應了她的祈禱？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.00,0:33:27.30,ENG,442,0,0,0,,What does she mean, answered her prayers?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.40,0:33:28.92,CHT,443,0,0,0,,謝謝，謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.40,0:33:28.92,ENG,443,0,0,0,,Thanks. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.03,0:33:31.40,CHT,444,0,0,0,,她有孩子了，傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.03,0:33:31.40,ENG,444,0,0,0,,She's gonna have a baby, silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.37,0:33:35.36,CHT,445,0,0,0,,我媽媽懷上弟弟的時候也這麼說過
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.37,0:33:35.36,ENG,445,0,0,0,,That's what my mama said when I was gonna have a baby brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.47,0:33:37.74,CHT,446,0,0,0,,可他沒活多久
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.47,0:33:37.74,ENG,446,0,0,0,,but he didn't live long,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.98,0:33:41.31,CHT,447,0,0,0,,因為他的呼吸有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.98,0:33:41.31,ENG,447,0,0,0,,'cause he didn't breathe right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.18,0:33:48.18,CHT,448,0,0,0,,“下午他長出了漂亮的後腿 （選自吉卜林創作的兒童作品故事集中的老袋鼠之歌）
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.18,0:33:48.18,ENG,448,0,0,0,,"In the afternoon, when he had got his beautiful hind legs
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.29,0:33:51.88,CHT,449,0,0,0,,“就如大神農答應過的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.29,0:33:51.88,ENG,449,0,0,0,,"just as Big God Nqong had promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.76,0:33:54.95,CHT,450,0,0,0,,“時間正好是5點
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.76,0:33:54.95,ENG,450,0,0,0,,"You can see that it is 5:00,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.06,0:33:59.02,CHT,451,0,0,0,,“大神農的鐘上就是這樣”
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.06,0:33:59.02,ENG,451,0,0,0,,"because Big God Nqong's clock says so."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.13,0:34:00.96,CHT,452,0,0,0,,很神奇吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.13,0:34:00.96,ENG,452,0,0,0,,Isn't that something?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.53,0:34:02.90,CHT,453,0,0,0,,再講一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.53,0:34:02.90,ENG,453,0,0,0,,Again, read it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.00,0:34:05.30,CHT,454,0,0,0,,哦，再講一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.00,0:34:05.30,ENG,454,0,0,0,,Oh, read it again, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.40,0:34:08.70,CHT,455,0,0,0,,好吧，不過講完之後，你們必須去睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.40,0:34:08.70,ENG,455,0,0,0,,All right. But afterwards, you must go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.07,0:34:10.47,CHT,456,0,0,0,,我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.07,0:34:10.47,ENG,456,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.44,0:34:14.28,CHT,457,0,0,0,,“老袋鼠”
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.44,0:34:14.28,ENG,457,0,0,0,,"Old Man Kangaroo."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.58,0:34:20.24,CHT,458,0,0,0,,你睡著了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.58,0:34:20.24,ENG,458,0,0,0,,Are you sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.79,0:34:23.28,CHT,459,0,0,0,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.79,0:34:23.28,ENG,459,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.39,0:34:24.95,CHT,460,0,0,0,,是我，黛西
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.39,0:34:24.95,ENG,460,0,0,0,,It's me, Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.99,0:34:27.46,CHT,461,0,0,0,,哦，嗨！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.99,0:34:27.46,ENG,461,0,0,0,,Oh, hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.06,0:34:29.55,CHT,462,0,0,0,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.06,0:34:29.55,ENG,462,0,0,0,,'Kay, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.71,0:34:42.44,CHT,463,0,0,0,,我們去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.71,0:34:42.44,ENG,463,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.61,0:34:46.41,CHT,464,0,0,0,,來，到這下麵
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.61,0:34:46.41,ENG,464,0,0,0,,Come on. Under here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.95,0:34:57.39,CHT,465,0,0,0,,給，把這點上
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.95,0:34:57.39,ENG,465,0,0,0,,Here, you light it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.49,0:34:59.58,CHT,466,0,0,0,,我不該玩火柴
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.49,0:34:59.58,ENG,466,0,0,0,,I'm not supposed to play with matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.69,0:35:01.96,CHT,467,0,0,0,,別那麼膽小，快點
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.69,0:35:01.96,ENG,467,0,0,0,,Don't be a chicken. Light it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.07,0:35:16.01,CHT,468,0,0,0,,我跟你說個秘密，你也跟我說個
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.07,0:35:16.01,ENG,468,0,0,0,,I'll tell you a secret if you'll tell me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.11,0:35:17.54,CHT,469,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.11,0:35:17.54,ENG,469,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.64,0:35:20.98,CHT,470,0,0,0,,我看見我媽媽吻了一個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.64,0:35:20.98,ENG,470,0,0,0,,I saw my mama kissing another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.38,0:35:23.44,CHT,471,0,0,0,,她臉都紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.38,0:35:23.44,ENG,471,0,0,0,,Her face was red from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.72,0:35:27.21,CHT,472,0,0,0,,該你了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.72,0:35:27.21,ENG,472,0,0,0,,Your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.52,0:35:32.82,CHT,473,0,0,0,,我並沒有看上去那麼老
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.52,0:35:32.82,ENG,473,0,0,0,,I'm not as old as I look.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.92,0:35:34.48,CHT,474,0,0,0,,我也這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.92,0:35:34.48,ENG,474,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.46,0:35:38.90,CHT,475,0,0,0,,你不像個老人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.46,0:35:38.90,ENG,475,0,0,0,,You don't seem like an old person.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.56,0:35:41.73,CHT,476,0,0,0,,- 比如我奶奶那樣 - 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.56,0:35:41.73,ENG,476,0,0,0,,- Like my grandma. - I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.50,0:35:45.09,CHT,477,0,0,0,,你病了？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.50,0:35:45.09,ENG,477,0,0,0,,Are you sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.67,0:35:48.83,CHT,478,0,0,0,,我聽見媽媽和蒂奇私下聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.67,0:35:48.83,ENG,478,0,0,0,,Well, I heard Mama and Tizzy whispering.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.94,0:35:53.10,CHT,479,0,0,0,,他們說我活不久了，但或許又不是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.94,0:35:53.10,ENG,479,0,0,0,,They said I was gonna die soon, but maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.35,0:35:56.87,CHT,480,0,0,0,,你真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.35,0:35:56.87,ENG,480,0,0,0,,You're odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.65,0:36:00.52,CHT,481,0,0,0,,你和我見過的人不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.65,0:36:00.52,ENG,481,0,0,0,,You're different than anybody I've ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.69,0:36:05.85,CHT,482,0,0,0,,- 可以嗎？ - 當然
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.69,0:36:05.85,ENG,482,0,0,0,,- May I? - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.10,0:36:15.53,CHT,483,0,0,0,,你們在下面幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.10,0:36:15.53,ENG,483,0,0,0,,What are you doing under there?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.63,0:36:19.07,CHT,484,0,0,0,,快回床上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.63,0:36:19.07,ENG,484,0,0,0,,You come right out here and get back up to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.17,0:36:20.93,CHT,485,0,0,0,,都大半夜了！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.17,0:36:20.93,ENG,485,0,0,0,,It's after midnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.04,0:36:23.13,CHT,486,0,0,0,,不可以再一起玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.04,0:36:23.13,ENG,486,0,0,0,,You are not to be playing together.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.24,0:36:24.77,CHT,487,0,0,0,,是，夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.24,0:36:24.77,ENG,487,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.88,0:36:27.04,CHT,488,0,0,0,,快回床上去，小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.88,0:36:27.04,ENG,488,0,0,0,,Now you get back to bed, little lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.15,0:36:31.10,CHT,489,0,0,0,,你還太小，半夜不能一個人出來亂跑
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.15,0:36:31.10,ENG,489,0,0,0,,You're too young to be wandering around in the night on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.79,0:36:37.62,CHT,490,0,0,0,,還有你該為自己感到羞愧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.79,0:36:37.62,ENG,490,0,0,0,,And you ought to be ashamed of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.90,0:36:54.96,CHT,491,0,0,0,,你跟別的小孩不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.90,0:36:54.96,ENG,491,0,0,0,,You are a different child.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.74,0:36:56.83,CHT,492,0,0,0,,有著大人外表，卻還是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.74,0:36:56.83,ENG,492,0,0,0,,A man-child.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.94,0:37:01.40,CHT,493,0,0,0,,孩子，別人是不會明白你的不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.94,0:37:01.40,ENG,493,0,0,0,,And, baby, people aren't gonna understand just how different you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.72,0:37:09.88,CHT,494,0,0,0,,我怎麼了，媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.72,0:37:09.88,ENG,494,0,0,0,,What's wrong with me, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.82,0:37:12.59,CHT,495,0,0,0,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.82,0:37:12.59,ENG,495,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.76,0:37:16.99,CHT,496,0,0,0,,上帝也沒說，孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.76,0:37:16.99,ENG,496,0,0,0,,God hasn't said yet, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.43,0:37:24.93,CHT,497,0,0,0,,快回床上，好嗎？乖點
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.43,0:37:24.93,ENG,497,0,0,0,,Now go on to bed, hear? And behave yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.27,0:37:28.83,CHT,498,0,0,0,,去吧，別忘了祈禱，聽見了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.27,0:37:28.83,ENG,498,0,0,0,,Go on. Say your prayers, hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.65,0:37:44.71,CHT,499,0,0,0,,我跟你說過我曾被閃電擊過7次嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.65,0:37:44.71,ENG,499,0,0,0,,Did I ever tell you I've been struck by lightning seven times?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.06,0:37:49.96,CHT,500,0,0,0,,一次是在修屋頂
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.06,0:37:49.96,ENG,500,0,0,0,,Once when I was repairing a leak on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.07,0:37:57.30,CHT,501,0,0,0,,一次是在過馬路取信
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.07,0:37:57.30,ENG,501,0,0,0,,Once I was just crossing the road to get the mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.35,0:38:14.65,CHT,502,0,0,0,,我永遠忘不了她那雙…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.35,0:38:14.65,ENG,502,0,0,0,,I never forgot her...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.75,0:38:16.24,CHT,503,0,0,0,,“…藍眼睛”
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.75,0:38:16.24,ENG,503,0,0,0,,"...blue eyes."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.72,0:38:19.28,CHT,504,0,0,0,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.72,0:38:19.28,ENG,504,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.39,0:38:24.16,CHT,505,0,0,0,,這個本傑明是不是對你一見鍾情啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.39,0:38:24.16,ENG,505,0,0,0,,Did you get that this Benjamin loved you from the first time that he saw you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.43,0:38:27.86,CHT,506,0,0,0,,很少人會有這種經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.43,0:38:27.86,ENG,506,0,0,0,,Not many people experience that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.37,0:38:31.13,CHT,507,0,0,0,,要我繼續嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.37,0:38:31.13,ENG,507,0,0,0,,Want me to go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.14,0:38:35.13,CHT,508,0,0,0,,他劃掉了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.14,0:38:35.13,ENG,508,0,0,0,,He crosses something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.24,0:38:38.54,CHT,509,0,0,0,,那個孩子到來後，一切變得不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.24,0:38:38.54,ENG,509,0,0,0,,When that baby came, things were different.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.64,0:38:41.98,CHT,510,0,0,0,,你媽媽走了，你爸爸還在
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.64,0:38:41.98,ENG,510,0,0,0,,Your mama gone away And your daddy gonna stay
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.08,0:38:45.88,CHT,511,0,0,0,,孩子也在
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.08,0:38:45.88,ENG,511,0,0,0,,Didn't leave nobody but the baby
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.35,0:38:49.95,CHT,512,0,0,0,,有人出生，有人死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.35,0:38:49.95,ENG,512,0,0,0,,Babies were born, people died.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.86,0:38:53.69,CHT,513,0,0,0,,許多人進出過那所老房子
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.86,0:38:53.69,ENG,513,0,0,0,,A lot of folks been through that old house.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.66,0:38:58.89,CHT,514,0,0,0,,我是來道別的，我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.66,0:38:58.89,ENG,514,0,0,0,,I've come to say goodbye. I'm going away.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.00,0:39:00.26,CHT,515,0,0,0,,走？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.00,0:39:00.26,ENG,515,0,0,0,,Going?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.77,0:39:02.29,CHT,516,0,0,0,,去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.77,0:39:02.29,ENG,516,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.40,0:39:03.96,CHT,517,0,0,0,,還沒想好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.40,0:39:03.96,ENG,517,0,0,0,,I haven't figured that out yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.07,0:39:06.54,CHT,518,0,0,0,,不過我會給你寄明信片
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.07,0:39:06.54,ENG,518,0,0,0,,but I'll send you a postcard when I get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.64,0:39:09.40,CHT,519,0,0,0,,你的朋友怎麼辦，那個高個子的女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.64,0:39:09.40,ENG,519,0,0,0,,What about your friend, the tall lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.51,0:39:10.91,CHT,520,0,0,0,,我們已經不是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.51,0:39:10.91,ENG,520,0,0,0,,We are not friends anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.01,0:39:14.27,CHT,521,0,0,0,,高個子的人有時就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.01,0:39:14.27,ENG,521,0,0,0,,That's what happens with tall people sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.38,0:39:17.14,CHT,522,0,0,0,,好吧，再見
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.38,0:39:17.14,ENG,522,0,0,0,,Well, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.43,0:39:39.20,CHT,523,0,0,0,,那年我就是一個人這麼過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.43,0:39:39.20,ENG,523,0,0,0,,Spent a lot of time by myself that year.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.57,0:39:41.80,CHT,524,0,0,0,,有人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.57,0:39:41.80,ENG,524,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.58,0:39:45.34,CHT,525,0,0,0,,- 你好 - 我今天剛搬來
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.58,0:39:45.34,ENG,525,0,0,0,,- Hi. - I'm moving in today.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.44,0:39:48.28,CHT,526,0,0,0,,歡迎，我們等你很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.44,0:39:48.28,ENG,526,0,0,0,,Welcome. We've been expecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.38,0:39:51.41,CHT,527,0,0,0,,你能帶她去盧梭太太住過的那間嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.38,0:39:51.41,ENG,527,0,0,0,,Can you please show her up to Mrs. Rousseau's old room?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.52,0:39:54.85,CHT,528,0,0,0,,抱歉，我們這裡是不許養狗的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.52,0:39:54.85,ENG,528,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but we usually don't allow dogs in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.95,0:39:57.95,CHT,529,0,0,0,,她已經很老了，都快瞎了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.95,0:39:57.95,ENG,529,0,0,0,,Well, she's old as the hills. She's almost blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.06,0:40:00.99,CHT,530,0,0,0,,不會麻煩你們很久
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.06,0:40:00.99,ENG,530,0,0,0,,She won't be a bother much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.09,0:40:04.79,CHT,531,0,0,0,,好吧，只要不礙事待多久都行
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.09,0:40:04.79,ENG,531,0,0,0,,Well, all right, long as she stays from up underfoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.90,0:40:06.09,CHT,532,0,0,0,,這邊，夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.90,0:40:06.09,ENG,532,0,0,0,,Right this way, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.20,0:40:09.33,CHT,533,0,0,0,,我想了很久也沒想起她叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.20,0:40:09.33,ENG,533,0,0,0,,As hard as I try, I can't remember her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.43,0:40:12.56,CHT,534,0,0,0,,勞森太太還是哈特福德太太
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.43,0:40:12.56,ENG,534,0,0,0,,Mrs. Lawson, or Mrs. Hartford.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.61,0:40:15.37,CHT,535,0,0,0,,也許是梅普爾太太
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.61,0:40:15.37,ENG,535,0,0,0,,Maybe it was Maple.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.47,0:40:17.81,CHT,536,0,0,0,,很有意思，有時候我們最記不得的人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.47,0:40:17.81,ENG,536,0,0,0,,It's funny how sometimes the people we remember the least
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.91,0:40:20.43,CHT,537,0,0,0,,卻印象最深
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.91,0:40:20.43,ENG,537,0,0,0,,make the greatest impression on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.05,0:40:23.38,CHT,538,0,0,0,,我清楚記得她戴著鑽戒
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.05,0:40:23.38,ENG,538,0,0,0,,I do remember she wore diamonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.48,0:40:27.28,CHT,539,0,0,0,,總是穿得很漂亮，像要出門一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.48,0:40:27.28,ENG,539,0,0,0,,And she always dressed in fine clothing, as if she was going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.39,0:40:30.95,CHT,540,0,0,0,,但她從沒出過門，也沒人來看她
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.39,0:40:30.95,ENG,540,0,0,0,,Although she never did and nobody ever came to visit her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.69,0:40:35.02,CHT,541,0,0,0,,她教我彈鋼琴
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.69,0:40:35.02,ENG,541,0,0,0,,She taught me to play the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.40,0:40:43.03,CHT,542,0,0,0,,無所謂你彈奏得怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.40,0:40:43.03,ENG,542,0,0,0,,It's not about how well you play.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.77,0:40:46.60,CHT,543,0,0,0,,重要的是你彈琴時的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.77,0:40:46.60,ENG,543,0,0,0,,It's how you feel about what you're playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.71,0:40:48.04,CHT,544,0,0,0,,試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.71,0:40:48.04,ENG,544,0,0,0,,Try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.39,0:41:07.62,CHT,545,0,0,0,,情不自禁沉浸於音樂中
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.39,0:41:07.62,ENG,545,0,0,0,,You can't help putting yourself in the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.70,0:41:17.69,CHT,546,0,0,0,,變化是無窮的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.70,0:41:17.69,ENG,546,0,0,0,,There were many changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.80,0:41:20.86,CHT,547,0,0,0,,有些看得到，有些看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.80,0:41:20.86,ENG,547,0,0,0,,Some you could see, some you couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.01,0:41:24.84,CHT,548,0,0,0,,比如頭髮會四處生長
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.01,0:41:24.84,ENG,548,0,0,0,,Hair had started growing in all sorts of places,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.38,0:41:27.35,CHT,549,0,0,0,,還有很多其他的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.38,0:41:27.35,ENG,549,0,0,0,,along with other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.65,0:41:31.38,CHT,550,0,0,0,,我感覺很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.65,0:41:31.38,ENG,550,0,0,0,,I felt pretty good, considering.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.45,0:41:35.11,CHT,551,0,0,0,,親愛的，痛
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.45,0:41:35.11,ENG,551,0,0,0,,Darling, the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.22,0:41:37.75,CHT,552,0,0,0,,好的，媽媽，我去叫護士
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.22,0:41:37.75,ENG,552,0,0,0,,All right, Mom, I'll get the nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.29,0:41:42.95,CHT,553,0,0,0,,看看風眼，這是強烈颶風
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.29,0:41:42.95,ENG,553,0,0,0,,Look at this eye. This is a major hurricane,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.53,0:41:46.05,CHT,554,0,0,0,,颶風移動不快，伴隨最大持續風…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.53,0:41:46.05,ENG,554,0,0,0,,a slow hurricane, with maximum sustained winds of...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.16,0:41:48.00,CHT,555,0,0,0,,感覺不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.16,0:41:48.00,ENG,555,0,0,0,,Not doing too good?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.87,0:41:52.13,CHT,556,0,0,0,,似乎沒人知道該走還是該留
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.87,0:41:52.13,ENG,556,0,0,0,,Nobody seems to know whether to stay or leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.24,0:41:54.54,CHT,557,0,0,0,,都會過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.24,0:41:54.54,ENG,557,0,0,0,,I'm gonna ride it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.64,0:41:57.51,CHT,558,0,0,0,,好了，讓她舒服點
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.64,0:41:57.51,ENG,558,0,0,0,,There. That should make things much easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.95,0:42:04.14,CHT,559,0,0,0,,道過別了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.95,0:42:04.14,ENG,559,0,0,0,,Have you had a chance to say your goodbyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.25,0:42:07.74,CHT,560,0,0,0,,我父親等我弟弟從柏格市回來 等了四個小時 （位於美國北卡羅來納州林肯郡）
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.25,0:42:07.74,ENG,560,0,0,0,,My father waited four hours for my brother to get here from Boger City.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.85,0:42:09.82,CHT,561,0,0,0,,想見他最後一面
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.85,0:42:09.82,ENG,561,0,0,0,,Couldn't go without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.36,0:42:13.02,CHT,562,0,0,0,,- 她看上去很安詳 - 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.36,0:42:13.02,ENG,562,0,0,0,,- She seems like a sweet woman. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.69,0:42:15.39,CHT,563,0,0,0,,我應該多陪陪她的…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.69,0:42:15.39,ENG,563,0,0,0,,I haven't had as much time with her as I would've...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.49,0:42:17.39,CHT,564,0,0,0,,- 忙嗎？過來幫我下 - 失陪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.49,0:42:17.39,ENG,564,0,0,0,,- You busy? I could use your help. - Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.50,0:42:18.72,CHT,565,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.50,0:42:18.72,ENG,565,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.92,0:42:38.94,CHT,566,0,0,0,,奎尼會同意我跟道斯先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.92,0:42:38.94,ENG,566,0,0,0,,"Queenie would let me go with Mr. Daws..."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.05,0:42:42.85,CHT,567,0,0,0,,去波弗蒂角看船 （路易斯安那州內印地安人遺址）
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.05,0:42:42.85,ENG,567,0,0,0,,... to Poverty Point to watch the boats go up and down the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.95,0:42:44.89,CHT,568,0,0,0,,這些日子不好過
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.95,0:42:44.89,ENG,568,0,0,0,,These were hard times.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.93,0:42:51.62,CHT,569,0,0,0,,我跟你說過我曾被閃電擊了7次嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.93,0:42:51.62,ENG,569,0,0,0,,Did I ever tell you I was struck by lightning seven times?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.56,0:42:55.97,CHT,570,0,0,0,,一次是在田裡放牛
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.56,0:42:55.97,ENG,570,0,0,0,,Once when I was in the field, just tending to my cows.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.51,0:43:04.77,CHT,571,0,0,0,,我的夥計沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.51,0:43:04.77,ENG,571,0,0,0,,My fourth hand didn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.01,0:43:10.47,CHT,572,0,0,0,,有人想在這打工賺個2塊錢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.01,0:43:10.47,ENG,572,0,0,0,,Anybody want to make $2 for a day's work 'round here?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.42,0:43:14.11,CHT,573,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.42,0:43:14.11,ENG,573,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.22,0:43:16.95,CHT,574,0,0,0,,沒人想勤懇工作賺這一天的工錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.22,0:43:16.95,ENG,574,0,0,0,,Nobody wants to do an honest day's work for an honest day's pay?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.09,0:43:18.61,CHT,575,0,0,0,,他從不給錢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.09,0:43:18.61,ENG,575,0,0,0,,He never pays.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.09,0:43:22.39,CHT,576,0,0,0,,- 沒人要做？ - 我做
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.09,0:43:22.39,ENG,576,0,0,0,,- Nobody wants a job? - I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.03,0:43:26.86,CHT,577,0,0,0,,你不暈船吧，老頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.03,0:43:26.86,ENG,577,0,0,0,,You got your sea legs about you, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.97,0:43:29.33,CHT,578,0,0,0,,我想是的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.97,0:43:29.33,ENG,578,0,0,0,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.30,0:43:35.74,CHT,579,0,0,0,,很好，這就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.30,0:43:35.74,ENG,579,0,0,0,,Well, that's good enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.84,0:43:39.30,CHT,580,0,0,0,,快上船，上來就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.84,0:43:39.30,ENG,580,0,0,0,,Get your ass on board. We'll sure as hell find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.82,0:43:46.44,CHT,581,0,0,0,,我從沒這麼開心過
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.82,0:43:46.44,ENG,581,0,0,0,,I was as happy as I could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.55,0:43:47.81,CHT,582,0,0,0,,誰來幫忙！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.55,0:43:47.81,ENG,582,0,0,0,,I need a volunteer!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.92,0:43:49.25,CHT,583,0,0,0,,我什麼都做
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.92,0:43:49.25,ENG,583,0,0,0,,I would do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.35,0:43:50.79,CHT,584,0,0,0,,是，船長！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.35,0:43:50.79,ENG,584,0,0,0,,Yes, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.89,0:43:53.19,CHT,585,0,0,0,,把鳥屎都刮了！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.89,0:43:53.19,ENG,585,0,0,0,,Scrape off all this bird shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.93,0:43:55.62,CHT,586,0,0,0,,馬上，先生
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.93,0:43:55.62,ENG,586,0,0,0,,Right away, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.46,0:44:00.92,CHT,587,0,0,0,,事實上，本沒報酬的我卻拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.46,0:44:00.92,ENG,587,0,0,0,,And I was actually gonna be paid for something I would've done for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.60,0:44:04.93,CHT,588,0,0,0,,他是邁克·克拉克船長
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.60,0:44:04.93,ENG,588,0,0,0,,His name was Captain Mike Clark.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.94,0:44:08.84,CHT,589,0,0,0,,7歲起就在拖船上了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.94,0:44:08.84,ENG,589,0,0,0,,He'd been on a tugboat since he was seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.87,0:44:11.60,CHT,590,0,0,0,,上來
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.87,0:44:11.60,ENG,590,0,0,0,,Get moving, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.54,0:44:14.03,CHT,591,0,0,0,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.54,0:44:14.03,ENG,591,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.11,0:44:19.21,CHT,592,0,0,0,,你還能勃起嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.11,0:44:19.21,ENG,592,0,0,0,,Can you still get it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.59,0:44:22.58,CHT,593,0,0,0,,每天早上都行
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.59,0:44:22.58,ENG,593,0,0,0,,I do every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.25,0:44:26.66,CHT,594,0,0,0,,就憑這根，哈？能豎得老高老硬的？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.25,0:44:26.66,ENG,594,0,0,0,,The old pole, huh? The high, hard one?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.29,0:44:28.59,CHT,595,0,0,0,,我想是的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.29,0:44:28.59,ENG,595,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.20,0:44:33.82,CHT,596,0,0,0,,你上一次碰女人是什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.20,0:44:33.82,ENG,596,0,0,0,,When was the last time you had a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.37,0:44:38.27,CHT,597,0,0,0,,- 從沒碰過 - 從沒碰過？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.37,0:44:38.27,ENG,597,0,0,0,,- Never. - Never?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.77,0:44:40.83,CHT,598,0,0,0,,我記得沒有，先生
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.77,0:44:40.83,ENG,598,0,0,0,,Not that I know of, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.34,0:44:43.10,CHT,599,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.34,0:44:43.10,ENG,599,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.91,0:44:48.04,CHT,600,0,0,0,,你是說你活了這麼多年
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.91,0:44:48.04,ENG,600,0,0,0,,You mean to say you've been on this earth however many years
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.15,0:44:51.41,CHT,601,0,0,0,,還沒上過女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.15,0:44:51.41,ENG,601,0,0,0,,and you've never had a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.09,0:44:59.15,CHT,602,0,0,0,,見鬼，這是我聽過最慘的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.09,0:44:59.15,ENG,602,0,0,0,,Damn, that's the saddest thing I've ever heard in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.63,0:45:01.85,CHT,603,0,0,0,,從沒碰過？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.63,0:45:01.85,ENG,603,0,0,0,,Never?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.63,0:45:03.72,CHT,604,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.63,0:45:03.72,ENG,604,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.36,0:45:10.46,CHT,605,0,0,0,,好吧，你得感謝老天爺讓你遇上我
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.36,0:45:10.46,ENG,605,0,0,0,,Well, then, by Jesus, you are coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.48,0:45:23.07,CHT,606,0,0,0,,你父親做什麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.48,0:45:23.07,ENG,606,0,0,0,,What did your father do?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.18,0:45:25.21,CHT,607,0,0,0,,我從沒見過我父親
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.18,0:45:25.21,ENG,607,0,0,0,,I never met my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.32,0:45:27.25,CHT,608,0,0,0,,你這走運的雜種
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.32,0:45:27.25,ENG,608,0,0,0,,You lucky bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.15,0:45:30.78,CHT,609,0,0,0,,做父親的都想壓制兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.15,0:45:30.78,ENG,609,0,0,0,,All fathers want to do is hold you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.42,0:45:36.83,CHT,610,0,0,0,,我在我父親的船上日夜做工
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.42,0:45:36.83,ENG,610,0,0,0,,Out on my father's boat, workin' the two-a-day,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.16,0:45:39.60,CHT,611,0,0,0,,這個混蛋胖子
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.16,0:45:39.60,ENG,611,0,0,0,,this little, fat bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.70,0:45:41.39,CHT,612,0,0,0,,別人都叫他“愛爾蘭苦力”
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.70,0:45:41.39,ENG,612,0,0,0,,"Tug Irish," they called him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.50,0:45:44.87,CHT,613,0,0,0,,不過最後我終於鼓足勇氣跟他說
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.50,0:45:44.87,ENG,613,0,0,0,,Anyway, I finally work up the nerve and tell him,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.77,0:45:49.47,CHT,614,0,0,0,,“我不想把我的一輩子都浪費在這破船上”
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.77,0:45:49.47,ENG,614,0,0,0,,"I don't want to spend the rest of my life on a goddamn tugboat."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.57,0:45:51.54,CHT,615,0,0,0,,知道我的意思嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.57,0:45:51.54,ENG,615,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.94,0:45:54.61,CHT,616,0,0,0,,你不想把一輩子浪費在破船上
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.94,0:45:54.61,ENG,616,0,0,0,,You don't want to spend the rest of your life on a tugboat.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.71,0:45:57.01,CHT,617,0,0,0,,對！就是這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.71,0:45:57.01,ENG,617,0,0,0,,Absolutely! Damn right!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.78,0:46:02.38,CHT,618,0,0,0,,那你知道我爸怎麼回答嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.78,0:46:02.38,ENG,618,0,0,0,,So you know what my father says to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.22,0:46:07.66,CHT,619,0,0,0,,他說，“你他媽以為自己是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.22,0:46:07.66,ENG,619,0,0,0,,He says, "Who the hell do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.76,0:46:10.49,CHT,620,0,0,0,,“你他媽以為自己能做什麼？”
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.76,0:46:10.49,ENG,620,0,0,0,,"What the hell do you think you can do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.80,0:46:12.46,CHT,621,0,0,0,,然後我告訴他
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.80,0:46:12.46,ENG,621,0,0,0,,So I tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.10,0:46:16.29,CHT,622,0,0,0,,“既然你問了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.10,0:46:16.29,ENG,622,0,0,0,,"Well, if you're asking,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.57,0:46:20.59,CHT,623,0,0,0,,“我想當藝術家”
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.57,0:46:20.59,ENG,623,0,0,0,,"I want to be an artist."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.17,0:46:23.07,CHT,624,0,0,0,,他笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.17,0:46:23.07,ENG,624,0,0,0,,He laughs.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.57,0:46:28.57,CHT,625,0,0,0,,“藝術家？你就是幹拖船的命 就和我一樣"
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.57,0:46:28.57,ENG,625,0,0,0,,"An artist? God meant for you to work a tugboat, just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.68,0:46:31.31,CHT,626,0,0,0,,“老老實實地給我幹活”
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.68,0:46:31.31,ENG,626,0,0,0,,"And that's exactly what you're gonna do."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.42,0:46:34.65,CHT,627,0,0,0,,後來我真成了藝術家
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.42,0:46:34.65,ENG,627,0,0,0,,Well, I turned myself into an artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.12,0:46:38.85,CHT,628,0,0,0,,一個紋身藝術家！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.12,0:46:38.85,ENG,628,0,0,0,,A tattoo artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.29,0:46:44.09,CHT,629,0,0,0,,這都是我自己紋的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.29,0:46:44.09,ENG,629,0,0,0,,I put on every one of these myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.63,0:46:50.43,CHT,630,0,0,0,,要拿走我的藝術，你得先活剝了我
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.63,0:46:50.43,ENG,630,0,0,0,,You have to skin me alive to take my art away from me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.24,0:46:54.73,CHT,631,0,0,0,,我死後，要把自己的手臂給他
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.24,0:46:54.73,ENG,631,0,0,0,,When I'm dead, I'm gonna send him my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.01,0:46:57.41,CHT,632,0,0,0,,那條
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.01,0:46:57.41,ENG,632,0,0,0,,That one.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.74,0:47:02.37,CHT,633,0,0,0,,讓別人去說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.74,0:47:02.37,ENG,633,0,0,0,,Don't let anyone tell you different.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.48,0:47:05.07,CHT,634,0,0,0,,想做什麼就去做
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.48,0:47:05.07,ENG,634,0,0,0,,You gotta do what you're meant to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.18,0:47:08.28,CHT,635,0,0,0,,我碰巧就成了他媽的藝術家
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.18,0:47:08.28,ENG,635,0,0,0,,And I happen to be a goddamned artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.89,0:47:11.18,CHT,636,0,0,0,,可你還是個拖船船長
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.89,0:47:11.18,ENG,636,0,0,0,,But you're a tugboat captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.79,0:47:13.52,CHT,637,0,0,0,,邁克船長？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.79,0:47:13.52,ENG,637,0,0,0,,Captain Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.62,0:47:16.35,CHT,638,0,0,0,,我們已經為你和你的朋友準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.62,0:47:16.35,ENG,638,0,0,0,,We're ready for you and your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.10,0:47:21.12,CHT,639,0,0,0,,走吧，老傢伙，去破你的身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.10,0:47:21.12,ENG,639,0,0,0,,Let's go, old timer, eh? Break your cherry.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.33,0:47:25.03,CHT,640,0,0,0,,- 好啊，甜心們！ - 嗨，船長
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.33,0:47:25.03,ENG,640,0,0,0,,- Hello, my lovelies! - Hey, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.17,0:47:26.14,CHT,641,0,0,0,,- 嗨，船長 - 嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.17,0:47:26.14,ENG,641,0,0,0,,- Hi, Captain. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.31,0:47:29.40,CHT,642,0,0,0,,- 嗨 - 嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.31,0:47:29.40,ENG,642,0,0,0,,- Hi. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.51,0:47:32.53,CHT,643,0,0,0,,好噁心，我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.51,0:47:32.53,ENG,643,0,0,0,,He gives me the willies. That is not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.48,0:47:36.74,CHT,644,0,0,0,,今晚過得如何，老爺爺？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.48,0:47:36.74,ENG,644,0,0,0,,How are you tonight, grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.42,0:47:39.54,CHT,645,0,0,0,,那是一個難忘的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.42,0:47:39.54,ENG,645,0,0,0,,It was a night to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.29,0:47:48.95,CHT,646,0,0,0,,你是什麼，狄克·崔西還是什麼？ 我得休息休息
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.29,0:47:48.95,ENG,646,0,0,0,,What are you, Dick Tracy or something? I've got to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.09,0:47:51.32,CHT,647,0,0,0,,再來
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.09,0:47:51.32,ENG,647,0,0,0,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.63,0:47:54.96,CHT,648,0,0,0,,- 謝謝 - 不，該謝謝你，你今晚過得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.63,0:47:54.96,ENG,648,0,0,0,,- Thank you. - No, thank you. You have a nice night.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.07,0:47:57.19,CHT,649,0,0,0,,- 明天你還在嗎？ - 除了星期天每天都在
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.07,0:47:57.19,ENG,649,0,0,0,,- Will you be here tomorrow? - Every night but Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.30,0:48:01.00,CHT,650,0,0,0,,我想我明白了掙錢的重要
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.30,0:48:01.00,ENG,650,0,0,0,,It sure made me understand the value of earning a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.64,0:48:03.47,CHT,651,0,0,0,,晚安，寶貝，再來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.64,0:48:03.47,ENG,651,0,0,0,,Good night, sweetie. Come back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.57,0:48:05.77,CHT,652,0,0,0,,錢能買到一切
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.57,0:48:05.77,ENG,652,0,0,0,,Things money can buy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.46,0:48:25.12,CHT,653,0,0,0,,外面髒
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.46,0:48:25.12,ENG,653,0,0,0,,It's nasty out.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.60,0:48:28.50,CHT,654,0,0,0,,要搭車嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.60,0:48:28.50,ENG,654,0,0,0,,Can I offer you a ride somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.27,0:48:32.53,CHT,655,0,0,0,,您真是太好了，先生
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.27,0:48:32.53,ENG,655,0,0,0,,Well, that's awfully kind of you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.88,0:48:44.35,CHT,656,0,0,0,,我叫湯瑪斯，湯瑪斯·巴頓
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.88,0:48:44.35,ENG,656,0,0,0,,My name is Thomas, Thomas Button.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.02,0:48:47.11,CHT,657,0,0,0,,- 我叫本傑明 - 本傑明
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.02,0:48:47.11,ENG,657,0,0,0,,- I'm Benjamin. - Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.39,0:48:50.51,CHT,658,0,0,0,,很高興認識你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.39,0:48:50.51,ENG,658,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.06,0:48:55.29,CHT,659,0,0,0,,願意停下去喝杯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.06,0:48:55.29,ENG,659,0,0,0,,Would you like to stop somewhere and have a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.39,0:48:56.76,CHT,660,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.39,0:48:56.76,ENG,660,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.06,0:49:00.33,CHT,661,0,0,0,,晚上好，巴頓先生
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.06,0:49:00.33,ENG,661,0,0,0,,Evening, Mr. Button.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.90,0:49:06.84,CHT,662,0,0,0,,要點什麼，先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.90,0:49:06.84,ENG,662,0,0,0,,What'll it be, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.57,0:49:10.60,CHT,663,0,0,0,,- 跟他一樣 - 給我們都來薩澤拉克雞尾酒
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.57,0:49:10.60,ENG,663,0,0,0,,- I'll have whatever he's having. - Sazerac for the both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.71,0:49:13.07,CHT,664,0,0,0,,加威士卡，不要白蘭地
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.71,0:49:13.07,ENG,664,0,0,0,,With whiskey, not brandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.18,0:49:14.67,CHT,665,0,0,0,,你不喝酒？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.18,0:49:14.67,ENG,665,0,0,0,,You don't drink, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.78,0:49:17.37,CHT,666,0,0,0,,- 今晚什麼都是第一次啊 - 怎麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.78,0:49:17.37,ENG,666,0,0,0,,- It's a night for firsts. - How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.48,0:49:19.54,CHT,667,0,0,0,,以前從沒找過妓女
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.48,0:49:19.54,ENG,667,0,0,0,,I've never been to a brothel, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.65,0:49:22.41,CHT,668,0,0,0,,這是種經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.65,0:49:22.41,ENG,668,0,0,0,,Well, it's an experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.55,0:49:25.65,CHT,669,0,0,0,,當然，凡事總有第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.55,0:49:25.65,ENG,669,0,0,0,,It certainly is. There's a time for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.76,0:49:28.16,CHT,670,0,0,0,,- 沒錯 - 你們的酒
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.76,0:49:28.16,ENG,670,0,0,0,,- True enough. - Your drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.83,0:49:35.03,CHT,671,0,0,0,,恕我冒昧，你的手，痛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.83,0:49:35.03,ENG,671,0,0,0,,I don't mean to be rude, but your hands. Is that painful?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.37,0:49:37.99,CHT,672,0,0,0,,我生來就有些病
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.37,0:49:37.99,ENG,672,0,0,0,,Well, I was born with some form of disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.10,0:49:39.66,CHT,673,0,0,0,,什麼病？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.10,0:49:39.66,ENG,673,0,0,0,,What kind of disease?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.77,0:49:41.50,CHT,674,0,0,0,,我天生就是老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.77,0:49:41.50,ENG,674,0,0,0,,I was born old.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.04,0:49:44.74,CHT,675,0,0,0,,- 抱歉 - 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.04,0:49:44.74,ENG,675,0,0,0,,- I'm sorry. - No need to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.84,0:49:47.37,CHT,676,0,0,0,,年老沒什麼錯
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.84,0:49:47.37,ENG,676,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with old age.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.25,0:49:59.28,CHT,677,0,0,0,,我妻子多年前去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.25,0:49:59.28,ENG,677,0,0,0,,My wife passed away many years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.69,0:50:02.52,CHT,678,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.69,0:50:02.52,ENG,678,0,0,0,,I'm so, so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.00,0:50:05.86,CHT,679,0,0,0,,難產死的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.00,0:50:05.86,ENG,679,0,0,0,,She died in childbirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.37,0:50:11.89,CHT,680,0,0,0,,- 敬孩子 - 敬母親
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.37,0:50:11.89,ENG,680,0,0,0,,- To children. - To mothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.74,0:50:19.01,CHT,681,0,0,0,,你幹哪行的，巴頓先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.74,0:50:19.01,ENG,681,0,0,0,,What line of work you in, Mr. Button?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.11,0:50:23.24,CHT,682,0,0,0,,紐扣，巴頓紐扣公司，我們生產各類紐扣
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.11,0:50:23.24,ENG,682,0,0,0,,Buttons. Button's Buttons. There isn't a button that we don't make.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.45,0:50:27.82,CHT,683,0,0,0,,我們最大的競爭對手是B.F.富善公司
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.45,0:50:27.82,ENG,683,0,0,0,,Our biggest competition is B.F. Goodrich
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.92,0:50:29.65,CHT,684,0,0,0,,還有他們該死的拉鍊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.92,0:50:29.65,ENG,684,0,0,0,,and his infernal zippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.75,0:50:32.55,CHT,685,0,0,0,,先生們還要來點什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.75,0:50:32.55,ENG,685,0,0,0,,Would you gentlemen like anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.66,0:50:34.68,CHT,686,0,0,0,,再來杯上路，本傑明？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.66,0:50:34.68,ENG,686,0,0,0,,One for the road, Benjamin?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.79,0:50:37.63,CHT,687,0,0,0,,這次算我的，巴頓先生
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.79,0:50:37.63,ENG,687,0,0,0,,Only if you let me pay for it, Mr. Button.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.90,0:50:41.36,CHT,688,0,0,0,,那你是幹哪行的？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.90,0:50:41.36,ENG,688,0,0,0,,So, what line of work do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.80,0:50:45.23,CHT,689,0,0,0,,我是個拖船工人
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.80,0:50:45.23,ENG,689,0,0,0,,I'm a tugboat man.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.44,0:50:53.47,CHT,690,0,0,0,,跟你聊天很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.44,0:50:53.47,ENG,690,0,0,0,,I enjoyed talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.95,0:50:56.07,CHT,691,0,0,0,,跟你喝酒也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.95,0:50:56.07,ENG,691,0,0,0,,I enjoyed drinking with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.68,0:51:01.08,CHT,692,0,0,0,,本傑明？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.68,0:51:01.08,ENG,692,0,0,0,,Benjamin?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.19,0:51:04.62,CHT,693,0,0,0,,我可以不時過來看看你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.19,0:51:04.62,ENG,693,0,0,0,,Would you mind if, time to time, I stopped by and said hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.72,0:51:08.12,CHT,694,0,0,0,,隨時歡迎，晚安，巴頓先生
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.72,0:51:08.12,ENG,694,0,0,0,,Anytime. Good night, Mr. Button.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.66,0:51:10.42,CHT,695,0,0,0,,晚安，本傑明
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.66,0:51:10.42,ENG,695,0,0,0,,Good night, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.16,0:51:12.53,CHT,696,0,0,0,,開車
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.16,0:51:12.53,ENG,696,0,0,0,,Drive on.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.20,0:51:19.53,CHT,697,0,0,0,,你去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.20,0:51:19.53,ENG,697,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.64,0:51:24.63,CHT,698,0,0,0,,沒什麼，遇到了個人，聽了會音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.64,0:51:24.63,ENG,698,0,0,0,,Nothing. I met some people and listened to some music.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.41,0:51:29.61,CHT,699,0,0,0,,哦，天啊，孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.41,0:51:29.61,ENG,699,0,0,0,,Oh, sweet Jesus, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.61,0:51:33.71,CHT,700,0,0,0,,長大是件很有意思的事 不經意間就發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.61,0:51:33.71,ENG,700,0,0,0,,Growing up's a funny thing. Sneaks up on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.65,0:51:38.99,CHT,701,0,0,0,,本來是這樣一個人 然後突然間變成了另一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.65,0:51:38.99,ENG,701,0,0,0,,One person is there, then suddenly somebody else has taken her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.59,0:51:41.25,CHT,702,0,0,0,,不再是原來那樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.59,0:51:41.25,ENG,702,0,0,0,,She wasn't all elbows and knees anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.36,0:51:43.05,CHT,703,0,0,0,,本傑明！過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.36,0:51:43.05,ENG,703,0,0,0,,Benjamin! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.43,0:51:44.79,CHT,704,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.43,0:51:44.79,ENG,704,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.06,0:51:47.62,CHT,705,0,0,0,,我喜歡那些週末，她會來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.06,0:51:47.62,ENG,705,0,0,0,,I loved those weekends when she'd come
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.73,0:51:50.53,CHT,706,0,0,0,,和她的奶奶共度晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.73,0:51:50.53,ENG,706,0,0,0,,and spend the night with her grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.61,0:52:01.08,CHT,707,0,0,0,,黛西，黛西
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.61,0:52:01.08,ENG,707,0,0,0,,Daisy. Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.28,0:52:04.41,CHT,708,0,0,0,,給你看些東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.28,0:52:04.41,ENG,708,0,0,0,,You want to see something?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.58,0:52:10.35,CHT,709,0,0,0,,不過你得保密 快穿好衣服，我在外面等你
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.58,0:52:10.35,ENG,709,0,0,0,,You gotta keep it a secret, so get dressed. I'll meet you out back.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.89,0:52:17.26,CHT,710,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.89,0:52:17.26,ENG,710,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.06,0:52:22.19,CHT,711,0,0,0,,- 你會游泳嗎？ - 你會的我也會
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.06,0:52:22.19,ENG,711,0,0,0,,- Can you swim? - I can do anything you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.30,0:52:24.89,CHT,712,0,0,0,,給，穿上，我們得動作快點
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.30,0:52:24.89,ENG,712,0,0,0,,Here, put this on. We gotta hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.85,0:52:39.37,CHT,713,0,0,0,,他還好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.85,0:52:39.37,ENG,713,0,0,0,,Is he okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.48,0:52:40.92,CHT,714,0,0,0,,船長？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.48,0:52:40.92,ENG,714,0,0,0,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.55,0:52:44.04,CHT,715,0,0,0,,邁克船長？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.55,0:52:44.04,ENG,715,0,0,0,,Captain Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.79,0:52:50.49,CHT,716,0,0,0,,早上好，船長，能帶我們出海嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.79,0:52:50.49,ENG,716,0,0,0,,Morning, Captain. Can you take us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.66,0:52:53.96,CHT,717,0,0,0,,知道今天星期幾嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.66,0:52:53.96,ENG,717,0,0,0,,Do you know what day it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.07,0:52:55.33,CHT,718,0,0,0,,星期天？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.07,0:52:55.33,ENG,718,0,0,0,,Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.43,0:52:57.56,CHT,719,0,0,0,,知道那表示什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.43,0:52:57.56,ENG,719,0,0,0,,Do you know what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.90,0:53:01.30,CHT,720,0,0,0,,意味著我昨晚喝醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.90,0:53:01.30,ENG,720,0,0,0,,Means I was very drunk last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.91,0:53:04.17,CHT,721,0,0,0,,你哪天不喝醉
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.91,0:53:04.17,ENG,721,0,0,0,,Well, you're drunk every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.64,0:53:08.91,CHT,722,0,0,0,,- 是個女孩？ - 好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.64,0:53:08.91,ENG,722,0,0,0,,- Is that a girl? - Close friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.65,0:53:10.74,CHT,723,0,0,0,,我想帶她看河
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.65,0:53:10.74,ENG,723,0,0,0,,I want to show her the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.85,0:53:14.15,CHT,724,0,0,0,,你別偷偷帶外人出海
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.85,0:53:14.15,ENG,724,0,0,0,,You're not supposed to go joyriding with civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.32,0:53:17.45,CHT,725,0,0,0,,我會丟掉執照的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.32,0:53:17.45,ENG,725,0,0,0,,I could lose my license.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.26,0:53:28.73,CHT,726,0,0,0,,你還等什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.26,0:53:28.73,ENG,726,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.93,0:54:02.02,CHT,727,0,0,0,,要進站維修了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.93,0:54:02.02,ENG,727,0,0,0,,Pulled in for repair a wounded duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.47,0:54:05.59,CHT,728,0,0,0,,她在飛了，哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.47,0:54:05.59,ENG,728,0,0,0,,She's flying now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.14,0:54:07.76,CHT,729,0,0,0,,喂，水手！
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.14,0:54:07.76,ENG,729,0,0,0,,Ahoy, sailor!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.34,0:54:14.68,CHT,730,0,0,0,,真希望能和他們一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.34,0:54:14.68,ENG,730,0,0,0,,I wish we could go with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.68,0:54:22.95,CHT,731,0,0,0,,你在說什麼，媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.68,0:54:22.95,ENG,731,0,0,0,,Did you say something, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.73,0:54:32.70,CHT,732,0,0,0,,天氣越來越糟
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.73,0:54:32.70,ENG,732,0,0,0,,It's getting really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.73,0:54:36.50,CHT,733,0,0,0,,能聽見嗎，媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.73,0:54:36.50,ENG,733,0,0,0,,Can you hear me, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.14,0:54:41.80,CHT,734,0,0,0,,我沒多少時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.14,0:54:41.80,ENG,734,0,0,0,,Time just seeped out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.58,0:54:50.38,CHT,735,0,0,0,,“變化太快”
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.58,0:54:50.38,ENG,735,0,0,0,,"Things were changing quickly."
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.48,0:54:54.58,CHT,736,0,0,0,,不知怎麼回事，可你的頭髮多了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.48,0:54:54.58,ENG,736,0,0,0,,I don't know how it's possible, but you seem to have more hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.12,0:54:59.09,CHT,737,0,0,0,,要是我告訴你我沒有變老
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.12,0:54:59.09,ENG,737,0,0,0,,What if I told you that I wasn't getting older,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.19,0:55:02.49,CHT,738,0,0,0,,而是變得更年輕了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.19,0:55:02.49,ENG,738,0,0,0,,but I was getting younger than everybody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.59,0:55:06.50,CHT,739,0,0,0,,那真不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.59,0:55:06.50,ENG,739,0,0,0,,Well, I'd feel sorry for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.60,0:55:09.43,CHT,740,0,0,0,,你必須看著你愛的人先你而去
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.60,0:55:09.43,ENG,740,0,0,0,,to have to see everybody you love die before you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.53,0:55:11.43,CHT,741,0,0,0,,真是可怕的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.53,0:55:11.43,ENG,741,0,0,0,,It's an awful responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.54,0:55:15.10,CHT,742,0,0,0,,我以前從沒想過生死
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.54,0:55:15.10,ENG,742,0,0,0,,I'd never thought about life or death that way before.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.74,0:55:20.80,CHT,743,0,0,0,,本傑明，我們命中註定要失去所愛之人
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.74,0:55:20.80,ENG,743,0,0,0,,Benjamin, we're meant to lose the people we love.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.28,0:55:24.65,CHT,744,0,0,0,,不然我們怎麼知道 他們在我們生命中有多重要？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.28,0:55:24.65,ENG,744,0,0,0,,How else would we know how important they are to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.75,0:55:32.21,CHT,745,0,0,0,,秋天的一天，死神不期而至
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.75,0:55:32.21,ENG,745,0,0,0,,And one fall day, a familiar visitor came knocking on our door.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.96,0:55:36.76,CHT,746,0,0,0,,跟我一起去雜貨店嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.96,0:55:36.76,ENG,746,0,0,0,,You want to go with me to the drugstore?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.90,0:55:49.27,CHT,747,0,0,0,,她教我彈鋼琴
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.90,0:55:49.27,ENG,747,0,0,0,,She taught me how to play the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.37,0:55:50.64,CHT,748,0,0,0,,- 阿門 - 阿門
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.37,0:55:50.64,ENG,748,0,0,0,,- Amen. - Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.74,0:55:53.90,CHT,749,0,0,0,,她讓我明白了失去一個人的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.74,0:55:53.90,ENG,749,0,0,0,,And she taught me what it meant to miss somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.48,0:55:59.92,CHT,750,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.48,0:55:59.92,ENG,750,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.95,0:56:02.89,CHT,751,0,0,0,,我去過妓院
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.95,0:56:02.89,ENG,751,0,0,0,,I had gone to a brothel.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.99,0:56:05.29,CHT,752,0,0,0,,我喝過酒
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.99,0:56:05.29,ENG,752,0,0,0,,I'd had my first drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.39,0:56:08.85,CHT,753,0,0,0,,跟一個朋友道別，跟另一個朋友永別
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.39,0:56:08.85,ENG,753,0,0,0,,Said goodbye to one friend and buried another.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.39,0:56:14.26,CHT,754,0,0,0,,1936年我人生的第17個年末
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.39,0:56:14.26,ENG,754,0,0,0,,In 1936, when I was coming to the end of the 17th year of my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.37,0:56:17.20,CHT,755,0,0,0,,我收拾了行裝跟大家告別
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.37,0:56:17.20,ENG,755,0,0,0,,I packed my bag, said goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.30,0:56:19.63,CHT,756,0,0,0,,- 再見，本傑明 - 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.30,0:56:19.63,ENG,756,0,0,0,,- Bye, Benjamin. - Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.74,0:56:24.20,CHT,757,0,0,0,,我知道，生活仍將繼續 也許我再也見不到他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.74,0:56:24.20,ENG,757,0,0,0,,I knew, life being what it was, I'd probably never see them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.41,0:56:28.04,CHT,758,0,0,0,,再見，本傑明先生
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.41,0:56:28.04,ENG,758,0,0,0,,Bye, Mr. Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.15,0:56:30.61,CHT,759,0,0,0,,- 祝你好運，兒子 - 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.15,0:56:30.61,ENG,759,0,0,0,,- Good luck to you, son. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.15,0:56:38.05,CHT,760,0,0,0,,- 我愛你，媽媽 - 我也愛你，寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.15,0:56:38.05,ENG,760,0,0,0,,- I love you, Mama. - I love you, too, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.26,0:56:42.49,CHT,761,0,0,0,,別忘了每晚做祈禱，好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.26,0:56:42.49,ENG,761,0,0,0,,I want you to say your prayers every night, hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.36,0:56:49.39,CHT,762,0,0,0,,平平安安的，聽見了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.36,0:56:49.39,ENG,762,0,0,0,,Be safe, hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.81,0:57:02.18,CHT,763,0,0,0,,本傑明！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.81,0:57:02.18,ENG,763,0,0,0,,Benjamin!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.28,0:57:07.91,CHT,764,0,0,0,,- 你去哪？ - 出海
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.28,0:57:07.91,ENG,764,0,0,0,,- Where you going? - To sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.32,0:57:11.38,CHT,765,0,0,0,,我會給你寄明信片的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.32,0:57:11.38,ENG,765,0,0,0,,I'll send you a postcard.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.22,0:57:15.16,CHT,766,0,0,0,,無論在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.22,0:57:15.16,ENG,766,0,0,0,,From everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.26,0:57:17.85,CHT,767,0,0,0,,無論在哪都要給我寄明信片
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.26,0:57:17.85,ENG,767,0,0,0,,Write me a postcard from everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.38,0:57:34.24,CHT,768,0,0,0,,你能想像嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.38,0:57:34.24,ENG,768,0,0,0,,Can you imagine?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.65,0:57:42.75,CHT,769,0,0,0,,無論他去哪，在什麼地方工作
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.65,0:57:42.75,ENG,769,0,0,0,,He sent me a postcard from everywhere he went.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.32,0:57:46.29,CHT,770,0,0,0,,都會給我寄明信片
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.32,0:57:46.29,ENG,770,0,0,0,,Every place he worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.62,0:57:50.68,CHT,771,0,0,0,,紐芬蘭，巴芬灣
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.62,0:57:50.68,ENG,771,0,0,0,,Newfoundland. Baffin Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.30,0:57:54.36,CHT,772,0,0,0,,格拉斯哥，利物浦，納爾維克
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.30,0:57:54.36,ENG,772,0,0,0,,Glasgow. Liverpool. Narvik.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.17,0:57:59.90,CHT,773,0,0,0,,他和邁克船長一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.17,0:57:59.90,ENG,773,0,0,0,,He had gone with that Captain Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.94,0:58:04.17,CHT,774,0,0,0,,邁克船長和莫蘭兄弟拖船打撈公司
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.94,0:58:04.17,ENG,774,0,0,0,,Captain Mike had contracted for three years
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.27,0:58:06.57,CHT,775,0,0,0,,簽了3年的合約
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.27,0:58:06.57,ENG,775,0,0,0,,with Moran Brothers Tug and Salvage.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.68,0:58:10.55,CHT,776,0,0,0,,舊船裝上了柴油機和新的絞車
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.68,0:58:10.55,ENG,776,0,0,0,,The old ship had been refitted with a diesel engine and a new sea winch.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.65,0:58:13.55,CHT,777,0,0,0,,我們繞過了佛羅里達 沿著大西洋海岸北上
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.65,0:58:13.55,ENG,777,0,0,0,,We went around Florida and up the Atlantic seaboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.65,0:58:17.05,CHT,778,0,0,0,,船上現在有7名船員了，邁爾船長和我
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.65,0:58:17.05,ENG,778,0,0,0,,We were a crew of seven now. Captain Mike and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.15,0:58:20.49,CHT,779,0,0,0,,廚師，來自德拉瓦州威靈頓的普蘭提斯·梅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.15,0:58:20.49,ENG,779,0,0,0,,Cookie, Prentiss Mayes from Wilmington, Delaware.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.59,0:58:22.99,CHT,780,0,0,0,,布羅迪雙胞胎，裡克和維克
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.59,0:58:22.99,ENG,780,0,0,0,,The Brody twins, Rick and Vic,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.09,0:58:25.32,CHT,781,0,0,0,,在海上這兄弟倆相處很好 但不知什麼原因
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.09,0:58:25.32,ENG,781,0,0,0,,who got along fine at sea but, for some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.43,0:58:28.49,CHT,782,0,0,0,,一旦回到陸地，他們就不對盤
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.43,0:58:28.49,ENG,782,0,0,0,,once they were on dry land couldn't stand the sight of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.60,0:58:32.16,CHT,783,0,0,0,,你知道的，每八艘船就有一艘永遠回不來
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.60,0:58:32.16,ENG,783,0,0,0,,You know, one in every eight boats never returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.27,0:58:34.40,CHT,784,0,0,0,,一個叫約翰·格林的，人如其名
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.27,0:58:34.40,ENG,784,0,0,0,,There was John Grimm, who sure fit his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.51,0:58:36.34,CHT,785,0,0,0,,全體船員在海上失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.51,0:58:36.34,ENG,785,0,0,0,,All hands lost at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.44,0:58:38.67,CHT,786,0,0,0,,來自南達科他州的貝爾維迪市
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.44,0:58:38.67,ENG,786,0,0,0,,From Belvedere, South Dakota.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.08,0:58:42.91,CHT,787,0,0,0,,還有來自北卡羅來納州阿什維爾的 普萊森特·柯帝士
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.08,0:58:42.91,ENG,787,0,0,0,,And Pleasant Curtis from Asheville, Notch.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.01,0:58:46.18,CHT,788,0,0,0,,從不跟人說話，除了他自己
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.01,0:58:46.18,ENG,788,0,0,0,,Never said a word to anyone, except himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.29,0:58:48.59,CHT,789,0,0,0,,我經常給他寫信
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.29,0:58:48.59,ENG,789,0,0,0,,I wrote him constantly. I wrote him constantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.59,0:58:51.18,CHT,790,0,0,0,,我經常給他寫信
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.82,0:58:57.82,CHT,791,0,0,0,,我告訴他我受邀參加紐約市
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.82,0:58:57.82,ENG,791,0,0,0,,I told him I had been invited to audition in New York City
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.40,0:59:01.06,CHT,792,0,0,0,,一所美國芭蕾學校的面試
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.40,0:59:01.06,ENG,792,0,0,0,,for the School of American Ballet.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.17,0:59:02.56,CHT,793,0,0,0,,請留下
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.17,0:59:02.56,ENG,793,0,0,0,,Please stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.67,0:59:04.79,CHT,794,0,0,0,,謝謝，謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.67,0:59:04.79,ENG,794,0,0,0,,Thank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.77,0:59:08.03,CHT,795,0,0,0,,你可以留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.77,0:59:08.03,ENG,795,0,0,0,,You can stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.54,0:59:13.60,CHT,796,0,0,0,,可我在團裡並不出名
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.54,0:59:13.60,ENG,796,0,0,0,,But I was relegated to the corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.94,0:59:16.31,CHT,797,0,0,0,,只不過是個跳舞的流浪者
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.94,0:59:16.31,ENG,797,0,0,0,,Another dancing gypsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.62,0:59:22.14,CHT,798,0,0,0,,本傑明！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.62,0:59:22.14,ENG,798,0,0,0,,Benjamin!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.79,0:59:25.25,CHT,799,0,0,0,,第一次見你時
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.79,0:59:25.25,ENG,799,0,0,0,,How is it when you showed up
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.36,0:59:29.22,CHT,800,0,0,0,,你比那個系船柱大不了多少 還一隻腳踩進了棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.36,0:59:29.22,ENG,800,0,0,0,,you were no bigger than a bollard with one foot in the grave,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.33,0:59:33.52,CHT,801,0,0,0,,而現在，是我喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.33,0:59:33.52,ENG,801,0,0,0,,but now, either I drink a hell of a lot more than I think I do,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.80,0:59:36.43,CHT,802,0,0,0,,還是你長個了？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.80,0:59:36.43,ENG,802,0,0,0,,or you sprouted?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.33,0:59:39.10,CHT,803,0,0,0,,你有什麼秘密？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.33,0:59:39.10,ENG,803,0,0,0,,What's your secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.54,0:59:42.10,CHT,804,0,0,0,,船長
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.54,0:59:42.10,ENG,804,0,0,0,,Well, Captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.91,0:59:45.70,CHT,805,0,0,0,,你確實喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.91,0:59:45.70,ENG,805,0,0,0,,you do drink a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.51,0:59:54.78,CHT,806,0,0,0,,我們住在一個小旅館裡 名字不錯，叫冬宮
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.51,0:59:54.78,ENG,806,0,0,0,,We stayed in a small hotel with a grand name, The Winter Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.89,0:59:57.65,CHT,807,0,0,0,,你根本不知道自己在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.89,0:59:57.65,ENG,807,0,0,0,,You have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.75,1:00:01.21,CHT,808,0,0,0,,蜂鳥不是一般的鳥類
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.75,1:00:01.21,ENG,808,0,0,0,,The hummingbird is not just another bird.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.96,1:00:05.66,CHT,809,0,0,0,,它的心率達到每分鐘1200下
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.96,1:00:05.66,ENG,809,0,0,0,,Its heart rate's 1,200 beats per minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.43,1:00:10.13,CHT,810,0,0,0,,它的翅膀每秒扇動80次
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.43,1:00:10.13,ENG,810,0,0,0,,Its wings beat 80 times a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.07,1:00:15.06,CHT,811,0,0,0,,要是讓它無法扇動翅膀
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.07,1:00:15.06,ENG,811,0,0,0,,If you was to stop their wings from beating,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.71,1:00:18.54,CHT,812,0,0,0,,不到10秒就會死掉
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.71,1:00:18.54,ENG,812,0,0,0,,it would be dead in less than 10 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.54,1:00:22.21,CHT,813,0,0,0,,這不是一般的鳥
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.54,1:00:22.21,ENG,813,0,0,0,,This is no ordinary bird.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.88,1:00:24.97,CHT,814,0,0,0,,簡直就是奇跡
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.88,1:00:24.97,ENG,814,0,0,0,,This is a frickin' miracle.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.15,1:00:32.05,CHT,815,0,0,0,,人們用影像慢放扇翅膀的動作
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.15,1:00:32.05,ENG,815,0,0,0,,They slowed down their wings with moving pictures,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.72,1:00:34.92,CHT,816,0,0,0,,知道他們看到了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.72,1:00:34.92,ENG,816,0,0,0,,and you know what they saw?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.43,1:00:38.22,CHT,817,0,0,0,,它們的翼尖像這樣運動
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.43,1:00:38.22,ENG,817,0,0,0,,Their wingtips are doing that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.27,1:00:46.10,CHT,818,0,0,0,,知道數字8有什麼數學含義嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.27,1:00:46.10,ENG,818,0,0,0,,You know what the figure eight is the mathematical symbol for?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.11,1:00:50.63,CHT,819,0,0,0,,無窮
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.11,1:00:50.63,ENG,819,0,0,0,,Infinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.74,1:00:52.07,CHT,820,0,0,0,,無窮！
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.74,1:00:52.07,ENG,820,0,0,0,,Infinity!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.58,1:00:58.48,CHT,821,0,0,0,,每個人，不論語言和膚色有何差異
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.58,1:00:58.48,ENG,821,0,0,0,,Everybody, no matter what differences they had,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.58,1:01:02.61,CHT,822,0,0,0,,卻都有一個共同點
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.58,1:01:02.61,ENG,822,0,0,0,,the languages, the color of their skin, had one thing in common.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.55,1:01:05.92,CHT,823,0,0,0,,每晚都會喝醉
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.55,1:01:05.92,ENG,823,0,0,0,,They were drunk every single night.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.02,1:01:07.55,CHT,824,0,0,0,,三樓，謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.02,1:01:07.55,ENG,824,0,0,0,,Three, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.66,1:01:09.25,CHT,825,0,0,0,,能等一下嗎，親愛的？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.66,1:01:09.25,ENG,825,0,0,0,,Could you hold, dear, for us, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.36,1:01:11.62,CHT,826,0,0,0,,非常感謝，晚上好
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.36,1:01:11.62,ENG,826,0,0,0,,Thank you very much. Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.73,1:01:14.42,CHT,827,0,0,0,,她叫伊莉莎白·亞伯特
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.73,1:01:14.42,ENG,827,0,0,0,,Her name was Elizabeth Abbott.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.53,1:01:17.83,CHT,828,0,0,0,,她並不漂亮，很平凡
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.53,1:01:17.83,ENG,828,0,0,0,,She was not beautiful. She was plain as paper.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.94,1:01:20.73,CHT,829,0,0,0,,但在我看來她很美
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.94,1:01:20.73,ENG,829,0,0,0,,But she was pretty as any picture to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.04,1:01:24.06,CHT,830,0,0,0,,你在看什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.04,1:01:24.06,ENG,830,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.31,1:01:28.84,CHT,831,0,0,0,,你該知道，我們有個長期協議
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.31,1:01:28.84,ENG,831,0,0,0,,If you must know, we have a longstanding agreement
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.95,1:01:30.31,CHT,832,0,0,0,,不醉不歸
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.95,1:01:30.31,ENG,832,0,0,0,,never to go to bed sober.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.41,1:01:32.81,CHT,833,0,0,0,,- 對嗎，親愛的？ - 隨你怎麼說，親愛的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.41,1:01:32.81,ENG,833,0,0,0,,- Isn't that right, darling? - Whatever you say, darling.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.92,1:01:34.98,CHT,834,0,0,0,,她丈夫是沃爾特·亞伯特
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.92,1:01:34.98,ENG,834,0,0,0,,Her husband was Walter Abbott.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.09,1:01:38.99,CHT,835,0,0,0,,他是英國貿易代表團在摩爾曼斯克的首席部長
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.09,1:01:38.99,ENG,835,0,0,0,,He was Chief Minister of the British Trade Mission in Murmansk,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.09,1:01:40.72,CHT,836,0,0,0,,而且他還是個間諜
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.09,1:01:40.72,ENG,836,0,0,0,,and he was a spy.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.82,1:01:43.69,CHT,837,0,0,0,,- 親愛的 - 哦，謝謝，親愛的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.82,1:01:43.69,ENG,837,0,0,0,,- Darling. - Oh, thank you, my darling.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.79,1:01:45.82,CHT,838,0,0,0,,- 鑰匙，親愛的 - 噢，對
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.79,1:01:45.82,ENG,838,0,0,0,,- Key, darling. - Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.33,1:01:53.36,CHT,839,0,0,0,,我的一隻鞋跟斷了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.33,1:01:53.36,ENG,839,0,0,0,,I broke my heel off one of my shoes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.47,1:01:57.07,CHT,840,0,0,0,,我不習慣只穿襪子走路
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.47,1:01:57.07,ENG,840,0,0,0,,I'm not in the habit of walking about in my stocking feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.48,1:02:03.64,CHT,841,0,0,0,,那裡白天很長
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.48,1:02:03.64,ENG,841,0,0,0,,They were long days there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.15,1:02:13.12,CHT,842,0,0,0,,夜晚更加漫長
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.15,1:02:13.12,ENG,842,0,0,0,,And even longer nights.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.33,1:02:18.89,CHT,843,0,0,0,,有一個晚上，我輾轉難眠
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.33,1:02:18.89,ENG,843,0,0,0,,One particular night, I was having trouble sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.33,1:02:21.85,CHT,844,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.33,1:02:21.85,ENG,844,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.73,1:02:25.46,CHT,845,0,0,0,,我睡不著
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.73,1:02:25.46,ENG,845,0,0,0,,I couldn't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.38,1:02:41.84,CHT,846,0,0,0,,我要去泡些茶，你要嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.38,1:02:41.84,ENG,846,0,0,0,,I was gonna make some tea. Would you like some?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.75,1:02:44.58,CHT,847,0,0,0,,哦，不用了，謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.75,1:02:44.58,ENG,847,0,0,0,,Oh, no. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.43,1:03:23.98,CHT,848,0,0,0,,牛奶？還是蜂蜜？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.43,1:03:23.98,ENG,848,0,0,0,,Milk? Honey?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.63,1:03:26.56,CHT,849,0,0,0,,一點蜂蜜，謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.63,1:03:26.56,ENG,849,0,0,0,,A bit of honey, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.10,1:03:28.86,CHT,850,0,0,0,,我希望你不介意蜂蜜裡有蒼蠅
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.10,1:03:28.86,ENG,850,0,0,0,,I hope you like flies in your honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.97,1:03:30.63,CHT,851,0,0,0,,哦，還是算了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.97,1:03:30.63,ENG,851,0,0,0,,Oh, perhaps not.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.48,1:03:49.71,CHT,852,0,0,0,,哦，也許多浸一會會更好
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.48,1:03:49.71,ENG,852,0,0,0,,Oh, maybe better to let it steep a little.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.72,1:03:51.92,CHT,853,0,0,0,,浸？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.72,1:03:51.92,ENG,853,0,0,0,,Steep?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.29,1:03:53.35,CHT,854,0,0,0,,浸泡
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.29,1:03:53.35,ENG,854,0,0,0,,Soak.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.62,1:03:57.29,CHT,855,0,0,0,,我不知道，我的意思是，泡茶就該這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.62,1:03:57.29,ENG,855,0,0,0,,I don't know, I mean, there's a proper way of making tea.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.39,1:04:00.63,CHT,856,0,0,0,,我家鄉那都喜歡喝熱茶
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.39,1:04:00.63,ENG,856,0,0,0,,Well, where I'm from, people just want it to be hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.73,1:04:02.82,CHT,857,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.73,1:04:02.82,ENG,857,0,0,0,,Well, quite right.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.74,1:04:14.14,CHT,858,0,0,0,,- 現在你是海員 - 水手
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.74,1:04:14.14,ENG,858,0,0,0,,- Now, you're a seaman. - A sailor.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.24,1:04:16.97,CHT,859,0,0,0,,希望你不要介意，我忍不住想問
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.24,1:04:16.97,ENG,859,0,0,0,,I hope you won't think me impolite, but I have to ask,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.08,1:04:19.21,CHT,860,0,0,0,,作為一個水手你是不是有點老？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.08,1:04:19.21,ENG,860,0,0,0,,aren't you a little old to be working on a boat?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.32,1:04:22.72,CHT,861,0,0,0,,沒有年齡限制，只要你能做
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.32,1:04:22.72,ENG,861,0,0,0,,There's no age limit, as long as you can do the work.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.53,1:04:35.83,CHT,862,0,0,0,,你睡不好是嗎？謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.53,1:04:35.83,ENG,862,0,0,0,,And you have trouble sleeping? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.93,1:04:39.13,CHT,863,0,0,0,,以前不這樣，通常我睡得像嬰兒一樣沉
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.93,1:04:39.13,ENG,863,0,0,0,,I didn't think I did. I usually sleep like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.10,1:04:42.54,CHT,864,0,0,0,,有些事讓我睡不著
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.10,1:04:42.54,ENG,864,0,0,0,,Something's been keeping me up.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.77,1:04:44.97,CHT,865,0,0,0,,我父親80歲的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.77,1:04:44.97,ENG,865,0,0,0,,My father, in his 80s,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.08,1:04:48.34,CHT,866,0,0,0,,深信自己會在睡眠中死去
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.08,1:04:48.34,ENG,866,0,0,0,,he was so convinced he was gonna die in his sleep,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.98,1:04:52.11,CHT,867,0,0,0,,他約束自己只睡午覺
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.98,1:04:52.11,ENG,867,0,0,0,,he limited himself to having afternoon naps.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.88,1:04:55.65,CHT,868,0,0,0,,他堅信自己可以逃脫死亡
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.88,1:04:55.65,ENG,868,0,0,0,,He was so determined he was gonna cheat death.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.82,1:04:58.69,CHT,869,0,0,0,,- 他做到了嗎？ - 做到什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.82,1:04:58.69,ENG,869,0,0,0,,- Did he? - Did he what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.82,1:05:00.45,CHT,870,0,0,0,,睡覺時死了？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.82,1:05:00.45,ENG,870,0,0,0,,Die in his sleep?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.16,1:05:04.75,CHT,871,0,0,0,,他死在自己最喜歡的椅子上
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.16,1:05:04.75,ENG,871,0,0,0,,He died sitting in his favorite chair
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.86,1:05:07.49,CHT,872,0,0,0,,聽著自己最喜歡的廣播節目
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.86,1:05:07.49,ENG,872,0,0,0,,listening to his favorite program on the wireless.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.60,1:05:10.07,CHT,873,0,0,0,,他一定已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.60,1:05:10.07,ENG,873,0,0,0,,He must have known something.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.81,1:05:20.87,CHT,874,0,0,0,,我的丈夫是英國貿易部長 我們已經在這呆了14個月了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.81,1:05:20.87,ENG,874,0,0,0,,My husband's the British Trade Minister, and we've been here for 14 months.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.98,1:05:24.31,CHT,875,0,0,0,,- 天哪 - 本來我們要去北京的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.98,1:05:24.31,ENG,875,0,0,0,,- Good God. - We were supposed to go to Peking
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.41,1:05:27.87,CHT,876,0,0,0,,可是看來永遠都無法成行了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.41,1:05:27.87,ENG,876,0,0,0,,but it never seemed to work out.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.35,1:05:31.05,CHT,877,0,0,0,,你去過遠東嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.35,1:05:31.05,ENG,877,0,0,0,,Have you been in the Far East?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.15,1:05:33.35,CHT,878,0,0,0,,沒有，事實上我哪也沒去過
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.15,1:05:33.35,ENG,878,0,0,0,,No. I've never been anywhere, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.46,1:05:35.89,CHT,879,0,0,0,,我是說，港口以外的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.46,1:05:35.89,ENG,879,0,0,0,,I mean, outside of harbors.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.99,1:05:37.65,CHT,880,0,0,0,,你從哪來？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.99,1:05:37.65,ENG,880,0,0,0,,And where is it that you're from?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.76,1:05:40.25,CHT,881,0,0,0,,路易斯安那州新奧爾良
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.76,1:05:40.25,ENG,881,0,0,0,,New Orleans. Louisiana.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.77,1:05:44.06,CHT,882,0,0,0,,我知道那個地方
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.77,1:05:44.06,ENG,882,0,0,0,,I didn't know there was another.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.37,1:05:51.40,CHT,883,0,0,0,,她跟我講了她去過的地方 還有她的所見所聞
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.37,1:05:51.40,ENG,883,0,0,0,,And she told me about all the places she had been, and what she had seen.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.01,1:05:55.91,CHT,884,0,0,0,,我們一直聊到天亮
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.01,1:05:55.91,ENG,884,0,0,0,,And we talked till just before the dawn.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.95,1:05:58.41,CHT,885,0,0,0,,我只是一個酒鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.95,1:05:58.41,ENG,885,0,0,0,,I'm just a lush, myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.52,1:06:03.45,CHT,886,0,0,0,,我們回到各自的房間，過各自的生活
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.52,1:06:03.45,ENG,886,0,0,0,,And we went back to our rooms, to our separate lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.89,1:06:12.19,CHT,887,0,0,0,,可每晚我們都會在大廳見面
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.89,1:06:12.19,ENG,887,0,0,0,,But every night, we'd meet again in that lobby.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.53,1:06:21.44,CHT,888,0,0,0,,午夜的旅館是一個神奇的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.53,1:06:21.44,ENG,888,0,0,0,,A hotel in the middle of the night can be a magical place.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.31,1:06:27.21,CHT,889,0,0,0,,老鼠在遠處跑跑停停
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.31,1:06:27.21,ENG,889,0,0,0,,A mouse running, and stopping.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.65,1:06:30.74,CHT,890,0,0,0,,暖氣爐發出嘶嘶的響聲
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.65,1:06:30.74,ENG,890,0,0,0,,A radiator hissing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.75,1:06:33.61,CHT,891,0,0,0,,窗簾在沙沙作響
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.75,1:06:33.61,ENG,891,0,0,0,,A curtain blowing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.39,1:06:40.75,CHT,892,0,0,0,,這樣的場景讓你感到安靜，甚至是溫暖
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.39,1:06:40.75,ENG,892,0,0,0,,There's something peaceful, even comforting
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.86,1:06:44.09,CHT,893,0,0,0,,你知道你所愛的人此刻正在熟睡之中
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.86,1:06:44.09,ENG,893,0,0,0,,knowing that the people you love are asleep in their beds
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.19,1:06:46.42,CHT,894,0,0,0,,而沒有什麼可以傷害到他們
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.19,1:06:46.42,ENG,894,0,0,0,,where nothing can harm them.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.53,1:06:52.47,CHT,895,0,0,0,,伊莉莎白和我都忘記了時間
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.53,1:06:52.47,ENG,895,0,0,0,,Elizabeth and I would lose track of the night
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.00,1:06:55.16,CHT,896,0,0,0,,直到黎明的到來
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.00,1:06:55.16,ENG,896,0,0,0,,until just before daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.77,1:07:00.57,CHT,897,0,0,0,,我想我可能讓你誤解了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.77,1:07:00.57,ENG,897,0,0,0,,I think I may have given you the wrong impression.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.68,1:07:02.20,CHT,898,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.68,1:07:02.20,ENG,898,0,0,0,,Beg pardon?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.31,1:07:06.11,CHT,899,0,0,0,,已婚女人通常不會在半夜
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.31,1:07:06.11,ENG,899,0,0,0,,Well, married women don't customarily sit around
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.22,1:07:08.24,CHT,900,0,0,0,,和陌生男人呆在旅館裡
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.22,1:07:08.24,ENG,900,0,0,0,,in the middle of the night with strange men in hotels.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.35,1:07:11.88,CHT,901,0,0,0,,我不知道已婚女人什麼該做 什麼不該做
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.35,1:07:11.88,ENG,901,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know what a married woman does or doesn't do.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.66,1:07:19.09,CHT,902,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.66,1:07:19.09,ENG,902,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.43,1:07:22.73,CHT,903,0,0,0,,摩爾曼斯克
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.43,1:07:22.73,ENG,903,0,0,0,,Murmansk.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.37,1:07:28.43,CHT,904,0,0,0,,“我遇見了一個人，我墜入了愛河”
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.37,1:07:28.43,ENG,904,0,0,0,,"I've met somebody, and I've fallen in love."
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.54,1:07:29.73,CHT,905,0,0,0,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.54,1:07:29.73,ENG,905,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.58,1:07:36.10,CHT,906,0,0,0,,那是60多年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.58,1:07:36.10,ENG,906,0,0,0,,That was over 60 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.41,1:07:38.44,CHT,907,0,0,0,,你愛他嗎，媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.41,1:07:38.44,ENG,907,0,0,0,,Did you love him, Mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.55,1:07:41.31,CHT,908,0,0,0,,小女孩哪懂什麼愛情？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.55,1:07:41.31,ENG,908,0,0,0,,What does a girl know about love?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.92,1:08:16.11,CHT,909,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.92,1:08:16.11,ENG,909,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.62,1:08:22.39,CHT,910,0,0,0,,- 我穿得不好 - 哦，看起來蠻好，這才像你
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.62,1:08:22.39,ENG,910,0,0,0,,- I'm not dressed. - Oh, you look splendid, just as you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.66,1:08:27.72,CHT,911,0,0,0,,在摩爾曼斯克，別浪費時間在酒和乳酪上
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.66,1:08:27.72,ENG,911,0,0,0,,Don't waste any time bothering about the wine or the cheese in Murmansk,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.83,1:08:30.86,CHT,912,0,0,0,,因為這些實在很平常
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.83,1:08:30.86,ENG,912,0,0,0,,'cause they're really completely ordinary,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.97,1:08:35.93,CHT,913,0,0,0,,但是魚子醬和伏特加
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.97,1:08:35.93,ENG,913,0,0,0,,but the caviar and the vodka
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.51,1:08:40.60,CHT,914,0,0,0,,更顯高貴奢華
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.51,1:08:40.60,ENG,914,0,0,0,,are sublime and plentiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.41,1:08:45.68,CHT,915,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.41,1:08:45.68,ENG,915,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.99,1:08:52.28,CHT,916,0,0,0,,好好嘗嘗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.99,1:08:52.28,ENG,916,0,0,0,,Savor it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.42,1:08:56.39,CHT,917,0,0,0,,別一下子全吃了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.42,1:08:56.39,ENG,917,0,0,0,,And don't eat it all at once,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.49,1:08:59.59,CHT,918,0,0,0,,因為那樣是享受不到什麼的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.49,1:08:59.59,ENG,918,0,0,0,,because that way, there's nothing left to enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.26,1:09:05.60,CHT,919,0,0,0,,現在，口含伏特加，咽下一點點
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.26,1:09:05.60,ENG,919,0,0,0,,And now, take a little swallow of vodka while it's still in your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.48,1:09:23.32,CHT,920,0,0,0,,你相處過的女人不多吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.48,1:09:23.32,ENG,920,0,0,0,,You haven't been with many women, have you?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.52,1:09:26.15,CHT,921,0,0,0,,星期天不多
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.52,1:09:26.15,ENG,921,0,0,0,,Not on Sundays.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.36,1:09:30.09,CHT,922,0,0,0,,你以前從沒吃過魚子醬，對吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.36,1:09:30.09,ENG,922,0,0,0,,And you've never had caviar before, have you?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.19,1:09:31.82,CHT,923,0,0,0,,是的，夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.19,1:09:31.82,ENG,923,0,0,0,,No, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.67,1:09:39.33,CHT,924,0,0,0,,我19歲時
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.67,1:09:39.33,ENG,924,0,0,0,,When I was 19,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.34,1:09:46.61,CHT,925,0,0,0,,試圖成為第一個遊過英吉利海峽的女人
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.34,1:09:46.61,ENG,925,0,0,0,,I attempted to become the first woman ever to swim the English Channel.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.61,1:09:49.01,CHT,926,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.61,1:09:49.01,ENG,926,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.65,1:09:52.67,CHT,927,0,0,0,,但那天的水流很急
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.65,1:09:52.67,ENG,927,0,0,0,,But the current that day was so strong that,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.78,1:09:55.88,CHT,928,0,0,0,,向前遊一下，被水流推後兩下
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.78,1:09:55.88,ENG,928,0,0,0,,for every stroke I took, I was pushed back two.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.49,1:09:59.08,CHT,929,0,0,0,,我在水裡待了32小時
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.49,1:09:59.08,ENG,929,0,0,0,,I was in the water for 32 hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.06,1:10:03.89,CHT,930,0,0,0,,距離加來兩英里時
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.06,1:10:03.89,ENG,930,0,0,0,,And when I was two miles from Calais,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.03,1:10:06.76,CHT,931,0,0,0,,天開始下雨了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.03,1:10:06.76,ENG,931,0,0,0,,it started to rain.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.50,1:10:09.40,CHT,932,0,0,0,,就是這樣！保持平穩！
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.50,1:10:09.40,ENG,932,0,0,0,,That's it! Steady on!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.93,1:10:12.56,CHT,933,0,0,0,,我實在游不動時
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.93,1:10:12.56,ENG,933,0,0,0,,When I couldn't go any further,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.17,1:10:15.60,CHT,934,0,0,0,,我停下了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.17,1:10:15.60,ENG,934,0,0,0,,I stopped.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.01,1:10:18.60,CHT,935,0,0,0,,我只好停下
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.01,1:10:18.60,ENG,935,0,0,0,,I just stopped.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.21,1:10:24.08,CHT,936,0,0,0,,別人都問我，要不要再來一次？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.21,1:10:24.08,ENG,936,0,0,0,,And everybody asked me, would I try again?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.81,1:10:26.68,CHT,937,0,0,0,,為什麼不呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.81,1:10:26.68,ENG,937,0,0,0,,For why wouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.59,1:10:31.28,CHT,938,0,0,0,,可我再沒有試過
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.59,1:10:31.28,ENG,938,0,0,0,,But I never did.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.72,1:10:36.95,CHT,939,0,0,0,,事實上，自那以後我沒做過什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.72,1:10:36.95,ENG,939,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, I've never done anything with my life after that.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.10,1:10:43.12,CHT,940,0,0,0,,你的手好粗糙
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.10,1:10:43.12,ENG,940,0,0,0,,Your hands are so coarse.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.48,1:10:56.04,CHT,941,0,0,0,,我能感覺到吹向你臉頰的海風
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.48,1:10:56.04,ENG,941,0,0,0,,I can feel the wind in your cheek.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.82,1:11:05.31,CHT,942,0,0,0,,恐怕已經到午夜了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.82,1:11:05.31,ENG,942,0,0,0,,I'm afraid it's the witching hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.23,1:11:14.46,CHT,943,0,0,0,,那是第一次有女人吻我
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.23,1:11:14.46,ENG,943,0,0,0,,It was the first time a woman had ever kissed me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.03,1:11:17.43,CHT,944,0,0,0,,難以忘懷
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.03,1:11:17.43,ENG,944,0,0,0,,It's something you never forget.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.94,1:11:29.97,CHT,945,0,0,0,,是你讓我感覺年輕了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.94,1:11:29.97,ENG,945,0,0,0,,I think you make me feel younger.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.08,1:11:32.60,CHT,946,0,0,0,,你也讓我覺得年輕了好幾歲
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.08,1:11:32.60,ENG,946,0,0,0,,You make me feel years younger, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.72,1:11:34.31,CHT,947,0,0,0,,希望如此
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.72,1:11:34.31,ENG,947,0,0,0,,I wish I was.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.32,1:11:37.45,CHT,948,0,0,0,,我會改變很多事
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.32,1:11:37.45,ENG,948,0,0,0,,So many things I'd change.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.15,1:11:40.49,CHT,949,0,0,0,,我會彌補所有的過錯
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.15,1:11:40.49,ENG,949,0,0,0,,I'd undo all my mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.59,1:11:42.29,CHT,950,0,0,0,,什麼過錯？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.59,1:11:42.29,ENG,950,0,0,0,,What mistakes?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.63,1:11:47.79,CHT,951,0,0,0,,我一直等著，知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.63,1:11:47.79,ENG,951,0,0,0,,I kept waiting, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.43,1:11:52.93,CHT,952,0,0,0,,想著做些什麼改變自己的狀況
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.43,1:11:52.93,ENG,952,0,0,0,,Thinking that I'd do something to change my circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.20,1:11:55.93,CHT,953,0,0,0,,做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.20,1:11:55.93,ENG,953,0,0,0,,Do something.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.51,1:12:00.74,CHT,954,0,0,0,,那些浪費掉的，一去不復返
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.51,1:12:00.74,ENG,954,0,0,0,,Such an awful waste. You never get it back.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.21,1:12:02.68,CHT,955,0,0,0,,人生就這麼平白無辜地浪費了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.21,1:12:02.68,ENG,955,0,0,0,,Wasted time.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.99,1:12:11.39,CHT,956,0,0,0,,如果我們在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.99,1:12:11.39,ENG,956,0,0,0,,If we're going to have an affair,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.12,1:12:14.95,CHT,957,0,0,0,,白天千萬不要見面
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.12,1:12:14.95,ENG,957,0,0,0,,you're never to look at me during the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.59,1:12:18.53,CHT,958,0,0,0,,日出之前我們一定要分開
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.59,1:12:18.53,ENG,958,0,0,0,,And we're always to part before sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.20,1:12:21.82,CHT,959,0,0,0,,永遠不要說“我愛你”
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.20,1:12:21.82,ENG,959,0,0,0,,And we will never say "I love you."
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.47,1:12:25.26,CHT,960,0,0,0,,這些是規則
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.47,1:12:25.26,ENG,960,0,0,0,,Those are the rules.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.87,1:12:30.03,CHT,961,0,0,0,,- 你冷嗎？ - 快凍僵了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.87,1:12:30.03,ENG,961,0,0,0,,- Are you cold? - I'm freezing.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.14,1:12:32.07,CHT,962,0,0,0,,哦，你！你快凍僵了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.14,1:12:32.07,ENG,962,0,0,0,,Oh, you! You're frozen.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.18,1:12:35.37,CHT,963,0,0,0,,真傻，我還穿著皮衣呢 我怎麼這麼粗心
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.18,1:12:35.37,ENG,963,0,0,0,,What an idiot, I'm standing here in this fur. How thoughtless of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.05,1:13:11.84,CHT,964,0,0,0,,她是第一個愛過我的女人
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.05,1:13:11.84,ENG,964,0,0,0,,She was the first woman that ever loved me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.82,1:13:16.05,CHT,965,0,0,0,,要我跳過一些內容嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.82,1:13:16.05,ENG,965,0,0,0,,You want me to skip some?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.15,1:13:21.92,CHT,966,0,0,0,,不用，我很高興有人能溫暖他
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.15,1:13:21.92,ENG,966,0,0,0,,No, I'm glad he had somebody to keep him warm.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.60,1:13:28.06,CHT,967,0,0,0,,“我等不及要再見到她”
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.60,1:13:28.06,ENG,967,0,0,0,,"I couldn't wait to see her again."
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.98,1:13:43.28,CHT,968,0,0,0,,我們每晚見面
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.98,1:13:43.28,ENG,968,0,0,0,,We saw each other every night.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.88,1:13:46.18,CHT,969,0,0,0,,總是在同一間屋子
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.88,1:13:46.18,ENG,969,0,0,0,,We always used the same room.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.15,1:13:51.48,CHT,970,0,0,0,,可每次都有不同的體驗
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.15,1:13:51.48,ENG,970,0,0,0,,But each time seemed new and different.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.89,1:13:54.32,CHT,971,0,0,0,,過來
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.89,1:13:54.32,ENG,971,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.80,1:14:03.20,CHT,972,0,0,0,,伊莉莎白
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.80,1:14:03.20,ENG,972,0,0,0,,Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.57,1:14:05.97,CHT,973,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.57,1:14:05.97,ENG,973,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.67,1:14:10.30,CHT,974,0,0,0,,直到有一個晚上
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.67,1:14:10.30,ENG,974,0,0,0,,Until one night.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.58,1:14:53.17,CHT,975,0,0,0,,昨天，1941年12月7日
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.58,1:14:53.17,ENG,975,0,0,0,,Yesterday, December 7th, 1941,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.28,1:14:56.38,CHT,976,0,0,0,,恥辱的一天…
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.28,1:14:56.38,ENG,976,0,0,0,,a date which will live in infamy...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.49,1:15:00.62,CHT,977,0,0,0,,這是一場會議 一場事關未來的政治性會議
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.49,1:15:00.62,ENG,977,0,0,0,,It's a meeting, a policy meeting regarding your future,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.56,1:15:03.12,CHT,978,0,0,0,,可能不止如此
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.56,1:15:03.12,ENG,978,0,0,0,,possibly beyond.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.53,1:15:07.09,CHT,979,0,0,0,,夥計們，計畫有變
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.53,1:15:07.09,ENG,979,0,0,0,,There's been a change of plan, lads.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.30,1:15:09.89,CHT,980,0,0,0,,你們或許知道，或許不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.30,1:15:09.89,ENG,980,0,0,0,,As you may or may not know,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.00,1:15:12.59,CHT,981,0,0,0,,日本人昨天轟炸了珍珠港
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.00,1:15:12.59,ENG,981,0,0,0,,the Japs bombed Pearl Harbor yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.04,1:15:16.49,CHT,982,0,0,0,,佛蘭克林·德拉諾·羅斯福 要求我們每個人盡到自己的職責
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.04,1:15:16.49,ENG,982,0,0,0,,Frank D. Roosevelt's asked each of us to do our part.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.01,1:15:21.10,CHT,983,0,0,0,,切爾西號被美國海軍徵用
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.01,1:15:21.10,ENG,983,0,0,0,,The Chelsea's been commissioned to serve in the United States Navy.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.54,1:15:24.81,CHT,984,0,0,0,,負責維修，打撈和營救
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.54,1:15:24.81,ENG,984,0,0,0,,To repair, to salvage, and to rescue.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.35,1:15:30.68,CHT,985,0,0,0,,有誰不想打仗，現在說還來得及
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.35,1:15:30.68,ENG,985,0,0,0,,Anybody doesn't want to go to war, now is the time to say so.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.79,1:15:34.99,CHT,986,0,0,0,,只要你踏上了那艘船 你就是海軍了，朋友
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.79,1:15:34.99,ENG,986,0,0,0,,Once you set foot on that boat, you're in the Navy, friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.23,1:15:41.25,CHT,987,0,0,0,,我一直想和你談談，邁克
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.23,1:15:41.25,ENG,987,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've been meaning to talk with you, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.36,1:15:43.36,CHT,988,0,0,0,,我老婆的情況不好
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.36,1:15:43.36,ENG,988,0,0,0,,My wife's doing poorly.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.47,1:15:46.20,CHT,989,0,0,0,,我希望能再見她一面
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.47,1:15:46.20,ENG,989,0,0,0,,I'd like to maybe see her one more time.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.94,1:15:51.74,CHT,990,0,0,0,,你現在可以自由地回家了，梅斯先生
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.94,1:15:51.74,ENG,990,0,0,0,,You're free to make your way home any way you can, Mr. Mayes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.38,1:15:59.14,CHT,991,0,0,0,,他走了誰做飯啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.38,1:15:59.14,ENG,991,0,0,0,,Well, if he's leaving, who's gonna cook?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.25,1:16:03.31,CHT,992,0,0,0,,食物中毒是海上人員死亡的最主要原因之一
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.25,1:16:03.31,ENG,992,0,0,0,,Food poisoning's one of the leading causes of death at sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.42,1:16:05.79,CHT,993,0,0,0,,僅次於安全裝備不足
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.42,1:16:05.79,ENG,993,0,0,0,,Right after inadequate safety equipment.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.89,1:16:08.52,CHT,994,0,0,0,,我會做飯，船長，幹了一輩子了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.89,1:16:08.52,ENG,994,0,0,0,,I can cook, Captain. Been doing it all my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.62,1:16:13.03,CHT,995,0,0,0,,我不知道，你也厭戰，本傑明
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.62,1:16:13.03,ENG,995,0,0,0,,I don't know. You're a little moody for war, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.13,1:16:15.10,CHT,996,0,0,0,,管他呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.13,1:16:15.10,ENG,996,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.20,1:16:19.53,CHT,997,0,0,0,,想打倒小日本和匈奴人的都跟我走
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.20,1:16:19.53,ENG,997,0,0,0,,I'll take any man wants to kick the shite out of the Japs and the Huns.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.94,1:16:24.70,CHT,998,0,0,0,,就這樣吧，收拾行裝 我們要上戰場了，先生們！
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.94,1:16:24.70,ENG,998,0,0,0,,That's it, pack your gear. We're going to war, gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.58,1:16:33.34,CHT,999,0,0,0,,她留了紙條
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.58,1:16:33.34,ENG,999,0,0,0,,She had left a note.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.72,1:16:37.45,CHT,1000,0,0,0,,她寫道，“能遇到你真好”
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.72,1:16:37.45,ENG,1000,0,0,0,,She wrote, "It was nice to have met you."
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.22,1:16:39.81,CHT,1001,0,0,0,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.22,1:16:39.81,ENG,1001,0,0,0,,And that was it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.06,1:16:46.12,CHT,1002,0,0,0,,戰爭和我們想像的不一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.06,1:16:46.12,ENG,1002,0,0,0,,It wasn't the war any of us expected.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.23,1:16:49.86,CHT,1003,0,0,0,,我們只是拖走破損的船 其實都是些廢銅爛鐵
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.23,1:16:49.86,ENG,1003,0,0,0,,We would just tow crippled ships, scraps of metal, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.47,1:16:53.44,CHT,1004,0,0,0,,真有戰爭，我們也沒看到
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.47,1:16:53.44,ENG,1004,0,0,0,,If there was a war, we didn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.34,1:16:59.40,CHT,1005,0,0,0,,派給我們的主炮手非常熱愛海軍
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.34,1:16:59.40,ENG,1005,0,0,0,,There was a man assigned to us. The Chief Gunner loved the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.51,1:17:01.70,CHT,1006,0,0,0,,最重要的是他愛美國
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.51,1:17:01.70,ENG,1006,0,0,0,,But most of all, he loved America.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.81,1:17:04.71,CHT,1007,0,0,0,,世界上沒有其他國家
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.81,1:17:04.71,ENG,1007,0,0,0,,There is no other country in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.81,1:17:05.91,CHT,1008,0,0,0,,當你拼寫美國…
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.81,1:17:05.91,ENG,1008,0,0,0,,When you spell America...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.02,1:17:10.18,CHT,1009,0,0,0,,他叫鄧尼斯·史密斯 是個純血統的切羅基人 （美洲土著人）
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.02,1:17:10.18,ENG,1009,0,0,0,,His name was Dennis Smith, and he was a full-blooded Cherokee.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.29,1:17:13.38,CHT,1010,0,0,0,,他的家族在美洲居住了500多年
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.29,1:17:13.38,ENG,1010,0,0,0,,His family had been Americans for over 500 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.49,1:17:18.02,CHT,1011,0,0,0,,去他們的和平主義者 說什麼不會憑良心打仗
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.49,1:17:18.02,ENG,1011,0,0,0,,These pacifists. They say they won't fight on conscience.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.13,1:17:21.72,CHT,1012,0,0,0,,要是所有人都憑良心
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.13,1:17:21.72,ENG,1012,0,0,0,,Now, where would be if everybody decided to act
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.83,1:17:25.79,CHT,1013,0,0,0,,- 那會怎麼樣？ - 冷靜點，長官？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.83,1:17:25.79,ENG,1013,0,0,0,,- according to their conscience? - Keep it down, would you, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.02,1:17:45.39,CHT,1014,0,0,0,,嘿，我觀察你很久了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.02,1:17:45.39,ENG,1014,0,0,0,,Hey. I've been watching you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.56,1:17:48.35,CHT,1015,0,0,0,,你看上去值得信任
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.56,1:17:48.35,ENG,1015,0,0,0,,You seem trustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.16,1:17:52.25,CHT,1016,0,0,0,,萬一我有什麼不測
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.16,1:17:52.25,ENG,1016,0,0,0,,If something happens to me,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.33,1:17:58.89,CHT,1017,0,0,0,,你能答應把這個給我老婆嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.33,1:17:58.89,ENG,1017,0,0,0,,could you see that this gets to my wife?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.00,1:18:03.53,CHT,1018,0,0,0,,他把全部工錢都給了我 一分錢也沒花過
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.00,1:18:03.53,ENG,1018,0,0,0,,He'd given me all of his pay. Hadn't spent a dime of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.44,1:18:08.71,CHT,1019,0,0,0,,我希望家人知道，我時刻掛念著他們
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.44,1:18:08.71,ENG,1019,0,0,0,,I want my family to know I was thinking about them.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.48,1:18:15.31,CHT,1020,0,0,0,,全體船員到甲板上！
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.48,1:18:15.31,ENG,1020,0,0,0,,All hands on deck!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.82,1:18:20.62,CHT,1021,0,0,0,,快起來，你們這群懶豬！
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.82,1:18:20.62,ENG,1021,0,0,0,,Get your asses up here, you lazy bastards!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.91,1:18:44.11,CHT,1022,0,0,0,,戰爭終於還是來了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.91,1:18:44.11,ENG,1022,0,0,0,,The war had finally found us.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.82,1:18:48.28,CHT,1023,0,0,0,,都別動！
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.82,1:18:48.28,ENG,1023,0,0,0,,All stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.02,1:18:53.01,CHT,1024,0,0,0,,普萊森特，轉下那燈
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.02,1:18:53.01,ENG,1024,0,0,0,,Pleasant, man that light.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.90,1:19:05.06,CHT,1025,0,0,0,,一艘載有1300人的運輸艦被魚雷擊沉
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.90,1:19:05.06,ENG,1025,0,0,0,,A transport carrying 1,300 men had been split by a torpedo.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.47,1:19:09.73,CHT,1026,0,0,0,,我們是第一個趕到現場的
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.47,1:19:09.73,ENG,1026,0,0,0,,We were first to arrive at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.84,1:19:13.40,CHT,1027,0,0,0,,- 關掉引擎！ - 都別動！
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.84,1:19:13.40,ENG,1027,0,0,0,,- Cut the engines! - All stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.55,1:19:20.45,CHT,1028,0,0,0,,四周只有我們的聲音
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.55,1:19:20.45,ENG,1028,0,0,0,,We were the only sound.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.40,1:19:35.80,CHT,1029,0,0,0,,夥計們！
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.40,1:19:35.80,ENG,1029,0,0,0,,Fellas!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.78,1:19:46.83,CHT,1030,0,0,0,,潛水艇！
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.78,1:19:46.83,ENG,1030,0,0,0,,Sub!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.65,1:19:54.45,CHT,1031,0,0,0,,我們絕對跑不過他們
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.65,1:19:54.45,ENG,1031,0,0,0,,We sure as hell can't outrun them fuckers.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.19,1:19:58.48,CHT,1032,0,0,0,,各就各位！
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.19,1:19:58.48,ENG,1032,0,0,0,,Battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.36,1:20:09.35,CHT,1033,0,0,0,,謝謝，長官
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.36,1:20:09.35,ENG,1033,0,0,0,,Thank you, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.67,1:20:12.76,CHT,1034,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.67,1:20:12.76,ENG,1034,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.75,1:20:27.55,CHT,1035,0,0,0,,是最後一個麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.75,1:20:27.55,ENG,1035,0,0,0,,Is that the last one?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.15,1:21:50.45,CHT,1036,0,0,0,,船長！
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.15,1:21:50.45,ENG,1036,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.05,1:22:08.65,CHT,1037,0,0,0,,狗日的把我的畫打爛了！
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.05,1:22:08.65,ENG,1037,0,0,0,,They shot the hell out of my painting!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.95,1:22:11.75,CHT,1038,0,0,0,,握著我的手
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.95,1:22:11.75,ENG,1038,0,0,0,,Give me your other hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.15,1:22:18.15,CHT,1039,0,0,0,,你會沒事的，船長
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.15,1:22:18.15,ENG,1039,0,0,0,,You'll be all right, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.35,1:22:22.55,CHT,1040,0,0,0,,天使們在天堂裡 給你留了個好地方呢
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.35,1:22:22.55,ENG,1040,0,0,0,,They got a nice spot in Heaven waiting for you. Nice spot.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.15,1:22:27.15,CHT,1041,0,0,0,,不順心的時候 你可以像瘋狗一樣發狂
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.15,1:22:27.15,ENG,1041,0,0,0,,You can be as mad as a mad dog at the way things went.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.15,1:22:33.85,CHT,1042,0,0,0,,可以破口大駡，詛咒命運
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.15,1:22:33.85,ENG,1042,0,0,0,,You could swear, curse the Fates.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.15,1:22:38.25,CHT,1043,0,0,0,,但到頭來
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.15,1:22:38.25,ENG,1043,0,0,0,,But when it comes to the end,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.45,1:22:42.15,CHT,1044,0,0,0,,還是得放手
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.45,1:22:42.15,ENG,1044,0,0,0,,you have to let go.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.25,1:22:50.45,CHT,1045,0,0,0,,船長？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.25,1:22:50.45,ENG,1045,0,0,0,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.25,1:23:14.55,CHT,1046,0,0,0,,那天，1328人離開了人間
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.25,1:23:14.55,ENG,1046,0,0,0,,Thirteen hundred and twenty eight men died that day.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.85,1:23:20.15,CHT,1047,0,0,0,,我和切羅基人鄧尼斯·史密斯道別
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.85,1:23:20.15,ENG,1047,0,0,0,,I said my goodbyes to the Cherokee, Dennis Smith.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.05,1:23:24.25,CHT,1048,0,0,0,,和約翰·格林道別--他猜得沒錯 他最後還是死在那兒了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.05,1:23:24.25,ENG,1048,0,0,0,,John Grimm, who was right, he was gonna die there.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.85,1:23:28.45,CHT,1049,0,0,0,,我把普萊森特·柯帝士的錢 寄給了他妻子
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.85,1:23:28.45,ENG,1049,0,0,0,,I sent Pleasant Curtis' wife his money.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.35,1:23:32.45,CHT,1050,0,0,0,,我向雙胞胎的維克·布羅迪道別
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.35,1:23:32.45,ENG,1050,0,0,0,,I said goodbye to the twin, Vic Brody,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.55,1:23:37.15,CHT,1051,0,0,0,,還有邁克·克拉克--切爾西號的船長
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.55,1:23:37.15,ENG,1051,0,0,0,,and to Mike Clark, captain of the tugboat Chelsea.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.65,1:23:44.15,CHT,1052,0,0,0,,我和那些仍舊懷揣夢想的人道別
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.65,1:23:44.15,ENG,1052,0,0,0,,I said goodbye to all the other men who had dreams of their own,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.25,1:23:46.75,CHT,1053,0,0,0,,他們有的想做保險推銷員
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.25,1:23:46.75,ENG,1053,0,0,0,,all the men who wanted to be insurance salesmen
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.85,1:23:49.85,CHT,1054,0,0,0,,有的想當醫生，律師 甚至是部落酋長
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.85,1:23:49.85,ENG,1054,0,0,0,,or doctors or lawyers or Indian chiefs.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.85,1:23:52.65,CHT,1055,0,0,0,,這個修不好了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.85,1:23:52.65,ENG,1055,0,0,0,,This don't get fixed.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.75,1:23:57.85,CHT,1056,0,0,0,,在那兒，死亡不再是自然發生的了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.75,1:23:57.85,ENG,1056,0,0,0,,Out here, death didn't seem natural.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.85,1:24:18.05,CHT,1057,0,0,0,,我從沒在遠海上見過蜂鳥
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.85,1:24:18.05,ENG,1057,0,0,0,,I'd never seen a hummingbird that far out to sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.55,1:24:21.15,CHT,1058,0,0,0,,無論是之前，還是此後
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.55,1:24:21.15,ENG,1058,0,0,0,,Before or since.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.95,1:24:33.15,CHT,1059,0,0,0,,1945年5月，我26歲
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.95,1:24:33.15,ENG,1059,0,0,0,,And in May of 1945, when I was 26 years old,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.15,1:24:34.25,CHT,1060,0,0,0,,我回家了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.15,1:24:34.25,ENG,1060,0,0,0,,I came home.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.15,1:24:37.75,CHT,1061,0,0,0,,我準備好了！準備好了！
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.15,1:24:37.75,ENG,1061,0,0,0,,I'm ready! I'm ready!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.85,1:24:39.25,CHT,1062,0,0,0,,來了！
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.85,1:24:39.25,ENG,1062,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.15,1:24:43.75,CHT,1063,0,0,0,,- 我準備好了！ - 這就來了，阿法莉娜
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.15,1:24:43.75,ENG,1063,0,0,0,,- I'm ready! - All right, I'm coming, Miss Alfalina.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.85,1:24:45.35,CHT,1064,0,0,0,,- 奎尼？ - 嗯？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.85,1:24:45.35,ENG,1064,0,0,0,,- Queenie? - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.25,1:24:57.15,CHT,1065,0,0,0,,老天爺！你回來了！ 神啊，你回來了！
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.25,1:24:57.15,ENG,1065,0,0,0,,Sweet Jesus! Oh, you're home! Oh, Lord, you came back!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.05,1:25:00.05,CHT,1066,0,0,0,,- 快讓我瞧瞧 - 他是誰呀，媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.05,1:25:00.05,ENG,1066,0,0,0,,- Let me look at you. - Who's that, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.15,1:25:03.35,CHT,1067,0,0,0,,- 孩子啊，這是你哥哥，本傑明 - 我都不知道我還有哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.15,1:25:03.35,ENG,1067,0,0,0,,- Child, it's your brother, Benjamin. - I didn't know he was my brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.45,1:25:05.15,CHT,1068,0,0,0,,你不知道的事情多了去了，小丫頭
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.45,1:25:05.15,ENG,1068,0,0,0,,There's a shitload of things you don't know, child.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.25,1:25:06.45,CHT,1069,0,0,0,,趕緊去把地掃完
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.25,1:25:06.45,ENG,1069,0,0,0,,Get on out there and finish sweeping.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.55,1:25:08.65,CHT,1070,0,0,0,,再把手洗洗來幫我擺餐桌，快去
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.55,1:25:08.65,ENG,1070,0,0,0,,Come here, wash your hands, help me with the table. Go on, now.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.75,1:25:12.65,CHT,1071,0,0,0,,轉過來，你看起來跟重生了一樣！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.75,1:25:12.65,ENG,1071,0,0,0,,Turn around. You look like you've been born again.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.75,1:25:15.05,CHT,1072,0,0,0,,比春天還有活力！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.75,1:25:15.05,ENG,1072,0,0,0,,Younger than the springtime.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.15,1:25:18.75,CHT,1073,0,0,0,,要我說，那牧師施法的時候 肯定是又給了你一條命
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.15,1:25:18.75,ENG,1073,0,0,0,,I think that preacher laid hands on you gave you a second life.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.85,1:25:22.55,CHT,1074,0,0,0,,那會我看著你就知道 你跟別人不一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.85,1:25:22.55,ENG,1074,0,0,0,,I knew it that moment I saw you, you were special.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.65,1:25:24.45,CHT,1075,0,0,0,,知道嘛，我的膝蓋現在都酸
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.65,1:25:24.45,ENG,1075,0,0,0,,I tell you what, my knees are sore,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.65,1:25:27.15,CHT,1076,0,0,0,,因為我每天晚上都跪著 求上帝保佑
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.65,1:25:27.15,ENG,1076,0,0,0,,'cause I've been on them every night asking the Lord,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.25,1:25:30.95,CHT,1077,0,0,0,,求他“上帝啊，我只要他平安回家”
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.25,1:25:30.95,ENG,1077,0,0,0,,I said, "God, just bring him home safely."
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.05,1:25:33.55,CHT,1078,0,0,0,,還記得我怎麼跟你說的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.05,1:25:33.55,ENG,1078,0,0,0,,Remember what I told you?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.65,1:25:35.35,CHT,1079,0,0,0,,“你永遠都猜不到 以後的生活是啥樣子”
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.65,1:25:35.35,ENG,1079,0,0,0,,"You never know what's coming for you"?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.45,1:25:37.35,CHT,1080,0,0,0,,沒錯，快坐下
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.45,1:25:37.35,ENG,1080,0,0,0,,That's right. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.75,1:25:42.85,CHT,1081,0,0,0,,這幾年，有碰上什麼有趣兒的事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.75,1:25:42.85,ENG,1081,0,0,0,,Well, you learn anything worth repeating?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.95,1:25:49.15,CHT,1082,0,0,0,,- 當然了 - 你嘗過了苦頭
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.95,1:25:49.15,ENG,1082,0,0,0,,- I sure saw some things. - Oh, you seen some pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.65,1:25:53.45,CHT,1083,0,0,0,,- 也嘗過甜頭？ - 嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.65,1:25:53.45,ENG,1083,0,0,0,,- Some joy, too? - Sure. Sure, I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.55,1:25:57.65,CHT,1084,0,0,0,,我就是想聽你親口說這些 瞧瞧你呀
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.55,1:25:57.65,ENG,1084,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what I want to hear. Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.75,1:26:01.25,CHT,1085,0,0,0,,- 蒂奇上哪兒去了？ - 哦，孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.75,1:26:01.25,ENG,1085,0,0,0,,- Where's Tizzy? - Oh, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.75,1:26:07.65,CHT,1086,0,0,0,,韋瑟斯走了，上個月 睡覺的時候去的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.75,1:26:07.65,ENG,1086,0,0,0,,Mr. Weathers died in his sleep one night last April.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.75,1:26:11.15,CHT,1087,0,0,0,,- 媽媽，您節哀 - 別操心我了，孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.75,1:26:11.15,ENG,1087,0,0,0,,- Mama, I'm so sorry. - Don't you worry about that, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.95,1:26:15.55,CHT,1088,0,0,0,,現在還活著的也就那麼一兩個
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.95,1:26:15.55,ENG,1088,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, it's only one or two of them left now.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.65,1:26:17.15,CHT,1089,0,0,0,,不過都還挺樂呵
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.65,1:26:17.15,ENG,1089,0,0,0,,They all just about new.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.25,1:26:21.15,CHT,1090,0,0,0,,他們應該和別人一樣 也都在等著那一天吧
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.25,1:26:21.15,ENG,1090,0,0,0,,Guess they're waiting their turn like everybody else, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.25,1:26:23.95,CHT,1091,0,0,0,,你能回家陪我，我就知足了！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.25,1:26:23.95,ENG,1091,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're back home with me!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.05,1:26:27.15,CHT,1092,0,0,0,,咱得趕緊給你找個媳婦，再找個工作 就這麼定了！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.05,1:26:27.15,ENG,1092,0,0,0,,Now, we're gonna have to find you a wife and a new job! That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.25,1:26:29.15,CHT,1093,0,0,0,,快進來，幫我擺桌子
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.25,1:26:29.15,ENG,1093,0,0,0,,Come on in here, help me with this table.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.35,1:26:33.95,CHT,1094,0,0,0,,本傑明
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.35,1:26:33.95,ENG,1094,0,0,0,,Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.05,1:26:37.15,CHT,1095,0,0,0,,別費勁了，她全聾了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.05,1:26:37.15,ENG,1095,0,0,0,,You're wasting your time, baby. She's stone deaf.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.25,1:26:41.35,CHT,1096,0,0,0,,你住以前德瑟羅住的房間
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.25,1:26:41.35,ENG,1096,0,0,0,,Oh, and you'll be staying in what was Mrs. DeSeroux's old room.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.45,1:26:44.35,CHT,1097,0,0,0,,你太大個了 再和別人擠一間可不像話
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.45,1:26:44.35,ENG,1097,0,0,0,,You're too big to be rooming with anybody else.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.45,1:26:51.05,CHT,1098,0,0,0,,回家的感覺，很奇妙
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.45,1:26:51.05,ENG,1098,0,0,0,,It's a funny thing about coming home.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.75,1:26:55.45,CHT,1099,0,0,0,,一切看起來都是一樣的 聞起來也是，摸起來也是
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.75,1:26:55.45,ENG,1099,0,0,0,,Looks the same, smells the same, feels the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.25,1:27:02.05,CHT,1100,0,0,0,,我說沒說過，我被閃電擊中過七次？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.25,1:27:02.05,ENG,1100,0,0,0,,Did I ever tell you I've been struck by lightning seven times?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.75,1:27:07.15,CHT,1101,0,0,0,,有一次我就那麼好端端地開著車 心裡想著自己的事
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.75,1:27:07.15,ENG,1101,0,0,0,,Once when I was sitting in my truck, just minding my own business.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.05,1:27:16.45,CHT,1102,0,0,0,,我才意識到，其實變的，只有你自己
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.05,1:27:16.45,ENG,1102,0,0,0,,You realize what's changed is you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.15,1:27:23.15,CHT,1103,0,0,0,,我回來後不久的某個清晨…
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.15,1:27:23.15,ENG,1103,0,0,0,,And late one morning, not long after I'd been back...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.55,1:27:24.85,CHT,1104,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.55,1:27:24.85,ENG,1104,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.95,1:27:48.05,CHT,1105,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.95,1:27:48.05,ENG,1105,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.65,1:27:56.45,CHT,1106,0,0,0,,- 請問，奎尼在嗎？ - 黛西？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.65,1:27:56.45,ENG,1106,0,0,0,,- Excuse me, is Queenie here? - Daisy?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.25,1:28:03.85,CHT,1107,0,0,0,,- 是我啊，本傑明 - 本傑明？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.25,1:28:03.85,ENG,1107,0,0,0,,- It's me, Benjamin. - Benjamin?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.55,1:28:09.55,CHT,1108,0,0,0,,哦，天！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.55,1:28:09.55,ENG,1108,0,0,0,,Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.85,1:28:14.75,CHT,1109,0,0,0,,真的是你！本傑明！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.85,1:28:14.75,ENG,1109,0,0,0,,Of course it's you! Benjamin!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.85,1:28:19.75,CHT,1110,0,0,0,,你過得怎麼樣？ 咱們太久沒見了！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.85,1:28:19.75,ENG,1110,0,0,0,,How are you? It's been such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.85,1:28:22.55,CHT,1111,0,0,0,,我有好多事情要問你 你什麼時候回來的？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.85,1:28:22.55,ENG,1111,0,0,0,,There's so much I want to know. When did you get back?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.65,1:28:24.05,CHT,1112,0,0,0,,我回來也沒幾周
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.65,1:28:24.05,ENG,1112,0,0,0,,Well, I got back a few weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.15,1:28:28.15,CHT,1113,0,0,0,,我上次問奎尼，她說你還在打仗 說是在海上的哪兒
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.15,1:28:28.15,ENG,1113,0,0,0,,I spoke to Queenie, she said you were in the war, somewhere at sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.25,1:28:32.05,CHT,1114,0,0,0,,- 我們都擔心死你了 - 哦，我挺好的
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.25,1:28:32.05,ENG,1114,0,0,0,,- We were so, so worried about you. - Oh, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.15,1:28:35.95,CHT,1115,0,0,0,,瞧瞧你啊，真是好看
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.15,1:28:35.95,ENG,1115,0,0,0,,Well, look at you. You're so lovely.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.75,1:28:39.55,CHT,1116,0,0,0,,你後來就不給我寫信了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.75,1:28:39.55,ENG,1116,0,0,0,,You stopped writing.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.65,1:28:46.75,CHT,1117,0,0,0,,“我離開的時候，她還只是個小女孩 如今，卻已出落成了窈窕淑女”
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.65,1:28:46.75,ENG,1117,0,0,0,,"When I had left, she was a girl. And a woman had taken her place.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.15,1:28:50.25,CHT,1118,0,0,0,,“她是我所見過的人中，最美的女子”
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.15,1:28:50.25,ENG,1118,0,0,0,,"She was the most beautiful woman I'd ever seen."
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.35,1:28:51.75,CHT,1119,0,0,0,,美
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.35,1:28:51.75,ENG,1119,0,0,0,,Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.95,1:28:55.75,CHT,1120,0,0,0,,是“最美”
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.95,1:28:55.75,ENG,1120,0,0,0,,"The most beautiful."
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.55,1:28:59.25,CHT,1121,0,0,0,,- 你還記得富勒奶奶嗎？ - 當然了，怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.55,1:28:59.25,ENG,1121,0,0,0,,- You remember Grandma Fuller? - Why, sure I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.35,1:29:02.45,CHT,1122,0,0,0,,- 她過世了 - 我聽說了，節哀
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.35,1:29:02.45,ENG,1122,0,0,0,,- She passed. - I heard that. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.55,1:29:07.15,CHT,1CHT,0,0,0,,真不敢想，我們又見面了 這一定是緣分
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.55,1:29:07.15,ENG,1CHT,0,0,0,,I just can't believe we're both here. Must be fate.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.25,1:29:09.15,CHT,1124,0,0,0,,不對不對，他們管這叫什麼來著？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.25,1:29:09.15,ENG,1124,0,0,0,,No, no, what do they call it?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.25,1:29:10.65,CHT,1125,0,0,0,,天意
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.25,1:29:10.65,ENG,1125,0,0,0,,Kismet.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.75,1:29:12.65,CHT,1126,0,0,0,,你知道愛德格·西嗎？ 就是那個會通靈的？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.75,1:29:12.65,ENG,1126,0,0,0,,Do you know about Edgar Cayce, the psychic?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.75,1:29:13.75,CHT,1127,0,0,0,,應該沒…
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.75,1:29:13.75,ENG,1127,0,0,0,,I don't believe I...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.85,1:29:16.75,CHT,1128,0,0,0,,他說，萬事萬物都是註定的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.85,1:29:16.75,ENG,1128,0,0,0,,He says that everything is predetermined,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.85,1:29:20.25,CHT,1129,0,0,0,,不過我寧願把這當成緣分
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.85,1:29:20.25,ENG,1129,0,0,0,,but I like to think of it as fate.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.45,1:29:26.65,CHT,1130,0,0,0,,雖然也搞不懂這到底是怎麼回事 我還是很高興咱們重逢了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.45,1:29:26.65,ENG,1130,0,0,0,,I'm not sure how it works, but I'm glad it happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.75,1:29:30.35,CHT,1131,0,0,0,,你去過曼哈頓嗎？ 就在我住的地方河對面
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.75,1:29:30.35,ENG,1131,0,0,0,,Have you been to Manhattan? It's right across the river from me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.45,1:29:32.65,CHT,1132,0,0,0,,要是我站在床上
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.45,1:29:32.65,ENG,1132,0,0,0,,Now, I can see the Empire State Building
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.75,1:29:34.45,CHT,1133,0,0,0,,就可以望見帝國大廈
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.75,1:29:34.45,ENG,1133,0,0,0,,if I stand on my bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.55,1:29:36.55,CHT,1134,0,0,0,,說說你吧？你都去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.55,1:29:36.55,ENG,1134,0,0,0,,What about you? Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.65,1:29:40.25,CHT,1135,0,0,0,,全都告訴我，上次你寫信說 你去俄國了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.65,1:29:40.25,ENG,1135,0,0,0,,Tell me everything. Last time you wrote, you said you'd been to Russia.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.35,1:29:44.55,CHT,1136,0,0,0,,我一直想去那呢 那兒真像別人說的那麼冷嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.35,1:29:44.55,ENG,1136,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to go to Russia. Is it as cold as they say?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.65,1:29:47.45,CHT,1137,0,0,0,,- 冷多了 - 我的天呀
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.65,1:29:47.45,ENG,1137,0,0,0,,- Twice as cold. - My goodness.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.05,1:29:52.65,CHT,1138,0,0,0,,大家嘴上都說你不一樣 我可是真的覺得你不是一般人
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.05,1:29:52.65,ENG,1138,0,0,0,,We always said you were different. But I think you really are.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.85,1:29:58.35,CHT,1139,0,0,0,,你還說你遇上了你喜歡的人 最後有結果嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.85,1:29:58.35,ENG,1139,0,0,0,,You wrote that you met somebody. Did it work out?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.85,1:30:00.55,CHT,1140,0,0,0,,還是沒成
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.85,1:30:00.55,ENG,1140,0,0,0,,It ran its course.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.85,1:30:03.95,CHT,1141,0,0,0,,嘿，還記得這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.85,1:30:03.95,ENG,1141,0,0,0,,Hey, do you remember this?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.85,1:30:17.55,CHT,1142,0,0,0,,“照片裡畫的是大袋鼠
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.85,1:30:17.55,ENG,1142,0,0,0,,"This is the picture of Old Man Kangaroo
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.65,1:30:19.75,CHT,1143,0,0,0,,下午五點，他終於會蹦蹦跳了”
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.65,1:30:19.75,ENG,1143,0,0,0,,"at 5:00 in the afternoon."
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.55,1:30:23.75,CHT,1144,0,0,0,,一起吃個晚飯好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.55,1:30:23.75,ENG,1144,0,0,0,,Would you like to have dinner?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.25,1:30:34.15,CHT,1145,0,0,0,,我有沒有跟你說過 我跟著巴蘭欽跳舞呀？ （著名芭蕾舞導演）
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.25,1:30:34.15,ENG,1145,0,0,0,,Did I tell you that I danced for Balanchine?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.85,1:30:39.35,CHT,1146,0,0,0,,他可是個有名的編舞大師 他說我的線條很完美
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.85,1:30:39.35,ENG,1146,0,0,0,,Oh, he's a famous choreographer. He said that I had perfect line.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.15,1:30:45.65,CHT,1147,0,0,0,,知道嗎，有一個排練，有人摔倒
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.15,1:30:45.65,ENG,1147,0,0,0,,You know, in a rehearsal once, a dancer fell.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.75,1:30:48.55,CHT,1148,0,0,0,,然後他…就把這個動作 編進舞蹈裡去了！
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.75,1:30:48.55,ENG,1148,0,0,0,,And he just... He just put it right into the production.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.65,1:30:52.15,CHT,1149,0,0,0,,你能想像那情形嗎？ 在一部…經典芭蕾舞劇裡
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.65,1:30:52.15,ENG,1149,0,0,0,,I mean, can you imagine that? Like in a... In a classical ballet?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.25,1:30:55.45,CHT,1150,0,0,0,,讓一個演員，故意跌倒
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.25,1:30:55.45,ENG,1150,0,0,0,,You know, a dancer, intentionally falling.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.55,1:30:59.25,CHT,1151,0,0,0,,如今形容舞蹈有個新詞了 叫“抽象”
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.55,1:30:59.25,ENG,1151,0,0,0,,There's a whole new word for dance now. It's called "abstract."
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.35,1:31:00.65,CHT,1152,0,0,0,,當然了，有名的大師不止他一個
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.35,1:31:00.65,ENG,1152,0,0,0,,No, he's not the only one, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.75,1:31:04.65,CHT,1153,0,0,0,,還有林肯·柯爾斯坦 露西亞·切斯，哦，對…
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.75,1:31:04.65,ENG,1153,0,0,0,,There's Lincoln Kirstein and Lucia Chase, and oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.75,1:31:07.25,CHT,1154,0,0,0,,還有阿格尼·德·米爾
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.75,1:31:07.25,ENG,1154,0,0,0,,Oh, there's Agnes de Mille.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.35,1:31:09.45,CHT,1155,0,0,0,,她根本就不管什麼條條框框
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.35,1:31:09.45,ENG,1155,0,0,0,,She's just torn up all those conventions,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.55,1:31:11.55,CHT,1156,0,0,0,,就是“抬頭挺胸”那一套
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.55,1:31:11.55,ENG,1156,0,0,0,,you know, all that straight-up-and-down stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.65,1:31:14.85,CHT,1157,0,0,0,,她說舞蹈最重要的不是形式 而是舞者的感覺
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.65,1:31:14.85,ENG,1157,0,0,0,,It's not about the formality of the dance, it's about what the dancer's feeling.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.95,1:31:17.65,CHT,1158,0,0,0,,她跟我說的這些 就像是另一個全新的世界
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.95,1:31:17.65,ENG,1158,0,0,0,,As she told me about this big new world,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.75,1:31:20.25,CHT,1159,0,0,0,,那些名字，對我來說，啥也不是
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.75,1:31:20.25,ENG,1159,0,0,0,,names that didn't mean a thing to me,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.35,1:31:22.35,CHT,1160,0,0,0,,其實她說什麼，我也沒怎麼聽進去
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.35,1:31:22.35,ENG,1160,0,0,0,,I didn't really hear very much of what she was saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.45,1:31:24.75,CHT,1161,0,0,0,,一切都是全新的，現代的，美式的！
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.45,1:31:24.75,ENG,1161,0,0,0,,It's new and it's modern and it's American.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.85,1:31:27.95,CHT,1162,0,0,0,,只有他們瞭解我們的活力和形體
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.85,1:31:27.95,ENG,1162,0,0,0,,They understand our vigor and our physicality.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.05,1:31:30.25,CHT,1163,0,0,0,,哦，天，我是不是說太多了呀
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.05,1:31:30.25,ENG,1163,0,0,0,,Oh, my God. I've just been talking and talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.45,1:31:34.85,CHT,1164,0,0,0,,沒有沒有，我喜歡聽你講 我不知道你還抽煙
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.45,1:31:34.85,ENG,1164,0,0,0,,No, no, I've enjoyed listening. I didn't know you smoked.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.95,1:31:36.45,CHT,1165,0,0,0,,我夠大了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.95,1:31:36.45,ENG,1165,0,0,0,,I'm old enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.85,1:31:42.35,CHT,1166,0,0,0,,除了這個，還能做很多別的
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.85,1:31:42.35,ENG,1166,0,0,0,,I'm old enough for a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.25,1:31:47.75,CHT,1167,0,0,0,,在紐約那會，我們整晚刷夜
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.25,1:31:47.75,ENG,1167,0,0,0,,In New York, we stay up all night,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.95,1:31:51.75,CHT,1168,0,0,0,,然後看著太陽爬上倉庫屋頂
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.95,1:31:51.75,ENG,1168,0,0,0,,watch the sun come up over the warehouses.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.15,1:31:56.45,CHT,1169,0,0,0,,在那兒，總是有新鮮事可做
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.15,1:31:56.45,ENG,1169,0,0,0,,There's always something to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.15,1:32:16.25,CHT,1170,0,0,0,,明天我就得回去了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.15,1:32:16.25,ENG,1170,0,0,0,,I have to go back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.35,1:32:19.55,CHT,1171,0,0,0,,- 這麼快 - 真想留下來
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.35,1:32:19.55,ENG,1171,0,0,0,,- So soon. - Wish I could stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.35,1:32:27.45,CHT,1172,0,0,0,,如今，跳舞的人 都不需要服裝和背景了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.35,1:32:27.45,ENG,1172,0,0,0,,Dancers don't need costumes or scenery anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.55,1:32:31.15,CHT,1173,0,0,0,,我都能想像 自己不穿衣服跳舞的樣子
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.55,1:32:31.15,ENG,1173,0,0,0,,I can imagine dancing completely naked.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.45,1:32:34.75,CHT,1174,0,0,0,,你讀過D.H.勞倫斯的書嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.45,1:32:34.75,ENG,1174,0,0,0,,Have you read D.H. Lawrence?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.85,1:32:36.95,CHT,1175,0,0,0,,- 呃… - 他的書都被禁了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.85,1:32:36.95,ENG,1175,0,0,0,,- Well... - His books were banned.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.15,1:32:40.65,CHT,1176,0,0,0,,那些文字，讀起來，就像做愛
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.15,1:32:40.65,ENG,1176,0,0,0,,The words are like making love.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.15,1:33:29.75,CHT,1177,0,0,0,,在舞團，大家必須互相信任
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.15,1:33:29.75,ENG,1177,0,0,0,,In our company, we have to trust each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.05,1:33:38.75,CHT,1178,0,0,0,,性，就是條件之一
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.05,1:33:38.75,ENG,1178,0,0,0,,Sex is a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.15,1:33:46.05,CHT,1179,0,0,0,,知道嘛，很多跳舞的都是女同
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.15,1:33:46.05,ENG,1179,0,0,0,,You know, a lot of the dancers are lesbians.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.25,1:33:51.25,CHT,1180,0,0,0,,有一個女人，就想跟我睡
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.25,1:33:51.25,ENG,1180,0,0,0,,There was one woman who wanted to sleep with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.65,1:34:01.65,CHT,1181,0,0,0,,- 你聽了會不高興嗎？ - 關於哪部分？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.65,1:34:01.65,ENG,1181,0,0,0,,- Does that upset you? - Which part?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.75,1:34:05.15,CHT,1182,0,0,0,,就是有人想和我睡那部分
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.75,1:34:05.15,ENG,1182,0,0,0,,Somebody wanting to sleep with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.65,1:34:06.85,CHT,1183,0,0,0,,你很性感
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.65,1:34:06.85,ENG,1183,0,0,0,,You're a desirable woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.95,1:34:10.65,CHT,1184,0,0,0,,我想，他們很多人都會想和你睡吧
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.95,1:34:10.65,ENG,1184,0,0,0,,I would think most of them would want to sleep with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.75,1:34:12.85,CHT,1185,0,0,0,,咱們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.75,1:34:12.85,ENG,1185,0,0,0,,Let's go back to the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.85,1:34:16.25,CHT,1186,0,0,0,,或者到哪開間房
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.85,1:34:16.25,ENG,1186,0,0,0,,Or we could get a room somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.25,1:34:22.35,CHT,1187,0,0,0,,- 你可以脫下夾克… - 這樣似乎不好，黛西
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.25,1:34:22.35,ENG,1187,0,0,0,,- We could lay down your jacket. - I don't know, Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.55,1:34:27.85,CHT,1188,0,0,0,,也不是說我不想還是怎麼的 我只是怕，會讓你失望
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.55,1:34:27.85,ENG,1188,0,0,0,,It's not that I wouldn't like to or anything. I think I'll just disappoint you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.75,1:34:31.85,CHT,1189,0,0,0,,本傑明，我和更老的人都在一起過
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.75,1:34:31.85,ENG,1189,0,0,0,,Oh, Benjamin, I've been with older men.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.65,1:34:34.65,CHT,1190,0,0,0,,明早你就要回紐約了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.65,1:34:34.65,ENG,1190,0,0,0,,You're going back to New York in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.75,1:34:37.05,CHT,1191,0,0,0,,你該和朋友在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.75,1:34:37.05,ENG,1191,0,0,0,,You should be with your friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.05,1:34:40.55,CHT,1192,0,0,0,,- 你只能年輕一次 - 我夠大了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.05,1:34:40.55,ENG,1192,0,0,0,,- You're only young once. - Oh, I'm old enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.65,1:34:43.25,CHT,1193,0,0,0,,黛西，就是，今晚不行
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.65,1:34:43.25,ENG,1193,0,0,0,,Daisy, just not tonight, is all.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.85,1:34:58.95,CHT,1194,0,0,0,,我們可以去聽聽音樂
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.85,1:34:58.95,ENG,1194,0,0,0,,We could go hear some music.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.25,1:35:03.95,CHT,1195,0,0,0,,我們的生命，因為各種各樣的機遇 而變得更有意義
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.25,1:35:03.95,ENG,1195,0,0,0,,Our lives are defined by opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.75,1:35:06.75,CHT,1196,0,0,0,,甚至那些我們錯過的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.75,1:35:06.75,ENG,1196,0,0,0,,Even the ones we miss.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.65,1:35:11.25,CHT,1197,0,0,0,,你看起來，如此英俊，與眾不同
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.65,1:35:11.25,ENG,1197,0,0,0,,You look so handsome and so distinguished.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.35,1:35:13.55,CHT,1198,0,0,0,,據說颶風不會過來 剛好從我們這塊刮過去
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.35,1:35:13.55,ENG,1198,0,0,0,,They're saying the hurricane's gonna miss us, blow right on by.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.65,1:35:18.25,CHT,1199,0,0,0,,- 太好了 - 我在毯子下面和媽媽一起躺著
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.65,1:35:18.25,ENG,1199,0,0,0,,- Oh, that's great. - I'll stay under the blankets with Mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.35,1:35:22.45,CHT,1200,0,0,0,,她什麼也沒說…本傑明你在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.35,1:35:22.45,ENG,1200,0,0,0,,She says nothing... Benjamin?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.35,1:35:25.45,CHT,1201,0,0,0,,“我的生命…
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.35,1:35:25.45,ENG,1201,0,0,0,,"Things were becoming different..."
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.55,1:35:26.65,CHT,1202,0,0,0,,又有了不一樣的變化
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.55,1:35:26.65,ENG,1202,0,0,0,,... for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.85,1:35:30.35,CHT,1203,0,0,0,,我的頭髮，越來越黑，像野草一樣生長
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.85,1:35:30.35,ENG,1203,0,0,0,,My hair had very little gray and grew like weeds.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.55,1:35:34.25,CHT,1204,0,0,0,,我的嗅覺更加靈敏 聽覺，也加更敏銳
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.55,1:35:34.25,ENG,1204,0,0,0,,My sense of smell was keener. My hearing, more acute.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.35,1:35:37.05,CHT,1205,0,0,0,,我走得更快更遠
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.35,1:35:37.05,ENG,1205,0,0,0,,I could walk further and faster.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.15,1:35:42.85,CHT,1206,0,0,0,,別人都在變老 而我，卻獨自一人，越來越年輕
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.15,1:35:42.85,ENG,1206,0,0,0,,While everybody else was aging, I was getting younger, all alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.95,1:35:47.15,CHT,1207,0,0,0,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.95,1:35:47.15,ENG,1207,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.55,1:35:49.85,CHT,1208,0,0,0,,本傑明
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.55,1:35:49.85,ENG,1208,0,0,0,,Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.85,1:35:54.05,CHT,1209,0,0,0,,- 還記得我嗎？ - 當然了，巴頓先生
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.85,1:35:54.05,ENG,1209,0,0,0,,- Do you remember me? - Well, sure I do, Mr. Button.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.75,1:35:58.35,CHT,1210,0,0,0,,- 你這是怎麼了？ - 該死的腳，感染了，那個…
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.75,1:35:58.35,ENG,1210,0,0,0,,- What happened to you? - Darn foot. Got infected, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.05,1:36:01.25,CHT,1211,0,0,0,,歡迎回家，朋友
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.05,1:36:01.25,ENG,1211,0,0,0,,Welcome home, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.95,1:36:07.05,CHT,1212,0,0,0,,你還是喜歡把威士卡 和別的酒混起來喝啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.95,1:36:07.05,ENG,1212,0,0,0,,I see you're still drinking your Sazerac with whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.15,1:36:08.35,CHT,1213,0,0,0,,呵，習慣這東西
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.15,1:36:08.35,ENG,1213,0,0,0,,Creature of habit.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.45,1:36:10.55,CHT,1214,0,0,0,,你還常去波旁大道那邊的工廠嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.45,1:36:10.55,ENG,1214,0,0,0,,You still visiting the house on Bourbon Street?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.65,1:36:12.45,CHT,1215,0,0,0,,很久沒去了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.65,1:36:12.45,ENG,1215,0,0,0,,Not for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.05,1:36:16.15,CHT,1216,0,0,0,,說來有趣
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.05,1:36:16.15,ENG,1216,0,0,0,,Interesting times, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.25,1:36:20.65,CHT,1217,0,0,0,,我們一開始每天做四萬個紐扣 到後來一天50萬
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.25,1:36:20.65,ENG,1217,0,0,0,,We went from making 40,000 to nearly half a million buttons a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.75,1:36:22.75,CHT,1218,0,0,0,,廠裡的工人多了十倍
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.75,1:36:22.75,ENG,1218,0,0,0,,We employed 10 times the number of people.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.85,1:36:25.35,CHT,1219,0,0,0,,我們沒日沒夜地工作
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.85,1:36:25.35,ENG,1219,0,0,0,,We were operating around the clock.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.95,1:36:31.25,CHT,1220,0,0,0,,說來慚愧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.95,1:36:31.25,ENG,1220,0,0,0,,Damn shame.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.45,1:36:35.35,CHT,1221,0,0,0,,戰爭讓紐扣生意更紅火了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.45,1:36:35.35,ENG,1221,0,0,0,,The war has been kind to the button industry.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.15,1:36:39.45,CHT,1222,0,0,0,,知道嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.15,1:36:39.45,ENG,1222,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.75,1:36:45.05,CHT,1223,0,0,0,,我病了，不知道還能活多久
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.75,1:36:45.05,ENG,1223,0,0,0,,I'm sick. I don't know how much longer I have.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.15,1:36:47.95,CHT,1224,0,0,0,,- 您也別太難過了，巴頓先生 - 別這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.15,1:36:47.95,ENG,1224,0,0,0,,- I'm sorry to hear that, Mr. Button. - No...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.35,1:36:52.45,CHT,1225,0,0,0,,我沒什麼朋友，一直都是獨來獨往
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.35,1:36:52.45,ENG,1225,0,0,0,,I don't have any people. I keep to myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.95,1:36:57.95,CHT,1226,0,0,0,,但願你不要介意，不過，如果有可能
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.95,1:36:57.95,ENG,1226,0,0,0,,I hope you don't mind, but, whenever possible,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.05,1:37:00.05,CHT,1227,0,0,0,,我希望你可以多陪陪我
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.05,1:37:00.05,ENG,1227,0,0,0,,I'd enjoy your company.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.15,1:37:02.65,CHT,1228,0,0,0,,如果力所能及，我當然會的
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.15,1:37:02.65,ENG,1228,0,0,0,,I'll certainly do what I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.95,1:37:08.85,CHT,1229,0,0,0,,本傑明，你懂紐扣生意嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.95,1:37:08.85,ENG,1229,0,0,0,,Benjamin, do you know anything about buttons?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.45,1:37:17.15,CHT,1230,0,0,0,,到現在，巴頓紐扣廠已經 在家族中傳承了124年了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.45,1:37:17.15,ENG,1230,0,0,0,,Now, Button's Buttons has been in our family for 124 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.75,1:37:22.35,CHT,1231,0,0,0,,我的祖父是個裁縫 只在里士滿開了間小裁縫鋪
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.75,1:37:22.35,ENG,1231,0,0,0,,My grandfather was a tailor, and he had a small shop in Richmond.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.45,1:37:24.85,CHT,1232,0,0,0,,內戰過後，他搬到了新奧爾良
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.45,1:37:24.85,ENG,1232,0,0,0,,After the Civil War, he moved to New Orleans,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.95,1:37:30.05,CHT,1233,0,0,0,,在那兒，我父親奮發圖強 開始經營自己的紐扣生意
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.95,1:37:30.05,ENG,1233,0,0,0,,where my father had the wisdom to make our own buttons.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.15,1:37:34.95,CHT,1234,0,0,0,,於是，在他的大力改革下 小裁縫鋪成長到了今天這樣的規模
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.15,1:37:34.95,ENG,1234,0,0,0,,So, with his help, the tailor shop grew to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.75,1:37:38.35,CHT,1235,0,0,0,,如今，我卻連衣服都不會自己縫了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.75,1:37:38.35,ENG,1235,0,0,0,,And today, I can't sew a stitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.55,1:37:44.85,CHT,1236,0,0,0,,這故事真的很有意思
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.55,1:37:44.85,ENG,1236,0,0,0,,That's very, very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.35,1:37:50.95,CHT,1237,0,0,0,,很顯然，您自己幹得也不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.35,1:37:50.95,ENG,1237,0,0,0,,You sure have done well for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.85,1:37:55.95,CHT,1238,0,0,0,,那我能幫上什麼忙呢，巴頓先生？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.85,1:37:55.95,ENG,1238,0,0,0,,So, what can I do for you, Mr. Button?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.45,1:38:01.45,CHT,1239,0,0,0,,本傑明，你是我兒子
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.45,1:38:01.45,ENG,1239,0,0,0,,Benjamin? You're my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.05,1:38:11.65,CHT,1240,0,0,0,,抱歉，我以前從沒提起過
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.05,1:38:11.65,ENG,1240,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry I never told you before.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.85,1:38:17.25,CHT,1241,0,0,0,,你是大戰結束那晚出生的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.85,1:38:17.25,ENG,1241,0,0,0,,You were born the night the Great War ended.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.15,1:38:22.85,CHT,1242,0,0,0,,你母親難產而死
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.15,1:38:22.85,ENG,1242,0,0,0,,Your mother died giving birth to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.35,1:38:26.55,CHT,1243,0,0,0,,我以為你是怪物
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.35,1:38:26.55,ENG,1243,0,0,0,,I thought you were a monster.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.05,1:38:33.35,CHT,1244,0,0,0,,我向你母親保證過 保證你會平平安安
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.05,1:38:33.35,ENG,1244,0,0,0,,I promised your mother I'd make sure you were safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.75,1:38:42.25,CHT,1245,0,0,0,,對不起，我不該拋棄你
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.75,1:38:42.25,ENG,1245,0,0,0,,I should never have abandoned you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.35,1:38:47.75,CHT,1246,0,0,0,,我母親？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.35,1:38:47.75,ENG,1246,0,0,0,,My mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.05,1:38:52.05,CHT,1247,0,0,0,,龐恰特雷恩湖邊的避暑別墅
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.05,1:38:52.05,ENG,1247,0,0,0,,At the summer house on Lake Pontchartrain.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.15,1:38:55.55,CHT,1248,0,0,0,,我小時候，總喜歡比大家早起
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.15,1:38:55.55,ENG,1248,0,0,0,,When I was a boy, I'd love to wake up before anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.65,1:38:58.65,CHT,1249,0,0,0,,然後跑到湖邊，迎接新一天的開始
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.65,1:38:58.65,ENG,1249,0,0,0,,run down to that lake and watch the day begin.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.35,1:39:02.95,CHT,1250,0,0,0,,那時候，我覺得自己 好像是這世上唯一一個活人
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.35,1:39:02.95,ENG,1250,0,0,0,,It was as if I was the only one alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.75,1:39:07.45,CHT,1251,0,0,0,,第一眼看到她，我就愛上她了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.75,1:39:07.45,ENG,1251,0,0,0,,I fell in love the first time I saw her.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.05,1:39:10.65,CHT,1252,0,0,0,,你母親叫卡洛琳·墨菲
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.05,1:39:10.65,ENG,1252,0,0,0,,Your mother's name was Caroline Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.35,1:39:14.15,CHT,1253,0,0,0,,她在你爺爺的廚房裡幹活
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.35,1:39:14.15,ENG,1253,0,0,0,,She worked in your grandfather's kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.45,1:39:19.15,CHT,1254,0,0,0,,她是都柏林人
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.45,1:39:19.15,ENG,1254,0,0,0,,She's from Dublin.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.85,1:39:24.25,CHT,1255,0,0,0,,1903年，她和她的兄弟姐妹 就到美國來謀生了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.85,1:39:24.25,ENG,1255,0,0,0,,In 1903, Caroline and all her brothers and sisters came to live here,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.35,1:39:25.85,CHT,1256,0,0,0,,就住在新奧爾良
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.35,1:39:25.85,ENG,1256,0,0,0,,in New Orleans.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.95,1:39:30.85,CHT,1257,0,0,0,,我常常找藉口下廚房
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.95,1:39:30.85,ENG,1257,0,0,0,,I'd find excuses to go down to that kitchen
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.65,1:39:33.75,CHT,1258,0,0,0,,就為了看她一眼
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.65,1:39:33.75,ENG,1258,0,0,0,,just so I could look at her.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.15,1:39:43.85,CHT,1259,0,0,0,,1918年4月25號，那天 是我一生中最快樂的時光
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.15,1:39:43.85,ENG,1259,0,0,0,,April 25th, 1918. Happiest day of my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.65,1:39:46.85,CHT,1260,0,0,0,,那天，我迎娶了你母親
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.65,1:39:46.85,ENG,1260,0,0,0,,The day I married your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.65,1:39:50.75,CHT,1261,0,0,0,,你為什麼不早點告訴我？
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.65,1:39:50.75,ENG,1261,0,0,0,,Why didn't you just tell me?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.65,1:39:54.45,CHT,1262,0,0,0,,我準備把遺產都留給你
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.65,1:39:54.45,ENG,1262,0,0,0,,I plan on leaving everything I have to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.05,1:39:58.45,CHT,1263,0,0,0,,- 我該走了 - 去哪？
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.05,1:39:58.45,ENG,1263,0,0,0,,- I have to go. - Where?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.55,1:40:00.85,CHT,1264,0,0,0,,回家
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.55,1:40:00.85,ENG,1264,0,0,0,,Home.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.55,1:40:02.95,CHT,1265,0,0,0,,他怎麼想的，嗯？
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.55,1:40:02.95,ENG,1265,0,0,0,,And what does he think, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.05,1:40:04.35,CHT,1266,0,0,0,,他以為自己這麼冒出來
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.05,1:40:04.35,ENG,1266,0,0,0,,He thinks he can just show up
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.45,1:40:06.25,CHT,1267,0,0,0,,然後就沒事了？
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.45,1:40:06.25,ENG,1267,0,0,0,,and everything's supposed to be fine and dandy.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.35,1:40:08.95,CHT,1268,0,0,0,,然後大家就能做朋友了？
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.35,1:40:08.95,ENG,1268,0,0,0,,Everybody's just supposed to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.05,1:40:11.95,CHT,1269,0,0,0,,要我說，這事我跟他沒完
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.05,1:40:11.95,ENG,1269,0,0,0,,Well, he got another thing coming, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.05,1:40:15.45,CHT,1270,0,0,0,,老天有眼，我跟他沒完！
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.05,1:40:15.45,ENG,1270,0,0,0,,God be my witness, he got another thing coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.55,1:40:18.65,CHT,1271,0,0,0,,他丟掉你那晚，只留了18塊錢
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.55,1:40:18.65,ENG,1271,0,0,0,,He left us $18 that night you was found.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.75,1:40:20.55,CHT,1272,0,0,0,,18張皺巴巴的票子！
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.75,1:40:20.55,ENG,1272,0,0,0,,Eighteen ratty dollars
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.65,1:40:22.35,CHT,1273,0,0,0,,- 還有一塊髒兮兮的尿布 - 晚安了，媽
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.65,1:40:22.35,ENG,1273,0,0,0,,- and a filthy diaper. - Good night, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.75,1:40:24.95,CHT,1274,0,0,0,,晚安，寶貝兒
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.75,1:40:24.95,ENG,1274,0,0,0,,Good night, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.25,1:40:42.55,CHT,1275,0,0,0,,我有沒有跟你說過 我被閃電擊中過七次？
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.25,1:40:42.55,ENG,1275,0,0,0,,Did I ever tell you I was struck by lightning seven times?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.35,1:40:46.45,CHT,1276,0,0,0,,有一次，我就那麼好好得遛著狗
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.35,1:40:46.45,ENG,1276,0,0,0,,Once, I was walking my dog down the road.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.45,1:40:55.25,CHT,1277,0,0,0,,現在我瞎了一隻眼，幾乎聽不見
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.45,1:40:55.25,ENG,1277,0,0,0,,I'm blind in the one eye, can't hardly hear,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.55,1:41:01.15,CHT,1278,0,0,0,,還無緣無故抽搐發抖，老是忘東西
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.55,1:41:01.15,ENG,1278,0,0,0,,get twitches and shakes out of nowhere, always losing my line of thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.75,1:41:04.35,CHT,1279,0,0,0,,但你知道嘛？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.75,1:41:04.35,ENG,1279,0,0,0,,But you know what?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.15,1:41:08.05,CHT,1280,0,0,0,,老天爺總是不斷地提醒我 讓我知道自己還活著，有多幸運
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.15,1:41:08.05,ENG,1280,0,0,0,,God keeps reminding me I'm lucky to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.85,1:41:15.35,CHT,1281,0,0,0,,暴風雨快來了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.85,1:41:15.35,ENG,1281,0,0,0,,Storm's coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.35,1:41:45.55,CHT,1282,0,0,0,,可以為您效勞嗎？ 樓上，第一間臥室
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.35,1:41:45.55,ENG,1282,0,0,0,,May I help you, sir? Up the stairs, first bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.65,1:41:46.75,CHT,1283,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.65,1:41:46.75,ENG,1283,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.55,1:42:03.85,CHT,1284,0,0,0,,醒醒
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.55,1:42:03.85,ENG,1284,0,0,0,,Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.35,1:42:08.25,CHT,1285,0,0,0,,我來幫你穿上衣服
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.35,1:42:08.25,ENG,1285,0,0,0,,Let's get you dressed.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.65,1:42:37.25,CHT,1286,0,0,0,,對，就這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.65,1:42:37.25,ENG,1286,0,0,0,,Now that's something.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.65,1:42:41.95,CHT,1287,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.65,1:42:41.95,ENG,1287,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.05,1:43:46.05,CHT,1288,0,0,0,,不順心的時候 你可以像瘋狗那樣發狂
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.05,1:43:46.05,ENG,1288,0,0,0,,You can be mad as a mad dog at the way things went.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.15,1:43:48.55,CHT,1289,0,0,0,,你可以破口大駡，詛咒命運
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.15,1:43:48.55,ENG,1289,0,0,0,,You can swear and curse the Fates.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.15,1:43:52.35,CHT,1290,0,0,0,,但到頭來
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.15,1:43:52.35,ENG,1290,0,0,0,,But when it comes to the end,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.65,1:43:55.35,CHT,1291,0,0,0,,還是得放手
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.65,1:43:55.35,ENG,1291,0,0,0,,you have to let go.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.35,1:44:19.95,CHT,1292,0,0,0,,這葬禮很體面
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.35,1:44:19.95,ENG,1292,0,0,0,,Well, it sure is a beautiful service.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.85,1:44:24.65,CHT,1293,0,0,0,,他會葬在你母親旁邊
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.85,1:44:24.65,ENG,1293,0,0,0,,He'll be buried right next to your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.05,1:44:27.75,CHT,1294,0,0,0,,您就是我母親
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.05,1:44:27.75,ENG,1294,0,0,0,,You're my mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.55,1:44:32.75,CHT,1295,0,0,0,,我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.55,1:44:32.75,ENG,1295,0,0,0,,My baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.35,1:44:39.55,CHT,1296,0,0,0,,我以前還從沒來過紐約
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.35,1:44:39.55,ENG,1296,0,0,0,,Now, I'd never seen New York.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.75,1:46:11.05,CHT,1297,0,0,0,,- 打擾下，我是黛西的朋友 - 這邊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.75,1:46:11.05,ENG,1297,0,0,0,,- Excuse me, I'm a friend of Daisy's. - Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.15,1:46:17.45,CHT,1298,0,0,0,,- 黛西有人找，黛西！ - 來了！
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.15,1:46:17.45,ENG,1298,0,0,0,,- Daisy has company. Daisy! Daisy! - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.85,1:46:21.15,CHT,1299,0,0,0,,- 我們要放衣服 - 是誰找我呀？
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.85,1:46:21.15,ENG,1299,0,0,0,,- We need the wardrobe. - Is somebody looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.75,1:46:25.95,CHT,1300,0,0,0,,- 本傑明 - 嗨
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.75,1:46:25.95,ENG,1300,0,0,0,,- Benjamin. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.25,1:46:31.05,CHT,1301,0,0,0,,- 你來這做什麼？ - 我覺得應該來看看你
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.25,1:46:31.05,ENG,1301,0,0,0,,- What are you doing here? - Thought I'd come visit.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.15,1:46:34.55,CHT,1302,0,0,0,,要是可以，約你出去轉轉
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.15,1:46:34.55,ENG,1302,0,0,0,,Spend some time with you, if I could.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.75,1:46:40.55,CHT,1303,0,0,0,,真希望你事先給我個電話 這樣我都沒法準備
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.75,1:46:40.55,ENG,1303,0,0,0,,Oh, well, I wish you would've called. You took me by surprise.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.95,1:46:46.05,CHT,1304,0,0,0,,- 要是不喜歡就扔了吧 - 哪裡，謝了，花很好看
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.95,1:46:46.05,ENG,1304,0,0,0,,- You can just throw them out. - No. Thank you, they're lovely.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.75,1:46:51.55,CHT,1305,0,0,0,,我從頭到尾都在看你 你真是…太迷人了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.75,1:46:51.55,ENG,1305,0,0,0,,I couldn't take my eyes off of you. I thought you were mesmerizing.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.55,1:46:56.35,CHT,1306,0,0,0,,謝謝，謝謝你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.55,1:46:56.35,ENG,1306,0,0,0,,Thank you. That's very kind of you to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.65,1:47:03.75,CHT,1307,0,0,0,,我得去換身衣服了 我們幾個要去聚會下
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.65,1:47:03.75,ENG,1307,0,0,0,,I better get changed. A group of us are going to a party.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.85,1:47:07.05,CHT,1308,0,0,0,,- 你來嗎？ - 聽人說有家餐館不錯
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.85,1:47:07.05,ENG,1308,0,0,0,,- Would you want to come? - Someone told me about a restaurant
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.25,1:47:08.45,CHT,1309,0,0,0,,你應該也會喜歡
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.25,1:47:08.45,ENG,1309,0,0,0,,I thought you might enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.55,1:47:11.05,CHT,1310,0,0,0,,我定了位，算是以防萬一
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.55,1:47:11.05,ENG,1310,0,0,0,,I made a reservation, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.15,1:47:14.15,CHT,1311,0,0,0,,不過我們跳完舞之後都會聚聚…
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.15,1:47:14.15,ENG,1311,0,0,0,,Just, all the dancers go out after the show. You're...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.25,1:47:18.05,CHT,1312,0,0,0,,你來我們會很歡迎的 我去換衣服，好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.25,1:47:18.05,ENG,1312,0,0,0,,You're welcome to come with us. I'll get changed. All right?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.55,1:47:26.65,CHT,1313,0,0,0,,她還給俄羅斯芭蕾舞團排過舞
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.55,1:47:26.65,ENG,1313,0,0,0,,She choreographs for the Ballets Russes.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.75,1:47:28.05,CHT,1314,0,0,0,,太神了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.75,1:47:28.05,ENG,1314,0,0,0,,She's divine.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.65,1:47:30.55,CHT,1315,0,0,0,,你真美
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.65,1:47:30.55,ENG,1315,0,0,0,,You were breathtaking.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.25,1:47:37.45,CHT,1316,0,0,0,,小甜心
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.25,1:47:37.45,ENG,1316,0,0,0,,Sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.65,1:47:41.55,CHT,1317,0,0,0,,這是大衛，他也是舞團的
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.65,1:47:41.55,ENG,1317,0,0,0,,This is David. He dances with the company.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.55,1:47:44.55,CHT,1318,0,0,0,,- 這是本傑明 - 誰？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.55,1:47:44.55,ENG,1318,0,0,0,,- This is Benjamin. - Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.65,1:47:47.85,CHT,1319,0,0,0,,- 我跟你說起過他的 - 哦，是你啊，近來可好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.65,1:47:47.85,ENG,1319,0,0,0,,- I told you about him. - Oh, yeah. How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.95,1:47:51.45,CHT,1320,0,0,0,,- 我去給你拿杯喝的 - 嗯，謝了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.95,1:47:51.45,ENG,1320,0,0,0,,- I'll go get you a drink. - All right. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.15,1:48:02.35,CHT,1321,0,0,0,,這麼說，你是她奶奶的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.15,1:48:02.35,ENG,1321,0,0,0,,So, you were a friend of her grandmother's?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.45,1:48:04.35,CHT,1322,0,0,0,,還是就那一類的？
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.45,1:48:04.35,ENG,1322,0,0,0,,Or something like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.45,1:48:07.25,CHT,1323,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.45,1:48:07.25,ENG,1323,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.55,1:48:09.15,CHT,1324,0,0,0,,嘿，失陪
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.55,1:48:09.15,ENG,1324,0,0,0,,Hey, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.45,1:48:32.75,CHT,1325,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.45,1:48:32.75,ENG,1325,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.05,1:48:55.15,CHT,1326,0,0,0,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.05,1:48:55.15,ENG,1326,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.15,1:48:58.65,CHT,1327,0,0,0,,我真不知道你會來
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.15,1:48:58.65,ENG,1327,0,0,0,,Now, I had no idea you were coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.65,1:49:01.15,CHT,1328,0,0,0,,天啊，本傑明
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.65,1:49:01.15,ENG,1328,0,0,0,,Lord, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.75,1:49:07.65,CHT,1329,0,0,0,,你想要我怎樣呢？ 難道要我丟下這一切，跟你走嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.75,1:49:07.65,ENG,1329,0,0,0,,What did you expect? What, you want me to drop everything?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.75,1:49:09.75,CHT,1330,0,0,0,,這可是我的人生
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.75,1:49:09.75,ENG,1330,0,0,0,,Now, this is my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.85,1:49:12.25,CHT,1331,0,0,0,,寶貝兒，去市中心不？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.85,1:49:12.25,ENG,1331,0,0,0,,Babe! You going downtown?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.25,1:49:20.35,CHT,1332,0,0,0,,來吧，你也會玩得很開心的
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.25,1:49:20.35,ENG,1332,0,0,0,,Come on. You'll have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.25,1:49:22.65,CHT,1333,0,0,0,,那兒有很多音樂家和有趣的人
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.25,1:49:22.65,ENG,1333,0,0,0,,There's lots of musicians, interesting people.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.85,1:49:25.75,CHT,1334,0,0,0,,真的不用了，都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.85,1:49:25.75,ENG,1334,0,0,0,,You don't have to do that. This is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.85,1:49:28.25,CHT,1335,0,0,0,,我是該先打個電話
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.85,1:49:28.25,ENG,1335,0,0,0,,I should've called.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.35,1:49:31.15,CHT,1336,0,0,0,,我本以為我突然過來
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.35,1:49:31.15,ENG,1336,0,0,0,,I thought I'd come here
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.25,1:49:33.95,CHT,1337,0,0,0,,會給你一個大驚喜
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.25,1:49:33.95,ENG,1337,0,0,0,,and sweep you off your feet or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.45,1:49:39.95,CHT,1338,0,0,0,,- 黛西，快來吧，出發了！ - 馬上到
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.45,1:49:39.95,ENG,1338,0,0,0,,- Daisy! Come on! Let's go. - Be right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.75,1:49:43.15,CHT,1339,0,0,0,,他看來還不錯
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.75,1:49:43.15,ENG,1339,0,0,0,,Seems nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.45,1:49:46.05,CHT,1340,0,0,0,,你愛他嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.45,1:49:46.05,ENG,1340,0,0,0,,Do you love him?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.25,1:49:50.55,CHT,1341,0,0,0,,應該吧
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.25,1:49:50.55,ENG,1341,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.75,1:49:54.35,CHT,1342,0,0,0,,真替你高興
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.75,1:49:54.35,ENG,1342,0,0,0,,I'm happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.35,1:49:58.45,CHT,1343,0,0,0,,那老家見吧
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.35,1:49:58.45,ENG,1343,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll see you at home.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.05,1:50:02.15,CHT,1344,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.05,1:50:02.15,ENG,1344,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.25,1:50:05.95,CHT,1345,0,0,0,,我很喜歡你的演出！
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.25,1:50:05.95,ENG,1345,0,0,0,,I enjoyed the show!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.55,1:50:18.05,CHT,1346,0,0,0,,他來，是想告訴我，他父親死了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.55,1:50:18.05,ENG,1346,0,0,0,,He came to tell me his father had died.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.55,1:50:25.75,CHT,1347,0,0,0,,- 你也猜不到啊 - 我那時才23歲，我…只是不在乎這些
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.55,1:50:25.75,ENG,1347,0,0,0,,- You couldn't have known. - I was 23. I... I just didn't care.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.35,1:50:29.75,CHT,1348,0,0,0,,那你後來呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.35,1:50:29.75,ENG,1348,0,0,0,,What did you do next?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.85,1:50:36.75,CHT,1349,0,0,0,,有些照片，我記得 就放在包的前袋裡
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.85,1:50:36.75,ENG,1349,0,0,0,,Some photographs, I think, in the front of my bag.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.85,1:50:42.95,CHT,1350,0,0,0,,我那會還挺了不得
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.85,1:50:42.95,ENG,1350,0,0,0,,I was as good a dancer as I was ever gonna be.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.85,1:50:46.75,CHT,1351,0,0,0,,有那麼五年，我…
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.85,1:50:46.75,ENG,1351,0,0,0,,For five years, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.55,1:50:51.35,CHT,1352,0,0,0,,在世界各地表演
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.55,1:50:51.35,ENG,1352,0,0,0,,I danced everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.75,1:50:56.25,CHT,1353,0,0,0,,倫敦，維也納，布拉格
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.75,1:50:56.25,ENG,1353,0,0,0,,London, Vienna, Prague.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.85,1:50:58.75,CHT,1354,0,0,0,,我從沒見過這些照片
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.85,1:50:58.75,ENG,1354,0,0,0,,I've never seen these.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.15,1:51:03.15,CHT,1355,0,0,0,,媽
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.15,1:51:03.15,ENG,1355,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.45,1:51:07.15,CHT,1356,0,0,0,,你從來沒提你跳舞的事
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.45,1:51:07.15,ENG,1356,0,0,0,,You never talked about your dancing.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.25,1:51:09.25,CHT,1357,0,0,0,,我還是頭一個
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.25,1:51:09.25,ENG,1357,0,0,0,,Well, I was the only American
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.35,1:51:14.35,CHT,1358,0,0,0,,受邀，和大劇院舞團共舞的美國人 （Bolshoi：俄國著名芭蕾舞團）
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.35,1:51:14.35,ENG,1358,0,0,0,,to be invited to dance with the Bolshoi, sugar.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.15,1:51:18.15,CHT,1359,0,0,0,,那真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.15,1:51:18.15,ENG,1359,0,0,0,,It was glorious.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.65,1:51:26.35,CHT,1360,0,0,0,,但我從沒忘記本傑明
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.65,1:51:26.35,ENG,1360,0,0,0,,But Benjamin was never far from my thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.55,1:51:33.05,CHT,1361,0,0,0,,有時候，我會不自覺地說…
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.55,1:51:33.05,ENG,1361,0,0,0,,And I'd find myself saying...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.25,1:51:34.95,CHT,1362,0,0,0,,晚安，本傑明
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.25,1:51:34.95,ENG,1362,0,0,0,,Good night, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.05,1:51:40.65,CHT,1363,0,0,0,,- “晚安，黛西” - 他也這麼說？
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.05,1:51:40.65,ENG,1363,0,0,0,,- "Good night, Daisy." - He said that?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.85,1:51:43.95,CHT,1364,0,0,0,,“生活並沒有那麼複雜
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.85,1:51:43.95,ENG,1364,0,0,0,,"Life wasn't all that complicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.85,1:51:47.65,CHT,1365,0,0,0,,要是你喜歡 大可以說我是在探索生命”
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.85,1:51:47.65,ENG,1365,0,0,0,,"If you want, you might say I was looking for something."
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.05,1:52:00.05,CHT,1366,0,0,0,,本傑明，拉·圖爾諾夫人剛剛過世了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.05,1:52:00.05,ENG,1366,0,0,0,,Benjamin? Mrs. La Tourneau just passed.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.45,1:52:10.15,CHT,1367,0,0,0,,- 本傑明·巴頓先生的信 - 我就是
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.45,1:52:10.15,ENG,1367,0,0,0,,- Letter for Mr. Benjamin Button? - That'd be me.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.05,1:52:14.35,CHT,1368,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.05,1:52:14.35,ENG,1368,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.75,1:52:42.65,CHT,1369,0,0,0,,我找黛西·富勒小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.75,1:52:42.65,ENG,1369,0,0,0,,Miss Daisy Fuller.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.75,1:52:45.55,CHT,1370,0,0,0,,- 稍等，請先坐一會 - 好的
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.75,1:52:45.55,ENG,1370,0,0,0,,- Just a minute. Please have a seat. - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.95,1:52:57.35,CHT,1371,0,0,0,,有時候，我們的人生軌道 會與別人的交錯，只是不自知罷了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.95,1:52:57.35,ENG,1371,0,0,0,,Sometimes we're on a collision course and we just don't know it.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.95,1:53:02.45,CHT,1372,0,0,0,,無論是意外，還是天意 我們都無力改變
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.95,1:53:02.45,ENG,1372,0,0,0,,Whether it's by accident or by design, there's not a thing we can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.25,1:53:08.35,CHT,1373,0,0,0,,巴黎，一名女子正要出門購物
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.25,1:53:08.35,ENG,1373,0,0,0,,A woman in Paris was on her way to go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.65,1:53:13.45,CHT,1374,0,0,0,,卻發現忘帶外套，於是回家去取
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.65,1:53:13.45,ENG,1374,0,0,0,,But she had forgotten her coat, went back to get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.55,1:53:15.75,CHT,1375,0,0,0,,她拿起外套，電話鈴響
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.55,1:53:15.75,ENG,1375,0,0,0,,When she had gotten her coat, the phone had rung.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.85,1:53:18.85,CHT,1376,0,0,0,,她接起電話，聊了一會
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.85,1:53:18.85,ENG,1376,0,0,0,,So she had stopped to answer it and talked for a couple of minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.35,1:53:22.15,CHT,1377,0,0,0,,與此同時
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.35,1:53:22.15,ENG,1377,0,0,0,,While the woman was on the phone,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.25,1:53:26.45,CHT,1378,0,0,0,,黛西正為一場巴黎歌劇院的演出彩排
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.25,1:53:26.45,ENG,1378,0,0,0,,Daisy was rehearsing for a performance at the Paris Opera House.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.55,1:53:29.25,CHT,1379,0,0,0,,不久，女子聊完，掛了電話
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.55,1:53:29.25,ENG,1379,0,0,0,,And while she was rehearsing, the woman, off the phone now,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.35,1:53:31.65,CHT,1380,0,0,0,,下樓去招計程車
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.35,1:53:31.65,ENG,1380,0,0,0,,had gone outside to get a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.25,1:53:38.55,CHT,1381,0,0,0,,另一邊，計程車司機 剛剛送完一位客人
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.25,1:53:38.55,ENG,1381,0,0,0,,Now, a taxi driver had dropped off a fare earlier,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.65,1:53:41.35,CHT,1382,0,0,0,,便停了車，去買咖啡
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.65,1:53:41.35,ENG,1382,0,0,0,,and had stopped to get a cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.25,1:53:44.95,CHT,1383,0,0,0,,而黛西還在繼續排練
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.25,1:53:44.95,ENG,1383,0,0,0,,And all the while, Daisy was rehearsing.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.55,1:53:51.05,CHT,1384,0,0,0,,那位送完了客人
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.55,1:53:51.05,ENG,1384,0,0,0,,And this cab driver, who dropped off the earlier fare
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.15,1:53:53.05,CHT,1385,0,0,0,,便去買咖啡的司機
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.15,1:53:53.05,ENG,1385,0,0,0,,and had stopped to get the cup of coffee,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.15,1:53:54.85,CHT,1386,0,0,0,,正巧接了要去購物的那位女子
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.15,1:53:54.85,ENG,1386,0,0,0,,he picked up the lady who was going shopping
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.95,1:53:57.65,CHT,1387,0,0,0,,而那位女子，因為一番延誤 剛錯過了之前的車
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.95,1:53:57.65,ENG,1387,0,0,0,,and had missed getting the earlier cab.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.65,1:54:01.05,CHT,1388,0,0,0,,車子中途停了一下 因為有人橫穿馬路
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.65,1:54:01.05,ENG,1388,0,0,0,,The taxi had to stop for a man crossing the street,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.15,1:54:03.95,CHT,1389,0,0,0,,這位男子那天比平時晚起了五分鐘
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.15,1:54:03.95,ENG,1389,0,0,0,,who had left for work five minutes later than he normally did
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.05,1:54:06.55,CHT,1390,0,0,0,,因為他忘了定鬧鐘
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.05,1:54:06.55,ENG,1390,0,0,0,,because he forgot to set his alarm.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.35,1:54:10.65,CHT,1391,0,0,0,,那個沒定鬧鐘，早上遲到的人 橫穿馬路的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.35,1:54:10.65,ENG,1391,0,0,0,,While that man, late for work, was crossing the street,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:10.75,1:54:14.15,CHT,1392,0,0,0,,黛西已經排練結束，開始沖澡
Dialogue: 0,1:54:10.75,1:54:14.15,ENG,1392,0,0,0,,Daisy had finished rehearsing and was taking a shower.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.65,1:54:15.95,CHT,1393,0,0,0,,她在洗澡的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.65,1:54:15.95,ENG,1393,0,0,0,,And while Daisy was showering,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.05,1:54:19.75,CHT,1394,0,0,0,,計程車停在一家糖果店門口 等女客人去取包裹
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.05,1:54:19.75,ENG,1394,0,0,0,,the taxi was waiting outside a boutique for the woman to pick up a package
Dialogue: 0,1:54:19.85,1:54:20.95,CHT,1395,0,0,0,,可包裹還沒備好
Dialogue: 0,1:54:19.85,1:54:20.95,ENG,1395,0,0,0,,which hadn't been wrapped yet,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:21.05,1:54:22.85,CHT,1396,0,0,0,,因為打包的女孩
Dialogue: 0,1:54:21.05,1:54:22.85,ENG,1396,0,0,0,,because the girl who was supposed to wrap it
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.95,1:54:26.55,CHT,1397,0,0,0,,昨晚剛剛與男友分手 太過傷心而忘了打包
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.95,1:54:26.55,ENG,1397,0,0,0,,had broken up with her boyfriend the night before and forgot.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.25,1:54:30.45,CHT,1398,0,0,0,,包裹打好之後，女子回到車上
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.25,1:54:30.45,ENG,1398,0,0,0,,When the package was wrapped, the woman, who was back in the cab,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.55,1:54:32.15,CHT,1399,0,0,0,,又被一輛貨車擋住了去路
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.55,1:54:32.15,ENG,1399,0,0,0,,was blocked by a delivery truck.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.25,1:54:34.95,CHT,1400,0,0,0,,與此同時，黛西換上了衣服
Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.25,1:54:34.95,ENG,1400,0,0,0,,All the while, Daisy was getting dressed.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.45,1:54:39.85,CHT,1401,0,0,0,,貨車開走之後，出租才重新上路
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.45,1:54:39.85,ENG,1401,0,0,0,,The delivery truck pulled away, and the taxi was able to move
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.95,1:54:42.05,CHT,1402,0,0,0,,而黛西最後一個才穿好衣服
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.95,1:54:42.05,ENG,1402,0,0,0,,while Daisy, the last to be dressed,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.15,1:54:45.65,CHT,1403,0,0,0,,又等了一會斷了鞋帶的朋友
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.15,1:54:45.65,ENG,1403,0,0,0,,waited for one of her friends who had broken a shoelace.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.15,1:54:49.05,CHT,1404,0,0,0,,出租在路燈處停下時
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.15,1:54:49.05,ENG,1404,0,0,0,,While the taxi was stopped, waiting for a traffic light,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.15,1:54:53.05,CHT,1405,0,0,0,,黛西和她朋友正從劇場後門出來
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.15,1:54:53.05,ENG,1405,0,0,0,,Daisy and her friend came out the back of the theater.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.15,1:54:56.55,CHT,1406,0,0,0,,如果有一件事，有一點點不一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.15,1:54:56.55,ENG,1406,0,0,0,,And if only one thing had happened differently,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.65,1:54:58.75,CHT,1407,0,0,0,,如果那鞋帶沒斷
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.65,1:54:58.75,ENG,1407,0,0,0,,if that shoelace hadn't broken
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.85,1:55:01.35,CHT,1408,0,0,0,,如果那貨車早一點兒開走
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.85,1:55:01.35,ENG,1408,0,0,0,,or that delivery truck had moved moments earlier
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.45,1:55:03.35,CHT,1409,0,0,0,,或者包裹早早備好
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.45,1:55:03.35,ENG,1409,0,0,0,,or that package had been wrapped and ready
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.45,1:55:06.15,CHT,1410,0,0,0,,因為男孩沒和女孩分手
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.45,1:55:06.15,ENG,1410,0,0,0,,because the girl hadn't broken up with her boyfriend,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.25,1:55:09.95,CHT,1411,0,0,0,,又或者那男子定了鬧鐘 和平時一樣起床
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.25,1:55:09.95,ENG,1411,0,0,0,,or that man had set his alarm and got up five minutes earlier
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.05,1:55:13.15,CHT,1412,0,0,0,,再或者司機沒有停車喝咖啡
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.05,1:55:13.15,ENG,1412,0,0,0,,or that taxi driver hadn't stopped for a cup of coffee
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.25,1:55:17.25,CHT,1413,0,0,0,,而那女子也帶了外套 上了之前的出租
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.25,1:55:17.25,ENG,1413,0,0,0,,or that woman had remembered her coat and got into an earlier cab,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:17.85,1:55:20.55,CHT,1414,0,0,0,,那麼，黛西和她朋友 就會平平安安地穿過馬路
Dialogue: 0,1:55:17.85,1:55:20.55,ENG,1414,0,0,0,,Daisy and her friend would have crossed the street
Dialogue: 0,1:55:20.65,1:55:23.05,CHT,1415,0,0,0,,那出租也只是和她們擦身而過
Dialogue: 0,1:55:20.65,1:55:23.05,ENG,1415,0,0,0,,and the taxi would have driven by.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.15,1:55:35.85,CHT,1416,0,0,0,,但是，生活沒有如果
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.15,1:55:35.85,ENG,1416,0,0,0,,But, life being what it is,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.95,1:55:38.95,CHT,1417,0,0,0,,只有一連串互相交錯的意外
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.95,1:55:38.95,ENG,1417,0,0,0,,a series of intersecting lives and incidents
Dialogue: 0,1:55:39.05,1:55:40.85,CHT,1418,0,0,0,,無人能夠控制
Dialogue: 0,1:55:39.05,1:55:40.85,ENG,1418,0,0,0,,out of anyone's control,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.75,1:55:44.45,CHT,1419,0,0,0,,那輛出租沒有和她們擦身而過
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.75,1:55:44.45,ENG,1419,0,0,0,,that taxi did not go by,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.55,1:55:47.35,CHT,1420,0,0,0,,而就在那時，司機分了一下神
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.55,1:55:47.35,ENG,1420,0,0,0,,and that driver was momentarily distracted.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.35,1:55:49.35,CHT,1421,0,0,0,,黛西！
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.35,1:55:49.35,ENG,1421,0,0,0,,Daisy!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.55,1:55:50.75,CHT,1422,0,0,0,,車子撞倒了黛西
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.55,1:55:50.75,ENG,1422,0,0,0,,And that taxi hit Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.85,1:55:52.55,CHT,1423,0,0,0,,黛西！來人啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.85,1:55:52.55,ENG,1423,0,0,0,,Daisy! Help!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:55.75,1:55:57.75,CHT,1424,0,0,0,,她的腿，就被撞斷了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:55.75,1:55:57.75,ENG,1424,0,0,0,,And her leg was crushed.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:05.15,1:56:06.35,CHT,1425,0,0,0,,黛西？
Dialogue: 0,1:56:05.15,1:56:06.35,ENG,1425,0,0,0,,Daisy?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:10.65,1:56:13.15,CHT,1426,0,0,0,,- 誰讓你來的？ - 你朋友寫信給我
Dialogue: 0,1:56:10.65,1:56:13.15,ENG,1426,0,0,0,,- Who told you? - Your friend wired me.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.25,1:56:18.25,CHT,1427,0,0,0,,你這麼大老遠來看我，真是好心
Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.25,1:56:18.25,ENG,1427,0,0,0,,Very kind of you to come all this way to see that I was all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:19.85,1:56:21.85,CHT,1428,0,0,0,,換了是你，也會這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,1:56:19.85,1:56:21.85,ENG,1428,0,0,0,,You'd do the same for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:23.75,1:56:24.95,CHT,1429,0,0,0,,我的天
Dialogue: 0,1:56:23.75,1:56:24.95,ENG,1429,0,0,0,,My God.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.15,1:56:30.55,CHT,1430,0,0,0,,瞧瞧你，你太完美了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.15,1:56:30.55,ENG,1430,0,0,0,,Look at you. You're perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.45,1:56:37.95,CHT,1431,0,0,0,,真希望你沒來這 我不想你看到我這樣子
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.45,1:56:37.95,ENG,1431,0,0,0,,I wish you hadn't come here. I don't want you to see me like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.35,1:56:46.65,CHT,1432,0,0,0,,她的腿，斷成了五段
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.35,1:56:46.65,ENG,1432,0,0,0,,Her leg had been broken in five places.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:46.75,1:56:49.85,CHT,1433,0,0,0,,如果治療得當，假以時日 她或許還能重新走路
Dialogue: 0,1:56:46.75,1:56:49.85,ENG,1433,0,0,0,,And with therapy and time, she might walk again.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.45,1:56:53.35,CHT,1434,0,0,0,,但不可能再跳舞了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.45,1:56:53.35,ENG,1434,0,0,0,,But she'd never dance.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:54.95,1:56:57.35,CHT,1435,0,0,0,,我帶你回家
Dialogue: 0,1:56:54.95,1:56:57.35,ENG,1435,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take you home with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:57.45,1:57:00.25,CHT,1436,0,0,0,,- 我願意照顧你 - 我不回新奧爾良
Dialogue: 0,1:56:57.45,1:57:00.25,ENG,1436,0,0,0,,- I want to look after you. - I'm not going back to New Orleans.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:00.35,1:57:02.55,CHT,1437,0,0,0,,那我就留在巴黎陪你
Dialogue: 0,1:57:00.35,1:57:02.55,ENG,1437,0,0,0,,Then I'll stay here in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.15,1:57:06.15,CHT,1438,0,0,0,,你還不明白嗎？我不用你可憐我！
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.15,1:57:06.15,ENG,1438,0,0,0,,Don't you understand? I don't want your help.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.25,1:57:11.55,CHT,1439,0,0,0,,我現在是很難過，可也不用你陪
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.25,1:57:11.55,ENG,1439,0,0,0,,I know I'm feeling sorry for myself, but I don't want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.65,1:57:15.35,CHT,1440,0,0,0,,在紐約那會就想告訴你了 可你就是不聽
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.65,1:57:15.35,ENG,1440,0,0,0,,Tried to tell you that in New York. You don't listen.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:16.95,1:57:18.85,CHT,1441,0,0,0,,你或許會改變主意
Dialogue: 0,1:57:16.95,1:57:18.85,ENG,1441,0,0,0,,You might change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.95,1:57:21.95,CHT,1442,0,0,0,,你也不是小孩子了，本傑明
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.95,1:57:21.95,ENG,1442,0,0,0,,We are not little children anymore, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.95,1:57:27.15,CHT,1443,0,0,0,,拜託，從我的生命裡消失吧
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.95,1:57:27.15,ENG,1443,0,0,0,,Just stay out of my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:50.05,1:57:53.25,CHT,1444,0,0,0,,我真的是太狠心了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:50.05,1:57:53.25,ENG,1444,0,0,0,,I was awfully cruel.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:54.35,1:57:59.75,CHT,1445,0,0,0,,他一定不明白 我只是不想讓他看我那副樣子
Dialogue: 0,1:57:54.35,1:57:59.75,ENG,1445,0,0,0,,He didn't understand. I couldn't have him see me like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:02.45,1:58:03.85,CHT,1446,0,0,0,,“我沒有馬上離開
Dialogue: 0,1:58:02.45,1:58:03.85,ENG,1446,0,0,0,,"I didn't leave right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:06.45,1:58:09.75,CHT,1447,0,0,0,,而是在巴黎逗留了一陣子 暗中照看她”
Dialogue: 0,1:58:06.45,1:58:09.75,ENG,1447,0,0,0,,"I stayed in Paris for a while to look out for her."
Dialogue: 0,1:58:13.45,1:58:15.25,CHT,1448,0,0,0,,我一點也不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:58:13.45,1:58:15.25,ENG,1448,0,0,0,,I never knew that.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:18.65,1:58:22.75,CHT,1449,0,0,0,,哦，親愛的，能幫我叫下護士嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:58:18.65,1:58:22.75,ENG,1449,0,0,0,,Oh, darling, could you get the nurse?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:26.45,1:58:31.45,CHT,1450,0,0,0,,我又重新學會走路
Dialogue: 0,1:58:26.45,1:58:31.45,ENG,1450,0,0,0,,I taught myself to walk again.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.55,1:58:37.05,CHT,1451,0,0,0,,又坐火車去盧德（法國西南部小城）
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.55,1:58:37.05,ENG,1451,0,0,0,,I took the train to Lourdes.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:38.45,1:58:44.05,CHT,1452,0,0,0,,我看看，很正常，脈搏舒緩下來了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:38.45,1:58:44.05,ENG,1452,0,0,0,,Let's take a look. That's normal. Pulse rate is slowing.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:44.15,1:58:46.15,CHT,1453,0,0,0,,稍後可能會呼吸困難一會
Dialogue: 0,1:58:44.15,1:58:46.15,ENG,1453,0,0,0,,She is gonna struggle to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:46.25,1:58:48.45,CHT,1454,0,0,0,,- 你在這沒事吧？ - 嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:58:46.25,1:58:48.45,ENG,1454,0,0,0,,- Will you be all right? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:01.65,1:59:07.55,CHT,1455,0,0,0,,我接著讀，他說“我回到家” 這裡有很多頁被撕掉了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:01.65,1:59:07.55,ENG,1455,0,0,0,,All right, he says, "I went back home." And then there's a lot of pages torn out.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:07.75,1:59:11.45,CHT,1456,0,0,0,,“我聆聽著房子的低語” 我讀過這段了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:07.75,1:59:11.45,ENG,1456,0,0,0,,"I listened to the sound of the house." I read that already.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:12.35,1:59:13.45,CHT,1457,0,0,0,,他…
Dialogue: 0,1:59:12.35,1:59:13.45,ENG,1457,0,0,0,,He...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:14.45,1:59:17.65,CHT,1458,0,0,0,,他把什麼東西濺到紙上 這段看不清了，媽
Dialogue: 0,1:59:14.45,1:59:17.65,ENG,1458,0,0,0,,He spilt something on it, so it's hard to read, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:18.85,1:59:21.55,CHT,1459,0,0,0,,好像是關於帆船的 您知道他在說什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:59:18.85,1:59:21.55,ENG,1459,0,0,0,,Something about sailing, does that make sense?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.35,1:59:25.75,CHT,1460,0,0,0,,我用父親留在湖邊別墅的帆船 學會了駕駛
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.35,1:59:25.75,ENG,1460,0,0,0,,I learned to sail an old boat of my father's from the lake house.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.95,1:59:36.85,CHT,1461,0,0,0,,說老實話
Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.95,1:59:36.85,ENG,1461,0,0,0,,I can't lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:36.95,1:59:39.75,CHT,1462,0,0,0,,我也確實很享受 與一兩位女子共度的時光
Dialogue: 0,1:59:36.95,1:59:39.75,ENG,1462,0,0,0,,I did enjoy the company of a woman or two.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:48.15,1:59:49.65,CHT,1463,0,0,0,,也許是三個吧
Dialogue: 0,1:59:48.15,1:59:49.65,ENG,1463,0,0,0,,Or maybe three.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:26.25,2:00:30.45,CHT,1464,0,0,0,,何必這麼煩呢，山姆 反正明天還是要去一趟的
Dialogue: 0,2:00:26.25,2:00:30.45,ENG,1464,0,0,0,,Don't know why you bother, Sam, just gonna be there again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:34.85,2:00:35.95,CHT,1465,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,2:00:34.85,2:00:35.95,ENG,1465,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.85,2:00:43.25,CHT,1466,0,0,0,,1962年春天
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.85,2:00:43.25,ENG,1466,0,0,0,,And in the spring of 1962,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:47.15,2:00:48.65,CHT,1467,0,0,0,,她回來了
Dialogue: 0,2:00:47.15,2:00:48.65,ENG,1467,0,0,0,,she came back.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:08.05,2:01:11.65,CHT,1468,0,0,0,,- 想知道我去了哪兒嗎？ - 不想
Dialogue: 0,2:01:08.05,2:01:11.65,ENG,1468,0,0,0,,- You want to know where I've been? - No.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:13.65,2:01:18.55,CHT,1469,0,0,0,,你怎麼連封信也不寫？ 就那麼人間蒸發了一樣
Dialogue: 0,2:01:13.65,2:01:18.55,ENG,1469,0,0,0,,How come you didn't write or nothing? Just disappearing like that.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:18.65,2:01:21.25,CHT,1470,0,0,0,,我只是去處理了一下私事
Dialogue: 0,2:01:18.65,2:01:21.25,ENG,1470,0,0,0,,It was something I needed to do for myself.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:21.35,2:01:25.05,CHT,1471,0,0,0,,我也從沒覺得你自私
Dialogue: 0,2:01:21.35,2:01:25.05,ENG,1471,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, I never took you to be the selfish type.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:25.15,2:01:27.65,CHT,1472,0,0,0,,但願如此
Dialogue: 0,2:01:25.15,2:01:27.65,ENG,1472,0,0,0,,I sure hope I'm not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:28.75,2:01:30.85,CHT,1473,0,0,0,,我一般看人不會看走眼的
Dialogue: 0,2:01:28.75,2:01:30.85,ENG,1473,0,0,0,,I'm usually not wrong about people.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:30.95,2:01:33.45,CHT,1474,0,0,0,,- 晚安，媽媽 - 晚安，寶貝兒
Dialogue: 0,2:01:30.95,2:01:33.45,ENG,1474,0,0,0,,- Good night, Mama. - Good night, baby.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.45,2:01:36.05,CHT,1475,0,0,0,,你倆好好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.45,2:01:36.05,ENG,1475,0,0,0,,Y'all have fun.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:38.85,2:01:43.25,CHT,1476,0,0,0,,- 你說到現在，還沒哪句話多過兩個字呢 - 我只是不想破壞氣氛
Dialogue: 0,2:01:38.85,2:01:43.25,ENG,1476,0,0,0,,- You haven't said two words. - I don't want to ruin it.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:13.45,2:02:15.75,CHT,1477,0,0,0,,- 和我睡吧 - 絕對地
Dialogue: 0,2:02:13.45,2:02:15.75,ENG,1477,0,0,0,,- Sleep with me? - Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:53.45,2:02:55.85,CHT,1478,0,0,0,,我邀她與我出遊
Dialogue: 0,2:02:53.45,2:02:55.85,ENG,1478,0,0,0,,I asked her to come away with me.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:58.15,2:03:01.25,CHT,1479,0,0,0,,我們沿著佛羅里達群島 一路乘帆駛進海灣
Dialogue: 0,2:02:58.15,2:03:01.25,ENG,1479,0,0,0,,We sailed into the Gulf along the Florida Keys.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:42.55,2:03:46.95,CHT,1480,0,0,0,,真高興我不是26歲那年和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,2:03:42.55,2:03:46.95,ENG,1480,0,0,0,,I am so glad we didn't find one another when I was 26.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:47.05,2:03:51.35,CHT,1481,0,0,0,,- 這話怎麼說？ - 我那會太嫩了
Dialogue: 0,2:03:47.05,2:03:51.35,ENG,1481,0,0,0,,- Why do you say that? - I was so young.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:51.45,2:03:53.25,CHT,1482,0,0,0,,你又太老
Dialogue: 0,2:03:51.45,2:03:53.25,ENG,1482,0,0,0,,And you were so old.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:53.95,2:03:56.85,CHT,1483,0,0,0,,現在這樣，才最自然
Dialogue: 0,2:03:53.95,2:03:56.85,ENG,1483,0,0,0,,It happened when it was supposed to happen.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:56.95,2:04:00.05,CHT,1484,0,0,0,,和你在一起的每分每秒，我都會珍惜
Dialogue: 0,2:03:56.95,2:04:00.05,ENG,1484,0,0,0,,I will enjoy each and every moment I have with you.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:05.25,2:04:07.75,CHT,1485,0,0,0,,我跟你打賭，我在這能比你堅持更久
Dialogue: 0,2:04:05.25,2:04:07.75,ENG,1485,0,0,0,,I bet I can stay out here longer than you.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:07.85,2:04:09.45,CHT,1486,0,0,0,,那我賭你撐不了
Dialogue: 0,2:04:07.85,2:04:09.45,ENG,1486,0,0,0,,I bet you can't.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:12.25,2:04:14.75,CHT,1487,0,0,0,,你臉上幾乎沒有皺紋
Dialogue: 0,2:04:12.25,2:04:14.75,ENG,1487,0,0,0,,Barely a line or a crease.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:15.25,2:04:18.35,CHT,1488,0,0,0,,而我，每天都會多長出幾條，不公平
Dialogue: 0,2:04:15.25,2:04:18.35,ENG,1488,0,0,0,,Every day I have more wrinkles. It's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:20.05,2:04:23.75,CHT,1489,0,0,0,,我喜歡你的皺紋，每一條都愛
Dialogue: 0,2:04:20.05,2:04:23.75,ENG,1489,0,0,0,,I love your wrinkles. Both of them.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:29.45,2:04:31.75,CHT,1490,0,0,0,,越活越年輕是種什麼感覺？
Dialogue: 0,2:04:29.45,2:04:31.75,ENG,1490,0,0,0,,What's it like growing younger?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:34.25,2:04:38.85,CHT,1491,0,0,0,,還真是很難形容 我自己又沒法看到全部變化
Dialogue: 0,2:04:34.25,2:04:38.85,ENG,1491,0,0,0,,I can't really say. I'm always looking out my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:43.85,2:04:47.65,CHT,1492,0,0,0,,我要是成了黃臉婆，你還會愛我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,2:04:43.85,2:04:47.65,ENG,1492,0,0,0,,Will you still love me when my skin grows old and saggy?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:47.75,2:04:52.25,CHT,1493,0,0,0,,等我老到臉上長滿青春痘，老到尿床
Dialogue: 0,2:04:47.75,2:04:52.25,ENG,1493,0,0,0,,Will you still love me when I have acne? When I wet the bed?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:53.55,2:04:56.45,CHT,1494,0,0,0,,老到連樓梯下有什麼都怕 你還會愛我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,2:04:53.55,2:04:56.45,ENG,1494,0,0,0,,When I'm afraid of what's under the stairs?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:03.85,2:05:04.95,CHT,1495,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,2:05:03.85,2:05:04.95,ENG,1495,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:10.95,2:05:14.95,CHT,1496,0,0,0,,- 你在想什麼？ - 我在想，為什麼世上沒有永恆呢
Dialogue: 0,2:05:10.95,2:05:14.95,ENG,1496,0,0,0,,- What are you thinking? - Well, I was thinking how nothing lasts.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:17.35,2:05:19.35,CHT,1497,0,0,0,,多可惜
Dialogue: 0,2:05:17.35,2:05:19.35,ENG,1497,0,0,0,,And what a shame that is.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:22.35,2:05:23.95,CHT,1498,0,0,0,,有些事情，是永恆的
Dialogue: 0,2:05:22.35,2:05:23.95,ENG,1498,0,0,0,,Some things last.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:26.35,2:05:30.45,CHT,1499,0,0,0,,- 晚安，黛西 - 晚安，本傑明
Dialogue: 0,2:05:26.35,2:05:30.45,ENG,1499,0,0,0,,- Good night, Daisy. - Good night, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:46.95,2:05:47.95,CHT,1500,0,0,0,,媽？
Dialogue: 0,2:05:46.95,2:05:47.95,ENG,1500,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:50.25,2:05:54.25,CHT,1501,0,0,0,,- 你什麼時候認識爸爸的？ - 在那之後
Dialogue: 0,2:05:50.25,2:05:54.25,ENG,1501,0,0,0,,- When did you meet Dad? - Some time after that.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:57.45,2:06:02.15,CHT,1502,0,0,0,,- 你跟他說過這個本傑明的事嗎？ - 親愛的，他知道得不少
Dialogue: 0,2:05:57.45,2:06:02.15,ENG,1502,0,0,0,,- Did you tell him about this Benjamin? - He knew enough, darling.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:22.15,2:06:23.25,CHT,1503,0,0,0,,媽？
Dialogue: 0,2:06:22.15,2:06:23.25,ENG,1503,0,0,0,,Mama?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:30.45,2:06:31.75,CHT,1504,0,0,0,,奎尼？
Dialogue: 0,2:06:30.45,2:06:31.75,ENG,1504,0,0,0,,Queenie?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:34.95,2:06:36.25,CHT,1505,0,0,0,,是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,2:06:34.95,2:06:36.25,ENG,1505,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:36.65,2:06:40.25,CHT,1506,0,0,0,,哦，嗨，卡特夫人，大家都上哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,2:06:36.65,2:06:40.25,ENG,1506,0,0,0,,Oh, hi, Mrs. Carter, it's Benjamin. Where is everybody?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:40.35,2:06:45.55,CHT,1507,0,0,0,,哦，本傑明，奎尼去世了，節哀啊
Dialogue: 0,2:06:40.35,2:06:45.55,ENG,1507,0,0,0,,Oh, Benjamin. Queenie died. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:14.25,2:07:17.65,CHT,1508,0,0,0,,你失去親人，我也很難過 她是個好女人
Dialogue: 0,2:07:14.25,2:07:17.65,ENG,1508,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry for your loss. She was a great woman.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:17.75,2:07:19.55,CHT,1509,0,0,0,,我們深表哀悼
Dialogue: 0,2:07:17.75,2:07:19.55,ENG,1509,0,0,0,,Our deepest condolences.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:24.75,2:07:27.75,CHT,1510,0,0,0,,她葬在她的摯愛，韋瑟斯身邊
Dialogue: 0,2:07:24.75,2:07:27.75,ENG,1510,0,0,0,,We buried her beside her beloved Mr. Weathers.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:34.75,2:07:38.15,CHT,1511,0,0,0,,為了過上我們自己的生活
Dialogue: 0,2:07:34.75,2:07:38.15,ENG,1511,0,0,0,,And so we might have memories of our own,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:38.35,2:07:40.25,CHT,1512,0,0,0,,我賣了父親的房子
Dialogue: 0,2:07:38.35,2:07:40.25,ENG,1512,0,0,0,,we sold my father's house on Esplanade.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:40.35,2:07:42.95,CHT,1513,0,0,0,,親愛的，這老房子真是太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,2:07:40.35,2:07:42.95,ENG,1513,0,0,0,,It is a wonderful old place, darling.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:43.55,2:07:46.45,CHT,1514,0,0,0,,我想我們生活在這裡會很開心
Dialogue: 0,2:07:43.55,2:07:46.45,ENG,1514,0,0,0,,I think we are going to be so happy here.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:46.55,2:07:49.45,CHT,1515,0,0,0,,哦，好長的家族史啊
Dialogue: 0,2:07:46.55,2:07:49.45,ENG,1515,0,0,0,,Oh, what a long family history you have.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:49.55,2:07:51.55,CHT,1516,0,0,0,,和房子的歷史一樣長
Dialogue: 0,2:07:49.55,2:07:51.55,ENG,1516,0,0,0,,They come with the house.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:54.15,2:07:57.05,CHT,1517,0,0,0,,- 上來吧 - 你一定得看看主臥室
Dialogue: 0,2:07:54.15,2:07:57.05,ENG,1517,0,0,0,,- Come on. - You have to see the master suite.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:58.55,2:08:00.75,CHT,1518,0,0,0,,我們買了一套二聯式的小公寓
Dialogue: 0,2:07:58.55,2:08:00.75,ENG,1518,0,0,0,,We bought ourselves a duplex.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:02.85,2:08:04.85,CHT,1519,0,0,0,,我愛死那房子了
Dialogue: 0,2:08:02.85,2:08:04.85,ENG,1519,0,0,0,,I loved that house.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:07.35,2:08:09.25,CHT,1520,0,0,0,,有木柴的味道
Dialogue: 0,2:08:07.35,2:08:09.25,ENG,1520,0,0,0,,It smelled like firewood.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:10.45,2:08:13.65,CHT,1521,0,0,0,,別…別停下，親愛的
Dialogue: 0,2:08:10.45,2:08:13.65,ENG,1521,0,0,0,,Don't... Don't stop, darling.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:14.25,2:08:17.15,CHT,1522,0,0,0,,“那是我生命中最快樂的時光”
Dialogue: 0,2:08:14.25,2:08:17.15,ENG,1522,0,0,0,,"It was one of the happiest times of my life."
Dialogue: 0,2:08:17.25,2:08:19.75,CHT,1523,0,0,0,,我們半件傢俱也沒有
Dialogue: 0,2:08:17.25,2:08:19.75,ENG,1523,0,0,0,,We didn't have a stick of furniture.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:20.55,2:08:23.25,CHT,1524,0,0,0,,在起居室裡野餐
Dialogue: 0,2:08:20.55,2:08:23.25,ENG,1524,0,0,0,,We would have picnics in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:26.75,2:08:30.75,CHT,1525,0,0,0,,想什麼時候吃飯就什麼時候吃 只要願意，就通宵不睡
Dialogue: 0,2:08:26.75,2:08:30.75,ENG,1525,0,0,0,,We ate when we felt like it. Stayed up all night when we wanted.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:32.15,2:08:34.15,CHT,1526,0,0,0,,我們發誓，一定不過循規蹈矩的生活
Dialogue: 0,2:08:32.15,2:08:34.15,ENG,1526,0,0,0,,We vowed never to fall into routine,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:34.25,2:08:37.15,CHT,1527,0,0,0,,絕不按時上床，起床
Dialogue: 0,2:08:34.25,2:08:37.15,ENG,1527,0,0,0,,to go to bed or wake up at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:37.25,2:08:39.25,CHT,1528,0,0,0,,我們就在床墊上過活
Dialogue: 0,2:08:37.25,2:08:39.25,ENG,1528,0,0,0,,We lived on that mattress.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:14.95,2:09:18.45,CHT,1529,0,0,0,,我們的鄰居，凡·丹夫人，是個理療師
Dialogue: 0,2:09:14.95,2:09:18.45,ENG,1529,0,0,0,,Our neighbor, a Mrs. Van Dam, was a physical therapist.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:20.05,2:09:22.75,CHT,1530,0,0,0,,離家四個街區，就有個公共泳池
Dialogue: 0,2:09:20.05,2:09:22.75,ENG,1530,0,0,0,,We lived four blocks from a public pool.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:01.25,2:10:03.95,CHT,1531,0,0,0,,也許，你能多跳幾年舞
Dialogue: 0,2:10:01.25,2:10:03.95,ENG,1531,0,0,0,,You know, you might've got a few more years out of it,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:04.05,2:10:08.15,CHT,1532,0,0,0,,可你的事業太與眾不同
Dialogue: 0,2:10:04.05,2:10:08.15,ENG,1532,0,0,0,,but you chose to do something so special and unique
Dialogue: 0,2:10:09.65,2:10:13.35,CHT,1533,0,0,0,,只有幾年的黃金時間可以發展
Dialogue: 0,2:10:09.65,2:10:13.35,ENG,1533,0,0,0,,that there was only a short window of time you could do it.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:15.15,2:10:17.65,CHT,1534,0,0,0,,就算沒發生意外
Dialogue: 0,2:10:15.15,2:10:17.65,ENG,1534,0,0,0,,So, even if nothing ever happened,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:17.75,2:10:20.85,CHT,1535,0,0,0,,你現在還是會回來，在這
Dialogue: 0,2:10:17.75,2:10:20.85,ENG,1535,0,0,0,,you'd still be right here where you are now.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:20.95,2:10:23.15,CHT,1536,0,0,0,,我只是不喜歡變老
Dialogue: 0,2:10:20.95,2:10:23.15,ENG,1536,0,0,0,,I just don't like getting old.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:24.75,2:10:27.25,CHT,1537,0,0,0,,這裡的水消毒過頭了 （泳池用氯氣消毒，氯氣有強刺激性）
Dialogue: 0,2:10:24.75,2:10:27.25,ENG,1537,0,0,0,,They put too much chlorine in here.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:08.55,2:11:12.45,CHT,1538,0,0,0,,我保證，以後再也不會自怨自艾了
Dialogue: 0,2:11:08.55,2:11:12.45,ENG,1538,0,0,0,,I promise you I'll never lose myself to self-pity again.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:16.75,2:11:19.85,CHT,1539,0,0,0,,那時候，我知道
Dialogue: 0,2:11:16.75,2:11:19.85,ENG,1539,0,0,0,,And I think right there and then
Dialogue: 0,2:11:19.95,2:11:23.95,CHT,1540,0,0,0,,她懂了，沒人是永遠完美無瑕的
Dialogue: 0,2:11:19.95,2:11:23.95,ENG,1540,0,0,0,,she realized none of us is perfect forever.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:27.85,2:11:29.45,CHT,1541,0,0,0,,她的內心，終於平靜了
Dialogue: 0,2:11:27.85,2:11:29.45,ENG,1541,0,0,0,,She found peace.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:31.35,2:11:34.35,CHT,1542,0,0,0,,她辦了間舞蹈室，教小女孩跳舞
Dialogue: 0,2:11:31.35,2:11:34.35,ENG,1542,0,0,0,,She opened a studio and taught young girls how to dance.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:34.45,2:11:37.45,CHT,1543,0,0,0,,足尖點地
Dialogue: 0,2:11:34.45,2:11:37.45,ENG,1543,0,0,0,,And tendu.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:37.65,2:11:42.65,CHT,1544,0,0,0,,跳回來，點地，點地，點地 好極了！
Dialogue: 0,2:11:37.65,2:11:42.65,ENG,1544,0,0,0,,Come back the other way. And spot, spot, spot. Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:44.35,2:11:46.85,CHT,1545,0,0,0,,- 晚安，黛西老師 - 晚安
Dialogue: 0,2:11:44.35,2:11:46.85,ENG,1545,0,0,0,,- Good night, Miss Daisy. - Good night.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:12.35,2:12:14.95,CHT,1546,0,0,0,,你看起來真美
Dialogue: 0,2:12:12.35,2:12:14.95,ENG,1546,0,0,0,,You certainly are beautiful to watch.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:16.75,2:12:19.15,CHT,1547,0,0,0,,舞蹈好不好就看身線
Dialogue: 0,2:12:16.75,2:12:19.15,ENG,1547,0,0,0,,Dancing's all about the line.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:21.45,2:12:23.25,CHT,1548,0,0,0,,身體的曲線
Dialogue: 0,2:12:21.45,2:12:23.25,ENG,1548,0,0,0,,The line of your body.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:24.65,2:12:28.95,CHT,1549,0,0,0,,早晚，身線都有不好的一天 之後，就一去不復返了
Dialogue: 0,2:12:24.65,2:12:28.95,ENG,1549,0,0,0,,Sooner or later, you lose that line, and you never get it back.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:34.85,2:12:40.85,CHT,1550,0,0,0,,我算了下，你是1918年出生的 今年也49了
Dialogue: 0,2:12:34.85,2:12:40.85,ENG,1550,0,0,0,,I figure, you were born in 1918, 49 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:40.95,2:12:42.45,CHT,1551,0,0,0,,我43
Dialogue: 0,2:12:40.95,2:12:42.45,ENG,1551,0,0,0,,I'm 43.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:44.65,2:12:47.15,CHT,1552,0,0,0,,差不多算是同齡
Dialogue: 0,2:12:44.65,2:12:47.15,ENG,1552,0,0,0,,We are almost the same age.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:50.45,2:12:54.65,CHT,1553,0,0,0,,- 我們在人生的中點相遇 - 總算是遇上了
Dialogue: 0,2:12:50.45,2:12:54.65,ENG,1553,0,0,0,,- We're meeting in the middle. - We finally caught up with each other.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:55.85,2:12:56.95,CHT,1554,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,2:12:55.85,2:12:56.95,ENG,1554,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:58.35,2:13:00.95,CHT,1555,0,0,0,,我想記著我們現在的樣子
Dialogue: 0,2:12:58.35,2:13:00.95,ENG,1555,0,0,0,,I want to remember us just as we are now.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:11.85,2:13:13.35,CHT,1556,0,0,0,,我有了
Dialogue: 0,2:13:11.85,2:13:13.35,ENG,1556,0,0,0,,I'm pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:31.05,2:13:34.65,CHT,1557,0,0,0,,知道嘛，我敢打賭 那護士說漏過嘴，是男孩
Dialogue: 0,2:13:31.05,2:13:34.65,ENG,1557,0,0,0,,You know, I swear the nurse slipped and said it was a boy.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:49.65,2:13:51.65,CHT,1558,0,0,0,,可我覺得是女孩
Dialogue: 0,2:13:49.65,2:13:51.65,ENG,1558,0,0,0,,But I think it's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:56.95,2:14:00.55,CHT,1559,0,0,0,,- 我知道你擔心 - 我也沒藏著掖著
Dialogue: 0,2:13:56.95,2:14:00.55,ENG,1559,0,0,0,,- I know you're afraid. - I'm not hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:00.65,2:14:01.75,CHT,1560,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,2:14:00.65,2:14:01.75,ENG,1560,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:09.05,2:14:11.65,CHT,1561,0,0,0,,- 你最擔心什麼？ - 孩子像我
Dialogue: 0,2:14:09.05,2:14:11.65,ENG,1561,0,0,0,,- What's your worst fear? - Baby born like me.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:11.75,2:14:14.15,CHT,1562,0,0,0,,那我更愛他還來不及呢
Dialogue: 0,2:14:11.75,2:14:14.15,ENG,1562,0,0,0,,Then I will love it all the more.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:16.25,2:14:21.15,CHT,1563,0,0,0,,這麼說吧，我這樣越活越小 怎麼能當好一個父親？
Dialogue: 0,2:14:16.25,2:14:21.15,ENG,1563,0,0,0,,Okay. How can I be a father when I'm heading in the other direction?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:21.85,2:14:25.15,CHT,1564,0,0,0,,對孩子來說也不公平，我不想變成累贅
Dialogue: 0,2:14:21.85,2:14:25.15,ENG,1564,0,0,0,,It's not fair to a child. I don't want to be anybody's burden.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:25.25,2:14:28.05,CHT,1565,0,0,0,,甜心，到頭來 我們都會重新用上尿布
Dialogue: 0,2:14:25.25,2:14:28.05,ENG,1565,0,0,0,,Sugar, we all end up in diapers.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:29.55,2:14:31.65,CHT,1566,0,0,0,,我會想辦法，讓一切都順利
Dialogue: 0,2:14:29.55,2:14:31.65,ENG,1566,0,0,0,,I am gonna make this work.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:34.25,2:14:37.15,CHT,1567,0,0,0,,我想要這孩子，我想和你一起 把他養育成人
Dialogue: 0,2:14:34.25,2:14:37.15,ENG,1567,0,0,0,,I want this, and I want it with you.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:37.25,2:14:40.65,CHT,1568,0,0,0,,你想要什麼，我就儘量給你 無論有多難
Dialogue: 0,2:14:37.25,2:14:40.65,ENG,1568,0,0,0,,I want you to have everything you want, all of it.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:40.75,2:14:43.95,CHT,1569,0,0,0,,只是現在，我還沒想好 我這樣子，怎麼才能不影響到孩子
Dialogue: 0,2:14:40.75,2:14:43.95,ENG,1569,0,0,0,,I'm just not sure how to reconcile this.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:44.05,2:14:46.15,CHT,1570,0,0,0,,你會跟一個盲人說，他不能有孩子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,2:14:44.05,2:14:46.15,ENG,1570,0,0,0,,Would you tell a blind man he couldn't have children?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:46.25,2:14:47.85,CHT,1571,0,0,0,,打包好了
Dialogue: 0,2:14:46.25,2:14:47.85,ENG,1571,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:47.95,2:14:51.35,CHT,1572,0,0,0,,你是孩子的父親，能當多久當多久
Dialogue: 0,2:14:47.95,2:14:51.35,ENG,1572,0,0,0,,You'll be a father for as long as you can.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:51.45,2:14:54.25,CHT,1573,0,0,0,,我知道最後會是什麼結局 我也準備好面對了
Dialogue: 0,2:14:51.45,2:14:54.25,ENG,1573,0,0,0,,I know the consequences. I've accepted that.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:54.35,2:14:56.95,CHT,1574,0,0,0,,為了愛你，我可以不惜一切
Dialogue: 0,2:14:54.35,2:14:56.95,ENG,1574,0,0,0,,Loving you is worth everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:01.55,2:15:03.15,CHT,1575,0,0,0,,我要噓噓去
Dialogue: 0,2:15:01.55,2:15:03.15,ENG,1575,0,0,0,,I have to go pee.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:17.25,2:15:19.45,CHT,1576,0,0,0,,有史以來，橫渡英吉利海峽 最年長的婦女
Dialogue: 0,2:15:17.25,2:15:19.45,ENG,1576,0,0,0,,The oldest woman to ever swim the English Channel
Dialogue: 0,2:15:19.55,2:15:21.25,CHT,1577,0,0,0,,今日遊抵加來…
Dialogue: 0,2:15:19.55,2:15:21.25,ENG,1577,0,0,0,,arrived here today in Calais...
Dialogue: 0,2:15:21.35,2:15:23.85,CHT,1578,0,0,0,,- 不用找了 - 全程花去34小時
Dialogue: 0,2:15:21.35,2:15:23.85,ENG,1578,0,0,0,,- Keep it. - ... having made the swim in 34 hours,
Dialogue: 0,2:15:23.95,2:15:26.15,CHT,1579,0,0,0,,22分鐘，14秒
Dialogue: 0,2:15:23.95,2:15:26.15,ENG,1579,0,0,0,,22 minutes and 14 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:26.25,2:15:31.15,CHT,1580,0,0,0,,現年68歲的伊莉莎白·亞伯特 于格林尼治時間5:38抵岸
Dialogue: 0,2:15:26.25,2:15:31.15,ENG,1580,0,0,0,,The 68-year-old Elizabeth Abbott arrived at 5:38 Greenwich mean time,
Dialogue: 0,2:15:31.25,2:15:32.95,CHT,1581,0,0,0,,雖然精疲力竭，但還是笑顏逐開
Dialogue: 0,2:15:31.25,2:15:32.95,ENG,1581,0,0,0,,exhausted but happy.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:33.05,2:15:36.65,CHT,1582,0,0,0,,亞伯特女士，能用幾句話來概括 形容下您的此次壯舉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,2:15:33.05,2:15:36.65,ENG,1582,0,0,0,,Miss Abbott, how would you sum up, in words, this achievement?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:36.75,2:15:38.25,CHT,1583,0,0,0,,那我得說…
Dialogue: 0,2:15:36.75,2:15:38.25,ENG,1583,0,0,0,,I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,2:15:39.65,2:15:41.45,CHT,1584,0,0,0,,凡事皆有可能
Dialogue: 0,2:15:39.65,2:15:41.45,ENG,1584,0,0,0,,Anything's possible.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:45.45,2:15:46.65,CHT,1585,0,0,0,,- 夠了嗎？ - 嗯，非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,2:15:45.45,2:15:46.65,ENG,1585,0,0,0,,- All right? - Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:46.75,2:15:47.65,CHT,1586,0,0,0,,- 可以走了嗎？ - 真謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,2:15:46.75,2:15:47.65,ENG,1586,0,0,0,,- You ready? - Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:47.75,2:15:49.75,CHT,1587,0,0,0,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,2:15:47.75,2:15:49.75,ENG,1587,0,0,0,,Thank you. Thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:49.85,2:15:51.75,CHT,1588,0,0,0,,- 嗯 - 你們真好
Dialogue: 0,2:15:49.85,2:15:51.75,ENG,1588,0,0,0,,- Yeah. - You're very kind.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:59.05,2:16:02.95,CHT,1589,0,0,0,,春天裡的某一天，尋常的一天…
Dialogue: 0,2:15:59.05,2:16:02.95,ENG,1589,0,0,0,,In the spring, on a day like any other...
Dialogue: 0,2:16:03.65,2:16:05.65,CHT,1590,0,0,0,,我出門去，一小時就回來！
Dialogue: 0,2:16:03.65,2:16:05.65,ENG,1590,0,0,0,,I'll be back in an hour!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:10.65,2:16:11.85,CHT,1591,0,0,0,,親愛的？
Dialogue: 0,2:16:10.65,2:16:11.85,ENG,1591,0,0,0,,Honey?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:13.95,2:16:15.95,CHT,1592,0,0,0,,快叫救護車！
Dialogue: 0,2:16:13.95,2:16:15.95,ENG,1592,0,0,0,,Go and call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:18.85,2:16:20.55,CHT,1593,0,0,0,,快生了
Dialogue: 0,2:16:18.85,2:16:20.55,ENG,1593,0,0,0,,The baby's coming.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:21.35,2:16:22.45,CHT,1594,0,0,0,,接線員，我找救護車
Dialogue: 0,2:16:21.35,2:16:22.45,ENG,1594,0,0,0,,Operator, I need an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:22.55,2:16:24.95,CHT,1595,0,0,0,,- 快生了！ - 拿破崙路2714號
Dialogue: 0,2:16:22.55,2:16:24.95,ENG,1595,0,0,0,,- The baby's coming! - 2714 Napoleon.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:32.25,2:16:34.85,CHT,1596,0,0,0,,就這樣，注意呼吸
Dialogue: 0,2:16:32.25,2:16:34.85,ENG,1596,0,0,0,,There you go. Keep breathing.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:35.85,2:16:38.15,CHT,1597,0,0,0,,深呼吸，用力！
Dialogue: 0,2:16:35.85,2:16:38.15,ENG,1597,0,0,0,,Deep breaths. Push.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:48.05,2:16:49.45,CHT,1598,0,0,0,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,2:16:48.05,2:16:49.45,ENG,1598,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:05.95,2:17:09.25,CHT,1599,0,0,0,,母女平安，孩子很健康
Dialogue: 0,2:17:05.95,2:17:09.25,ENG,1599,0,0,0,,Everyone's fine. She's a perfectly healthy baby girl.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:16.15,2:17:17.35,CHT,1600,0,0,0,,親愛的？
Dialogue: 0,2:17:16.15,2:17:17.35,ENG,1600,0,0,0,,Honey?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:19.35,2:17:22.95,CHT,1601,0,0,0,,她生下了一個5磅4盎司重的女孩 （約6斤3兩）
Dialogue: 0,2:17:19.35,2:17:22.95,ENG,1601,0,0,0,,She gave birth to a five pound, four ounce baby girl.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:39.15,2:17:41.05,CHT,1602,0,0,0,,你數過腳趾了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,2:17:39.15,2:17:41.05,ENG,1602,0,0,0,,Did you count the toes?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:45.35,2:17:46.85,CHT,1603,0,0,0,,她可真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,2:17:45.35,2:17:46.85,ENG,1603,0,0,0,,She's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:47.35,2:17:50.55,CHT,1604,0,0,0,,“我們用我母親的名字 給她取名，卡洛琳”
Dialogue: 0,2:17:47.35,2:17:50.55,ENG,1604,0,0,0,,"And we named her for my mother, Caroline."
Dialogue: 0,2:17:54.35,2:17:56.45,CHT,1605,0,0,0,,這個叫本傑明的，是我父親？
Dialogue: 0,2:17:54.35,2:17:56.45,ENG,1605,0,0,0,,This Benjamin was my father?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:57.95,2:18:00.15,CHT,1606,0,0,0,,你就這麼告訴我真相？
Dialogue: 0,2:17:57.95,2:18:00.15,ENG,1606,0,0,0,,And this is how you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:05.75,2:18:07.05,CHT,1607,0,0,0,,我走開一會
Dialogue: 0,2:18:05.75,2:18:07.05,ENG,1607,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:17.55,2:18:20.35,CHT,1608,0,0,0,,一場特大颶風所需具備的條件 都已成形
Dialogue: 0,2:18:17.55,2:18:20.35,ENG,1608,0,0,0,,... because all the ingredients are there for a major storm,
Dialogue: 0,2:18:20.45,2:18:22.95,CHT,1609,0,0,0,,本次颶風甚至可能達到第5級 （約相當於16級颱風）
Dialogue: 0,2:18:20.45,2:18:22.95,ENG,1609,0,0,0,,possibly even up to a Category 5.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:29.75,2:18:33.35,CHT,1610,0,0,0,,嘿，我知道你不好受 可不能在這吸煙
Dialogue: 0,2:18:29.75,2:18:33.35,ENG,1610,0,0,0,,Hey, I know it's hard. You can't smoke in here.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:36.65,2:18:38.95,CHT,1611,0,0,0,,目前還不知其登陸地點
Dialogue: 0,2:18:36.65,2:18:38.95,ENG,1611,0,0,0,,Nobody can tell you exactly where it's gonna hit,
Dialogue: 0,2:18:39.05,2:18:40.85,CHT,1612,0,0,0,,但我們會儘快查閱已有資料
Dialogue: 0,2:18:39.05,2:18:40.85,ENG,1612,0,0,0,,but we have to go with the guidance that we have,
Dialogue: 0,2:18:40.95,2:18:44.65,CHT,1613,0,0,0,,重新整理，並為大家 提供相應的防颱措施
Dialogue: 0,2:18:40.95,2:18:44.65,ENG,1613,0,0,0,,incorporate that information and then pass it along to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:51.55,2:18:56.35,CHT,1614,0,0,0,,“醫生說得沒錯，你慢慢長大 正常，健康”
Dialogue: 0,2:18:51.55,2:18:56.35,ENG,1614,0,0,0,,"You grew as the doctor had promised, normal and healthy."
Dialogue: 0,2:19:05.05,2:19:08.15,CHT,1615,0,0,0,,你該給她找個能勝任的父親
Dialogue: 0,2:19:05.05,2:19:08.15,ENG,1615,0,0,0,,You're gonna have to find a real father for her.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:11.35,2:19:13.05,CHT,1616,0,0,0,,你說什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,2:19:11.35,2:19:13.05,ENG,1616,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:13.15,2:19:16.45,CHT,1617,0,0,0,,得有人陪著她長大
Dialogue: 0,2:19:13.15,2:19:16.45,ENG,1617,0,0,0,,She's gonna need someone to grow old with.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:16.55,2:19:19.35,CHT,1618,0,0,0,,她會學著接受這一切的 再說，她愛你
Dialogue: 0,2:19:16.55,2:19:19.35,ENG,1618,0,0,0,,She'll learn to accept whatever happens. She loves you.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:19.55,2:19:22.25,CHT,1619,0,0,0,,親愛的，她需要的是父親，不是玩伴
Dialogue: 0,2:19:19.55,2:19:22.25,ENG,1619,0,0,0,,Honey, she needs a father, not a playmate.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:26.35,2:19:27.65,CHT,1620,0,0,0,,- 是我的問題嗎？ - 當然不是
Dialogue: 0,2:19:26.35,2:19:27.65,ENG,1620,0,0,0,,- Is it me? - Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:27.75,2:19:29.75,CHT,1621,0,0,0,,- 是不是我變老了，惹你嫌了？ - 當然不是
Dialogue: 0,2:19:27.75,2:19:29.75,ENG,1621,0,0,0,,- Is my age beginning to bother you? - Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:29.85,2:19:33.85,CHT,1622,0,0,0,,- 你是不是就這個意思？ - 你沒法把我們兩個一起養
Dialogue: 0,2:19:29.85,2:19:33.85,ENG,1622,0,0,0,,- Is that what you're telling me? - You can't raise the both of us.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:42.55,2:19:47.45,CHT,1623,0,0,0,,今天是你的第一次生日 我們為你辦了場生日聚會
Dialogue: 0,2:19:42.55,2:19:47.45,ENG,1623,0,0,0,,It was your first birthday. We had a party for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:48.15,2:19:50.05,CHT,1624,0,0,0,,屋子裡全是小朋友
Dialogue: 0,2:19:48.15,2:19:50.05,ENG,1624,0,0,0,,The house was filled with children.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:50.15,2:19:52.05,CHT,1625,0,0,0,,- 近來如何啊？ - 嘿，老兄
Dialogue: 0,2:19:50.15,2:19:52.05,ENG,1625,0,0,0,,- How are you? - Hey, man.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:52.15,2:19:55.75,CHT,1626,0,0,0,,一眨眼的功夫 他們就該上高中，開始約會了
Dialogue: 0,2:19:52.15,2:19:55.75,ENG,1626,0,0,0,,Before you turn around, they'll be in high school, dating.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:28.25,2:20:32.25,CHT,1627,0,0,0,,我賣了龐恰特雷恩湖邊的避暑別墅
Dialogue: 0,2:20:28.25,2:20:32.25,ENG,1627,0,0,0,,I sold the summer house on Lake Pontchartrain,
Dialogue: 0,2:20:32.35,2:20:35.05,CHT,1628,0,0,0,,賣了巴頓紐扣廠
Dialogue: 0,2:20:32.35,2:20:35.05,ENG,1628,0,0,0,,I sold Button's Buttons,
Dialogue: 0,2:20:35.15,2:20:39.65,CHT,1629,0,0,0,,賣了父親的帆船，把錢全都存進了銀行
Dialogue: 0,2:20:35.15,2:20:39.65,ENG,1629,0,0,0,,I sold my father's sailboat, put it all into a savings account.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:41.95,2:20:45.15,CHT,1630,0,0,0,,這樣你和你媽媽或許能過上好日子
Dialogue: 0,2:20:41.95,2:20:45.15,ENG,1630,0,0,0,,And so that you and your mother might have a life,
Dialogue: 0,2:20:46.35,2:20:50.25,CHT,1631,0,0,0,,趁你還不記得我，我得早日離開
Dialogue: 0,2:20:46.35,2:20:50.25,ENG,1631,0,0,0,,I left, before you could ever remember me.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:40.05,2:21:42.15,CHT,1632,0,0,0,,“離開的時候 我只帶走了身上穿的衣服”
Dialogue: 0,2:21:40.05,2:21:42.15,ENG,1632,0,0,0,,"I left with just the clothes on my back."
Dialogue: 0,2:21:43.55,2:21:48.25,CHT,1633,0,0,0,,我不想再念了 您能不能直接告訴我，他去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,2:21:43.55,2:21:48.25,ENG,1633,0,0,0,,I don't want to read this now. Can you just tell me where he went?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:49.65,2:21:51.95,CHT,1634,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,2:21:49.65,2:21:51.95,ENG,1634,0,0,0,,I don't really know.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:03.15,2:22:08.15,CHT,1635,0,0,0,,這是寄給我的，1970年，我才兩歲 “生日快樂”
Dialogue: 0,2:22:03.15,2:22:08.15,ENG,1635,0,0,0,,It's for me. 1970. I was two. "Happy Birthday."
Dialogue: 0,2:22:10.95,2:22:13.75,CHT,1636,0,0,0,,“我希望，可以在你臨睡前，吻你”
Dialogue: 0,2:22:10.95,2:22:13.75,ENG,1636,0,0,0,,"I wish I could have kissed you good night."
Dialogue: 0,2:22:18.85,2:22:20.65,CHT,1637,0,0,0,,都是寄給我的
Dialogue: 0,2:22:18.85,2:22:20.65,ENG,1637,0,0,0,,They're all for me.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:21.65,2:22:26.65,CHT,1638,0,0,0,,五歲，“我希望 可以領著你，上第一天學”
Dialogue: 0,2:22:21.65,2:22:26.65,ENG,1638,0,0,0,,Five. "I wish I could have taken you to your first day of school."
Dialogue: 0,2:22:31.15,2:22:36.95,CHT,1639,0,0,0,,六歲，“我希望 可以在你身邊，教你鋼琴”
Dialogue: 0,2:22:31.15,2:22:36.95,ENG,1639,0,0,0,,Six. "I wish I could have been there to teach you to play piano."
Dialogue: 0,2:22:40.45,2:22:43.45,CHT,1640,0,0,0,,1981年，13歲
Dialogue: 0,2:22:40.45,2:22:43.45,ENG,1640,0,0,0,,1981, 13.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:43.55,2:22:46.85,CHT,1641,0,0,0,,“我希望，可以告訴你 別去追那幫楞頭小子”
Dialogue: 0,2:22:43.55,2:22:46.85,ENG,1641,0,0,0,,"I wish I could have told you not to chase some boy.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:48.15,2:22:51.75,CHT,1642,0,0,0,,“我希望，你傷心的時候，有我安慰”
Dialogue: 0,2:22:48.15,2:22:51.75,ENG,1642,0,0,0,,"I wish I could have held you when you had a broken heart.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:53.25,2:22:59.05,CHT,1643,0,0,0,,“我希望，我可以當你爸爸 再沒有什麼，比這更讓我夢繞”
Dialogue: 0,2:22:53.25,2:22:59.05,ENG,1643,0,0,0,,"I wish I could have been your father. Nothing I ever did will replace that."
Dialogue: 0,2:23:06.55,2:23:09.05,CHT,1644,0,0,0,,我猜他去過印度
Dialogue: 0,2:23:06.55,2:23:09.05,ENG,1644,0,0,0,,I guess he went to India.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:09.15,2:23:11.65,CHT,1645,0,0,0,,“只要是有意義的事 再晚去做還有意義的”
Dialogue: 0,2:23:09.15,2:23:11.65,ENG,1645,0,0,0,,"For what it's worth, it's never too late,
Dialogue: 0,2:23:11.75,2:23:13.55,CHT,1646,0,0,0,,- “不過如果是我說，該說再‘早’…” - 再‘早’去做都是有意義的
Dialogue: 0,2:23:11.75,2:23:13.55,ENG,1646,0,0,0,,- "or, in my case, too early..." - ... or, in my case, too early,
Dialogue: 0,2:23:14.85,2:23:16.75,CHT,1647,0,0,0,,做你想做的人
Dialogue: 0,2:23:14.85,2:23:16.75,ENG,1647,0,0,0,,to be whoever you want to be.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:20.85,2:23:23.55,CHT,1648,0,0,0,,這件事，沒有時間的限制 只要願意，什麼時候都可以開始
Dialogue: 0,2:23:20.85,2:23:23.55,ENG,1648,0,0,0,,There's no time limit. Start whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:26.45,2:23:30.85,CHT,1649,0,0,0,,你能從現在開始改變，也可以一成不變 這件事，沒有規矩可言
Dialogue: 0,2:23:26.45,2:23:30.85,ENG,1649,0,0,0,,You can change or stay the same. There are no rules to this thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:33.45,2:23:36.95,CHT,1650,0,0,0,,你能活出最精彩的自己 也可能搞得一團糟
Dialogue: 0,2:23:33.45,2:23:36.95,ENG,1650,0,0,0,,We can make the best or the worst of it.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:37.05,2:23:39.35,CHT,1651,0,0,0,,我希望，你能活出最精彩的自己
Dialogue: 0,2:23:37.05,2:23:39.35,ENG,1651,0,0,0,,And I hope you make the best of it.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:42.45,2:23:45.15,CHT,1652,0,0,0,,我希望，你能見識到令你驚奇的事物
Dialogue: 0,2:23:42.45,2:23:45.15,ENG,1652,0,0,0,,I hope you see things that startle you.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:47.35,2:23:50.85,CHT,1653,0,0,0,,我希望，你能體驗未曾體驗過的情感
Dialogue: 0,2:23:47.35,2:23:50.85,ENG,1653,0,0,0,,I hope you feel things you never felt before.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:53.35,2:23:56.75,CHT,1654,0,0,0,,我希望，你能遇見一些想法不同的人
Dialogue: 0,2:23:53.35,2:23:56.75,ENG,1654,0,0,0,,I hope you meet people with a different point of view.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:57.95,2:24:00.65,CHT,1655,0,0,0,,我希望，你為你自己的人生感到驕傲
Dialogue: 0,2:23:57.95,2:24:00.65,ENG,1655,0,0,0,,I hope you live a life you're proud of.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:03.65,2:24:08.75,CHT,1656,0,0,0,,如果你發現自己還沒有做到 我希望，你有勇氣
Dialogue: 0,2:24:03.65,2:24:08.75,ENG,1656,0,0,0,,And if you find that you're not, I hope you have the strength
Dialogue: 0,2:24:08.85,2:24:12.05,CHT,1657,0,0,0,,- 重頭再來 - “重頭再來”
Dialogue: 0,2:24:08.85,2:24:12.05,ENG,1657,0,0,0,,- to start all over again. - "...start all over again."
Dialogue: 0,2:24:13.55,2:24:17.25,CHT,1658,0,0,0,,他離開我們很久
Dialogue: 0,2:24:13.55,2:24:17.25,ENG,1658,0,0,0,,He had been gone a long time.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:19.05,2:24:21.15,CHT,1659,0,0,0,,下週四見了
Dialogue: 0,2:24:19.05,2:24:21.15,ENG,1659,0,0,0,,I'll see you next Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:24.15,2:24:27.55,CHT,1660,0,0,0,,- 晚安，黛西老師 - 晚安，小甜心
Dialogue: 0,2:24:24.15,2:24:27.55,ENG,1660,0,0,0,,- Good night, Miss Daisy. - Oh, good night, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:45.35,2:24:47.35,CHT,1661,0,0,0,,抱歉，我們要關門了
Dialogue: 0,2:24:45.35,2:24:47.35,ENG,1661,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, we're closing.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:50.35,2:24:51.85,CHT,1662,0,0,0,,有什麼需要幫忙的嗎
Dialogue: 0,2:24:50.35,2:24:51.85,ENG,1662,0,0,0,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:53.45,2:24:55.85,CHT,1663,0,0,0,,您是來接孩子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,2:24:53.45,2:24:55.85,ENG,1663,0,0,0,,Are you here to pick somebody up?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:06.25,2:25:08.15,CHT,1664,0,0,0,,你為什麼要回來？
Dialogue: 0,2:25:06.25,2:25:08.15,ENG,1664,0,0,0,,Why did you come back?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:09.75,2:25:10.95,CHT,1665,0,0,0,,媽？
Dialogue: 0,2:25:09.75,2:25:10.95,ENG,1665,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:12.05,2:25:13.15,CHT,1666,0,0,0,,媽？
Dialogue: 0,2:25:12.05,2:25:13.15,ENG,1666,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:14.35,2:25:15.85,CHT,1667,0,0,0,,可以走了吧？
Dialogue: 0,2:25:14.35,2:25:15.85,ENG,1667,0,0,0,,You ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:18.85,2:25:19.95,CHT,1668,0,0,0,,媽，怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,2:25:18.85,2:25:19.95,ENG,1668,0,0,0,,Mom, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:20.05,2:25:23.65,CHT,1669,0,0,0,,只是剛剛聽說一個朋友的噩耗
Dialogue: 0,2:25:20.05,2:25:23.65,ENG,1669,0,0,0,,I was just hearing a very sad story about a mutual friend
Dialogue: 0,2:25:23.75,2:25:26.45,CHT,1670,0,0,0,,我都很久沒見過他了
Dialogue: 0,2:25:23.75,2:25:26.45,ENG,1670,0,0,0,,who I hadn't seen for a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:27.75,2:25:30.45,CHT,1671,0,0,0,,卡洛琳，這是本傑明
Dialogue: 0,2:25:27.75,2:25:30.45,ENG,1671,0,0,0,,Caroline, this is Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:30.55,2:25:33.25,CHT,1672,0,0,0,,其實你小時候就認識他了
Dialogue: 0,2:25:30.55,2:25:33.25,ENG,1672,0,0,0,,You knew him when you were just a baby.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:35.75,2:25:36.95,CHT,1673,0,0,0,,- 嗨 - 嗨
Dialogue: 0,2:25:35.75,2:25:36.95,ENG,1673,0,0,0,,- Hi. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:38.85,2:25:40.75,CHT,1674,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,2:25:38.85,2:25:40.75,ENG,1674,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:42.75,2:25:47.55,CHT,1675,0,0,0,,- 哦，抱歉，我還以為你完事了 - 這位是我家的世交
Dialogue: 0,2:25:42.75,2:25:47.55,ENG,1675,0,0,0,,- Oh, I'm sorry, I thought you were done. - Oh, this is a friend of my family's.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:47.65,2:25:52.65,CHT,1676,0,0,0,,本傑明·巴頓，這是我丈夫，羅伯特
Dialogue: 0,2:25:47.65,2:25:52.65,ENG,1676,0,0,0,,Benjamin Button, this is my husband, Robert.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:52.75,2:25:55.15,CHT,1677,0,0,0,,- 你好 - 幸會
Dialogue: 0,2:25:52.75,2:25:55.15,ENG,1677,0,0,0,,- How do you do? - A pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:03.25,2:26:06.25,CHT,1678,0,0,0,,嗯，很高興認識你
Dialogue: 0,2:26:03.25,2:26:06.25,ENG,1678,0,0,0,,Well, it was very nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:06.35,2:26:08.15,CHT,1679,0,0,0,,- 我們就在車上等了，親愛的 - 嗯，好
Dialogue: 0,2:26:06.35,2:26:08.15,ENG,1679,0,0,0,,- We'll be in the car, darling. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:08.25,2:26:09.45,CHT,1680,0,0,0,,拜
Dialogue: 0,2:26:08.25,2:26:09.45,ENG,1680,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:10.15,2:26:11.95,CHT,1681,0,0,0,,我去關門
Dialogue: 0,2:26:10.15,2:26:11.95,ENG,1681,0,0,0,,I'm just locking up.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:16.65,2:26:17.75,CHT,1682,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,2:26:16.65,2:26:17.75,ENG,1682,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:20.25,2:26:23.15,CHT,1683,0,0,0,,她可真美，像她母親
Dialogue: 0,2:26:20.25,2:26:23.15,ENG,1683,0,0,0,,She's beautiful. Like her mother.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:24.75,2:26:27.25,CHT,1684,0,0,0,,- 她跳舞嗎？ - 跳得不是很好
Dialogue: 0,2:26:24.75,2:26:27.25,ENG,1684,0,0,0,,- Does she dance? - Not very well.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:27.35,2:26:29.25,CHT,1685,0,0,0,,估計是遺傳我的吧
Dialogue: 0,2:26:27.35,2:26:29.25,ENG,1685,0,0,0,,I guess that'd be from my side of things.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:29.35,2:26:31.35,CHT,1686,0,0,0,,她是個好姑娘
Dialogue: 0,2:26:29.35,2:26:31.35,ENG,1686,0,0,0,,She's a dear, sweet girl.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:32.55,2:26:36.85,CHT,1687,0,0,0,,只是有點迷惘 不過說回來，誰12歲的時候不是呢
Dialogue: 0,2:26:32.55,2:26:36.85,ENG,1687,0,0,0,,She seems a little lost. But then, who isn't at 12?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:37.05,2:26:41.35,CHT,1688,0,0,0,,她總是讓我想起…你
Dialogue: 0,2:26:37.05,2:26:41.35,ENG,1688,0,0,0,,A lot of her reminds me of you.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:42.25,2:26:46.15,CHT,1689,0,0,0,,我丈夫是個鰥夫，那個…過去是
Dialogue: 0,2:26:42.25,2:26:46.15,ENG,1689,0,0,0,,My husband, he's a widower, or was... Was a widower.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:46.55,2:26:50.45,CHT,1690,0,0,0,,他是個大好人，愛冒險，很陽光
Dialogue: 0,2:26:46.55,2:26:50.45,ENG,1690,0,0,0,,He's an incredibly kind, just bright, adventurous man.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:53.65,2:26:56.35,CHT,1691,0,0,0,,- 他也是個好父親 - 真好
Dialogue: 0,2:26:53.65,2:26:56.35,ENG,1691,0,0,0,,- He's been a terrific father. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:01.05,2:27:04.95,CHT,1692,0,0,0,,- 你看起來，又年輕了好多 - 只是外表
Dialogue: 0,2:27:01.05,2:27:04.95,ENG,1692,0,0,0,,- You are so much younger. - Only on the outside.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:07.05,2:27:08.55,CHT,1693,0,0,0,,你說得對
Dialogue: 0,2:27:07.05,2:27:08.55,ENG,1693,0,0,0,,You were right.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:10.35,2:27:13.75,CHT,1694,0,0,0,,我沒法同時養你們兩個人
Dialogue: 0,2:27:10.35,2:27:13.75,ENG,1694,0,0,0,,I couldn't have been raising both of you.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:13.85,2:27:15.55,CHT,1695,0,0,0,,我不夠堅強
Dialogue: 0,2:27:13.85,2:27:15.55,ENG,1695,0,0,0,,I'm not that strong.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:19.75,2:27:21.85,CHT,1696,0,0,0,,那你住哪？
Dialogue: 0,2:27:19.75,2:27:21.85,ENG,1696,0,0,0,,So, where are you staying?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:24.45,2:27:25.45,CHT,1697,0,0,0,,接下來準備幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,2:27:24.45,2:27:25.45,ENG,1697,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:25.55,2:27:29.35,CHT,1698,0,0,0,,我住在龐恰特雷恩旅店
Dialogue: 0,2:27:25.55,2:27:29.35,ENG,1698,0,0,0,,I'm staying at the Pontchartrain Hotel on the Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:29.45,2:27:33.05,CHT,1699,0,0,0,,也不知道接著該幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,2:27:29.45,2:27:33.05,ENG,1699,0,0,0,,I don't know what I'm gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:33.15,2:27:34.25,CHT,1700,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,2:27:33.15,2:27:34.25,ENG,1700,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,2:27:40.85,2:27:42.45,CHT,1701,0,0,0,,他們在等我
Dialogue: 0,2:27:40.85,2:27:42.45,ENG,1701,0,0,0,,They're waiting.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:24.55,2:28:27.85,CHT,1702,0,0,0,,我還記得，他就是？
Dialogue: 0,2:28:24.55,2:28:27.85,ENG,1702,0,0,0,,I remember that. That was him?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:30.55,2:28:31.65,CHT,1703,0,0,0,,颶風轉向了
Dialogue: 0,2:28:30.55,2:28:31.65,ENG,1703,0,0,0,,The hurricane has changed directions.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:31.75,2:28:33.65,CHT,1704,0,0,0,,不久就登陸
Dialogue: 0,2:28:31.75,2:28:33.65,ENG,1704,0,0,0,,It's going to make landfall sometime soon.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:33.75,2:28:35.45,CHT,1705,0,0,0,,- 我該做些什麼？ - 正在組織撤離人員
Dialogue: 0,2:28:33.75,2:28:35.45,ENG,1705,0,0,0,,- Am I supposed to do something? - Arrangements are being made
Dialogue: 0,2:28:35.55,2:28:36.75,CHT,1706,0,0,0,,不過走不走還是你自己說了算
Dialogue: 0,2:28:35.55,2:28:36.75,ENG,1706,0,0,0,,to move people, but it's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:36.85,2:28:38.75,CHT,1707,0,0,0,,不了，我們留著
Dialogue: 0,2:28:36.85,2:28:38.75,ENG,1707,0,0,0,,No. No, we're... We're staying.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:38.85,2:28:41.45,CHT,1708,0,0,0,,要是情況有變，我會及時通知你
Dialogue: 0,2:28:38.85,2:28:41.45,ENG,1708,0,0,0,,I'll let you know if anything changes.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:43.55,2:28:47.85,CHT,1709,0,0,0,,“那晚，我正坐著 奇怪自己為什麼要回來”
Dialogue: 0,2:28:43.55,2:28:47.85,ENG,1709,0,0,0,,"That night, while I was sitting and wondering why I came back at all,
Dialogue: 0,2:28:47.95,2:28:50.35,CHT,1710,0,0,0,,“傳來了敲門聲”
Dialogue: 0,2:28:47.95,2:28:50.35,ENG,1710,0,0,0,,"there was a knock at the door."
Dialogue: 0,2:28:53.95,2:28:55.15,CHT,1711,0,0,0,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,2:28:53.95,2:28:55.15,ENG,1711,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:09.45,2:29:11.15,CHT,1712,0,0,0,,你過得好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,2:29:09.45,2:29:11.15,ENG,1712,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:14.25,2:29:18.35,CHT,1713,0,0,0,,對不起，我都不知道 自己來這是要幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,2:29:14.25,2:29:18.35,ENG,1713,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I don't know what I'm doing here.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:27.45,2:29:28.85,CHT,1714,0,0,0,,沒什麼是永恆的
Dialogue: 0,2:29:27.45,2:29:28.85,ENG,1714,0,0,0,,Nothing lasts.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:32.35,2:29:34.75,CHT,1715,0,0,0,,我愛你，從沒變過
Dialogue: 0,2:29:32.35,2:29:34.75,ENG,1715,0,0,0,,I have never stopped loving you.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:40.75,2:29:43.45,CHT,1716,0,0,0,,哦，別，本傑明，我太老了
Dialogue: 0,2:29:40.75,2:29:43.45,ENG,1716,0,0,0,,Oh, but, Benjamin, I'm an old woman now.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:54.05,2:29:56.25,CHT,1717,0,0,0,,有些事，你永遠都不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,2:29:54.05,2:29:56.25,ENG,1717,0,0,0,,Some things you never forget.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:16.55,2:30:17.65,CHT,1718,0,0,0,,很少有人知道
Dialogue: 0,2:30:16.55,2:30:17.65,ENG,1718,0,0,0,,... so few people even know
Dialogue: 0,2:30:17.75,2:30:19.45,CHT,1719,0,0,0,,您過去還蹲過監獄
Dialogue: 0,2:30:17.75,2:30:19.45,ENG,1719,0,0,0,,that you were ever in jail in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:19.55,2:30:21.75,CHT,1720,0,0,0,,告訴您吧，我也覺得不爽
Dialogue: 0,2:30:19.55,2:30:21.75,ENG,1720,0,0,0,,I'll tell you, I am sick about it, too,
Dialogue: 0,2:30:21.85,2:30:24.35,CHT,1721,0,0,0,,因為，拜託，他們就算不給您頒個
Dialogue: 0,2:30:21.85,2:30:24.35,ENG,1721,0,0,0,,because, please, if they're not gonna give you an award
Dialogue: 0,2:30:24.45,2:30:26.55,CHT,1722,0,0,0,,“年度人物”之類的大獎，至少
Dialogue: 0,2:30:24.45,2:30:26.55,ENG,1722,0,0,0,,like "Man of the Year," at least what they could do
Dialogue: 0,2:30:26.65,2:30:29.35,CHT,1723,0,0,0,,也該把您的名字從犯人檔案裡除掉
Dialogue: 0,2:30:26.65,2:30:29.35,ENG,1723,0,0,0,,is stop having you listed as an ex-convict
Dialogue: 0,2:30:29.45,2:30:31.95,CHT,1724,0,0,0,,我覺得，這真是太不公了
Dialogue: 0,2:30:29.45,2:30:31.95,ENG,1724,0,0,0,,which I think is, again, so unfair.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:44.75,2:30:46.55,CHT,1725,0,0,0,,晚安，本傑明
Dialogue: 0,2:30:44.75,2:30:46.55,ENG,1725,0,0,0,,Good night, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:48.05,2:30:49.75,CHT,1726,0,0,0,,晚安，黛西
Dialogue: 0,2:30:48.05,2:30:49.75,ENG,1726,0,0,0,,Good night, Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:52.95,2:30:57.15,CHT,1727,0,0,0,,和預想的一樣，我看著她離開
Dialogue: 0,2:30:52.95,2:30:57.15,ENG,1727,0,0,0,,And as I knew I would, I watched her go.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:59.95,2:31:02.15,CHT,1728,0,0,0,,後面他就沒寫了
Dialogue: 0,2:30:59.95,2:31:02.15,ENG,1728,0,0,0,,That's the last thing he wrote.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:03.35,2:31:07.95,CHT,1729,0,0,0,,你父親死後的某一天
Dialogue: 0,2:31:03.35,2:31:07.95,ENG,1729,0,0,0,,Sometime after your father passed,
Dialogue: 0,2:31:08.05,2:31:10.85,CHT,1730,0,0,0,,我接到一個電話
Dialogue: 0,2:31:08.05,2:31:10.85,ENG,1730,0,0,0,,there was a call.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:13.95,2:31:15.15,CHT,1731,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,2:31:13.95,2:31:15.15,ENG,1731,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:16.25,2:31:17.75,CHT,1732,0,0,0,,是我，請講
Dialogue: 0,2:31:16.25,2:31:17.75,ENG,1732,0,0,0,,Yes, speaking.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:21.05,2:31:23.55,CHT,1733,0,0,0,,抱歉，我不太明白
Dialogue: 0,2:31:21.05,2:31:23.55,ENG,1733,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:33.45,2:31:35.25,CHT,1734,0,0,0,,在路邊那房子停下
Dialogue: 0,2:31:33.45,2:31:35.25,ENG,1734,0,0,0,,It's the corner house.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:57.45,2:31:58.85,CHT,1735,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,2:31:57.45,2:31:58.85,ENG,1735,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:04.45,2:32:06.45,CHT,1736,0,0,0,,- 我是黛西·富勒 - 我叫大衛·埃爾南德斯
Dialogue: 0,2:32:04.45,2:32:06.45,ENG,1736,0,0,0,,- I'm Daisy Fuller. - I'm David Hernandez,
Dialogue: 0,2:32:06.55,2:32:10.25,CHT,1737,0,0,0,,是兒童福利中心奧爾良分局的
Dialogue: 0,2:32:06.55,2:32:10.25,ENG,1737,0,0,0,,with the Orleans Parish Department of Child Welfare Services.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:10.35,2:32:12.95,CHT,1738,0,0,0,,他住在一棟危樓裡
Dialogue: 0,2:32:10.35,2:32:12.95,ENG,1738,0,0,0,,He was living in a condemned building.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:14.85,2:32:17.15,CHT,1739,0,0,0,,警方發現了這個
Dialogue: 0,2:32:14.85,2:32:17.15,ENG,1739,0,0,0,,The police found this with him.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:17.25,2:32:20.15,CHT,1740,0,0,0,,裡面有這個地址 而且很多次提到你的名字
Dialogue: 0,2:32:17.25,2:32:20.15,ENG,1740,0,0,0,,This address. It's got your name in it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:21.35,2:32:23.95,CHT,1741,0,0,0,,他不太健康，已經去過醫院了
Dialogue: 0,2:32:21.35,2:32:23.95,ENG,1741,0,0,0,,He's in very poor health. He was taken to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:24.05,2:32:28.15,CHT,1742,0,0,0,,他似乎都分不清，自己是誰，在哪 好像是糊塗了
Dialogue: 0,2:32:24.05,2:32:28.15,ENG,1742,0,0,0,,He doesn't seem to know who or where he is. He's very confused.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:28.25,2:32:31.75,CHT,1743,0,0,0,,我告訴埃爾南德斯先生了 本傑明和我們一樣
Dialogue: 0,2:32:28.25,2:32:31.75,ENG,1743,0,0,0,,I was telling Mr. Hernandez that Benjamin is one of us.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:31.85,2:32:35.75,CHT,1744,0,0,0,,要是他需要個住的地方，就呆在這吧
Dialogue: 0,2:32:31.85,2:32:35.75,ENG,1744,0,0,0,,If he needs a place to stay, it's all right, he can stay here.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:05.15,2:33:06.45,CHT,1745,0,0,0,,本傑明？
Dialogue: 0,2:33:05.15,2:33:06.45,ENG,1745,0,0,0,,Benjamin?
Dialogue: 0,2:33:10.35,2:33:12.15,CHT,1746,0,0,0,,你彈得真好聽
Dialogue: 0,2:33:10.35,2:33:12.15,ENG,1746,0,0,0,,You play beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:15.65,2:33:17.45,CHT,1747,0,0,0,,他好像不太喜歡被人碰
Dialogue: 0,2:33:15.65,2:33:17.45,ENG,1747,0,0,0,,He doesn't seem to like to be touched.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:17.55,2:33:19.25,CHT,1748,0,0,0,,他記性時好時壞，不太能認人
Dialogue: 0,2:33:17.55,2:33:19.25,ENG,1748,0,0,0,,He goes in and out of states of recognition.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:19.35,2:33:20.95,CHT,1749,0,0,0,,醫生說，他們也無能為力
Dialogue: 0,2:33:19.35,2:33:20.95,ENG,1749,0,0,0,,The doctors say, if they didn't know any better,
Dialogue: 0,2:33:21.05,2:33:23.55,CHT,1750,0,0,0,,他已經出現癡呆的症狀了
Dialogue: 0,2:33:21.05,2:33:23.55,ENG,1750,0,0,0,,he has the beginnings of dementia.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:25.35,2:33:27.05,CHT,1751,0,0,0,,你還記得我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,2:33:25.35,2:33:27.05,ENG,1751,0,0,0,,Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,2:33:30.25,2:33:31.55,CHT,1752,0,0,0,,我是黛西
Dialogue: 0,2:33:30.25,2:33:31.55,ENG,1752,0,0,0,,I'm Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:34.15,2:33:35.65,CHT,1753,0,0,0,,我叫本傑明
Dialogue: 0,2:33:34.15,2:33:35.65,ENG,1753,0,0,0,,I'm Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:41.35,2:33:43.95,CHT,1754,0,0,0,,很高興認識你，本傑明
Dialogue: 0,2:33:41.35,2:33:43.95,ENG,1754,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:45.65,2:33:51.05,CHT,1755,0,0,0,,你不介意我坐你旁邊吧？ 我很喜歡聽你彈琴
Dialogue: 0,2:33:45.65,2:33:51.05,ENG,1755,0,0,0,,Would you mind if I sit with you? I would love to hear you play.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:54.95,2:33:56.45,CHT,1756,0,0,0,,我認識你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,2:33:54.95,2:33:56.45,ENG,1756,0,0,0,,Do I know you?
Dialogue: 0,2:34:01.45,2:34:03.05,CHT,1757,0,0,0,,- 我要吃早飯 - 此後，每天
Dialogue: 0,2:34:01.45,2:34:03.05,ENG,1757,0,0,0,,- I want some breakfast. - And every day,
Dialogue: 0,2:34:03.15,2:34:07.15,CHT,1758,0,0,0,,我都要過去看看，他過得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,2:34:03.15,2:34:07.15,ENG,1758,0,0,0,,I would stop by to make sure that he was comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:07.25,2:34:09.85,CHT,1759,0,0,0,,- 不，我沒吃過 - 你剛剛吃完了
Dialogue: 0,2:34:07.25,2:34:09.85,ENG,1759,0,0,0,,- No, I didn't. - You just finished eating.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:09.95,2:34:12.25,CHT,1760,0,0,0,,別以為我不知道你們想耍我！
Dialogue: 0,2:34:09.95,2:34:12.25,ENG,1760,0,0,0,,Don't think I don't know what you're doing!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:12.35,2:34:15.15,CHT,1761,0,0,0,,你們這群該死的騙子！
Dialogue: 0,2:34:12.35,2:34:15.15,ENG,1761,0,0,0,,You're all fucking liars!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:15.25,2:34:18.15,CHT,1762,0,0,0,,他不信自己剛吃了早飯
Dialogue: 0,2:34:15.25,2:34:18.15,ENG,1762,0,0,0,,He doesn't believe he just had his breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:19.45,2:34:23.05,CHT,1763,0,0,0,,哦，咱來想想
Dialogue: 0,2:34:19.45,2:34:23.05,ENG,1763,0,0,0,,Now, why don't we see
Dialogue: 0,2:34:23.25,2:34:26.55,CHT,1764,0,0,0,,給你找點別的事做吧
Dialogue: 0,2:34:23.25,2:34:26.55,ENG,1764,0,0,0,,if we can't find something else for you to do?
Dialogue: 0,2:34:26.75,2:34:29.95,CHT,1765,0,0,0,,我總覺得，自己好像 有很多事情記不得了
Dialogue: 0,2:34:26.75,2:34:29.95,ENG,1765,0,0,0,,I have a feeling there's a lot of things I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:30.05,2:34:31.95,CHT,1766,0,0,0,,比如呢？
Dialogue: 0,2:34:30.05,2:34:31.95,ENG,1766,0,0,0,,Well, like what, sugar?
Dialogue: 0,2:34:33.15,2:34:37.15,CHT,1767,0,0,0,,好像我已經活了很久
Dialogue: 0,2:34:33.15,2:34:37.15,ENG,1767,0,0,0,,It's like there's this whole life I had,
Dialogue: 0,2:34:38.65,2:34:41.05,CHT,1768,0,0,0,,卻不記得過去的生活
Dialogue: 0,2:34:38.65,2:34:41.05,ENG,1768,0,0,0,,and I can't remember what it was.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:43.85,2:34:45.15,CHT,1769,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,2:34:43.85,2:34:45.15,ENG,1769,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:47.25,2:34:48.75,CHT,1770,0,0,0,,即使忘了，也沒事的
Dialogue: 0,2:34:47.25,2:34:48.75,ENG,1770,0,0,0,,It's okay to forget things.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:48.95,2:34:54.55,CHT,1771,0,0,0,,很多時候，他根本不記得 自己是誰，自己在哪
Dialogue: 0,2:34:48.95,2:34:54.55,ENG,1771,0,0,0,,Many times, he would simply forget who or where he was.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:54.95,2:34:56.55,CHT,1772,0,0,0,,他在那，屋頂上
Dialogue: 0,2:34:54.95,2:34:56.55,ENG,1772,0,0,0,,There he is, he's up there on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:56.65,2:34:58.35,CHT,1773,0,0,0,,照顧他並不容易
Dialogue: 0,2:34:56.65,2:34:58.35,ENG,1773,0,0,0,,It wasn't easy.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:58.45,2:35:00.75,CHT,1774,0,0,0,,- 本傑明！ - 我看見了！
Dialogue: 0,2:34:58.45,2:35:00.75,ENG,1774,0,0,0,,- Benjamin! - I can see everything!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:00.85,2:35:02.55,CHT,1775,0,0,0,,- 我能看見大河！ - 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,2:35:00.85,2:35:02.55,ENG,1775,0,0,0,,- I can see the big river! - That's right,
Dialogue: 0,2:35:02.65,2:35:04.45,CHT,1776,0,0,0,,你當然什麼都看得見，小可愛
Dialogue: 0,2:35:02.65,2:35:04.45,ENG,1776,0,0,0,,you can see everything, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:04.55,2:35:06.55,CHT,1777,0,0,0,,我看得見葬著媽媽的墓地
Dialogue: 0,2:35:04.55,2:35:06.55,ENG,1777,0,0,0,,I can see the graveyard where Mama's buried,
Dialogue: 0,2:35:06.65,2:35:09.95,CHT,1778,0,0,0,,- 那裡還埋著很多其他人 - 快下來！
Dialogue: 0,2:35:06.65,2:35:09.95,ENG,1778,0,0,0,,- and all those other people. - I want you to come down!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:10.05,2:35:13.85,CHT,1779,0,0,0,,- 我要是會飛呢？ - 我認識個人就會飛
Dialogue: 0,2:35:10.05,2:35:13.85,ENG,1779,0,0,0,,- What if I could fly? - I knew a man who could fly.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:14.85,2:35:17.75,CHT,1780,0,0,0,,你下來，我就講他的故事給你聽
Dialogue: 0,2:35:14.85,2:35:17.75,ENG,1780,0,0,0,,You come down and I'll tell you all about him.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:21.35,2:35:22.95,CHT,1781,0,0,0,,誰快上去接他
Dialogue: 0,2:35:21.35,2:35:22.95,ENG,1781,0,0,0,,Somebody go up there.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:29.55,2:35:32.55,CHT,1782,0,0,0,,我搬進去住的時候，他相當於五歲
Dialogue: 0,2:35:29.55,2:35:32.55,ENG,1782,0,0,0,,He was five when I moved in.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:32.65,2:35:37.05,CHT,1783,0,0,0,,差不多就是我認識他時候那麼大
Dialogue: 0,2:35:32.65,2:35:37.05,ENG,1783,0,0,0,,Nearly the same age I was when I had met him.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:43.15,2:35:47.05,CHT,1784,0,0,0,,“畫裡畫的是大袋鼠
Dialogue: 0,2:35:43.15,2:35:47.05,ENG,1784,0,0,0,,"This is the picture of Old Man Kangaroo
Dialogue: 0,2:35:47.15,2:35:49.55,CHT,1785,0,0,0,,下午五點，他終於會蹦蹦跳了
Dialogue: 0,2:35:47.15,2:35:49.55,ENG,1785,0,0,0,,"at 5:00 in the afternoon
Dialogue: 0,2:35:49.65,2:35:53.15,CHT,1786,0,0,0,,他的雙腿又粗又壯又漂亮”
Dialogue: 0,2:35:49.65,2:35:53.15,ENG,1786,0,0,0,,"when he had got his beautiful hind legs."
Dialogue: 0,2:35:54.35,2:35:55.65,CHT,1787,0,0,0,,歲月就這樣流逝
Dialogue: 0,2:35:54.35,2:35:55.65,ENG,1787,0,0,0,,The days passed.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:55.75,2:36:00.05,CHT,1788,0,0,0,,我看著他，不會再走路
Dialogue: 0,2:35:55.75,2:36:00.05,ENG,1788,0,0,0,,And I watched as he forgot how to walk
Dialogue: 0,2:36:05.25,2:36:07.75,CHT,1789,0,0,0,,- 不會再說話 - 我叫什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,2:36:05.25,2:36:07.75,ENG,1789,0,0,0,,- and how to talk. - What's my name?
Dialogue: 0,2:36:08.15,2:36:09.55,CHT,1790,0,0,0,,我叫黛西
Dialogue: 0,2:36:08.15,2:36:09.55,ENG,1790,0,0,0,,I'm Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:10.65,2:36:12.45,CHT,1791,0,0,0,,你會說“黛西”嗎？
Dialogue: 0,2:36:10.65,2:36:12.45,ENG,1791,0,0,0,,Can you say "Daisy"?
Dialogue: 0,2:36:14.05,2:36:19.25,CHT,1792,0,0,0,,2002年，火車站換了新鐘
Dialogue: 0,2:36:14.05,2:36:19.25,ENG,1792,0,0,0,,In 2002, they put up a new clock in that train station.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:26.15,2:36:29.85,CHT,1793,0,0,0,,2003年，春天
Dialogue: 0,2:36:26.15,2:36:29.85,ENG,1793,0,0,0,,And in the spring of 2003,
Dialogue: 0,2:36:34.25,2:36:35.95,CHT,1794,0,0,0,,他看著我
Dialogue: 0,2:36:34.25,2:36:35.95,ENG,1794,0,0,0,,he looked at me
Dialogue: 0,2:36:38.45,2:36:43.55,CHT,1795,0,0,0,,那一刻，我知道他認出我來了
Dialogue: 0,2:36:38.45,2:36:43.55,ENG,1795,0,0,0,,and I knew that he knew who I was.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:47.05,2:36:52.85,CHT,1796,0,0,0,,接著，他閉上了眼睛，好像是睡著了
Dialogue: 0,2:36:47.05,2:36:52.85,ENG,1796,0,0,0,,And then he closed his eyes as if to go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:25.45,2:37:29.55,CHT,1797,0,0,0,,- 我真希望我認識他 - 現在你就認識了
Dialogue: 0,2:37:25.45,2:37:29.55,ENG,1797,0,0,0,,- I wish I'd known him. - Now you do.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:34.05,2:37:37.85,CHT,1798,0,0,0,,媽，我去看看怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,2:37:34.05,2:37:37.85,ENG,1798,0,0,0,,Mom, I think I should go see what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:44.95,2:37:46.95,CHT,1799,0,0,0,,晚安，本傑明
Dialogue: 0,2:37:44.95,2:37:46.95,ENG,1799,0,0,0,,Good night, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:17.05,2:38:19.95,CHT,1800,0,0,0,,有些人，生來 就註定可以悠閒地坐在河邊
Dialogue: 0,2:38:17.05,2:38:19.95,ENG,1800,0,0,0,,Some people are born to sit by a river.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:21.45,2:38:23.35,CHT,1801,0,0,0,,有些人，會被閃電擊中
Dialogue: 0,2:38:21.45,2:38:23.35,ENG,1801,0,0,0,,Some get struck by lightning.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:25.25,2:38:27.35,CHT,1802,0,0,0,,有些人，會音樂
Dialogue: 0,2:38:25.25,2:38:27.35,ENG,1802,0,0,0,,Some have an ear for music.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:28.95,2:38:30.65,CHT,1803,0,0,0,,有些人，是藝術家
Dialogue: 0,2:38:28.95,2:38:30.65,ENG,1803,0,0,0,,Some are artists.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:31.95,2:38:33.25,CHT,1804,0,0,0,,有些人，是游泳健將
Dialogue: 0,2:38:31.95,2:38:33.25,ENG,1804,0,0,0,,Some swim.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:34.75,2:38:36.35,CHT,1805,0,0,0,,有些人，懂紐扣
Dialogue: 0,2:38:34.75,2:38:36.35,ENG,1805,0,0,0,,Some know buttons.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:38.15,2:38:39.55,CHT,1806,0,0,0,,有些人，懂莎士比亞
Dialogue: 0,2:38:38.15,2:38:39.55,ENG,1806,0,0,0,,Some know Shakespeare.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:40.65,2:38:42.45,CHT,1807,0,0,0,,有些人，是媽媽
Dialogue: 0,2:38:40.65,2:38:42.45,ENG,1807,0,0,0,,Some are mothers.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:44.45,2:38:47.45,CHT,1808,0,0,0,,有些人，是舞者
Dialogue: 0,2:38:44.45,2:38:47.45,ENG,1808,0,0,0,,And some people dance.
